(121, 78, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'KCPE', 'Head of Nursery Nyongoro', '11', '121', NULL, '4', '11/08/2021 - 11/08/2022', 'Employee: Comments\r\nEvaluation was interactive and good, it has showed me areas of improvement as well as those I need to maintain for achievement of company targets. \r\n\r\nSupervisor: Comments\r\nKarisa Johnson is a well informed, full of ideologies and very discipline. He has interesting interpersonal skills that made working with him enjoyable. \r\nHOD: Comments\r\nThere was no production this year and as expected not much for Sulubu to do in the nursery apart from cleanliness and maintenance of the nursery structures, identifying plus trees. This being said, he could have done more in terms of proposing some trials with the aim of improving the production process especially in the areas he has mentioned he needs on in section three.', '2022-11-08 12:13:16', '2022-11-10 13:08:09'),
