(135, 99, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'KCSE certificate', 'Plantation Maintenance Staff Nyongoro', '5', '119', NULL, '4', '01/01/2022 - 12/31/2022', 'Employee: Comments\r\n\r\nThe company has provided key procedure in evaluating its employees effeciently and organizing to support workers has been encouraging. the evaluation was detailed and informing.\r\n\r\nSupervisor: Comments\r\n\r\nThe evaluation process was on mutual agreement and pointing out of areas to improve on. the staff was over willing to be more resourceful to the company. \r\n\r\nHOD: Comments\r\n\r\nSalim is well aware of his responsibility and tries to do well all duties assigned to him. some issues raised by him in the evaluation have been addressed (salary scale and bonuses for permanent staff etc) and issues relating to transport shall be addressed in due time by the management.', '2022-11-08 17:41:44', '2022-11-10 13:36:17'),
