(144, 95, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'KCPE', 'Plantation Maintenance Staff Nyongoro', '5', '119', NULL, '4', '01/01/2022 - 12/31/2022', 'Employee: Comments\r\n\r\nThe evaluation was smooth and informative. I have learnt my weakensess and strengths from the laments made by my superviors.\r\n\r\nSupervisor: Comments\r\n\r\nEvaluation process was interactive, the staff acknowledged to understand all the question raised.  He was appreciative and pledged to be an assest to the company henceforth. \r\n\r\nHOD: Comments\r\n\r\nHe seems to have skills in all the maintenance activities. He also shows genuine concern for the state of the plantation by suggesting that we need to mechanise more for efficiency and faster maintenance intervention. Like the rest of his colleagues he needs to be made to get a deeper understanding on the importance of his job and how that relates to the company\'s mission and vision.', '2022-11-09 14:05:54', '2022-11-10 13:57:20'),
(145, 68, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'Bachelors of Science in Forestry', 'Forest Technician Kiambere', '2', '33', 33, '4', '01/01/2022 - 11/09/2022', 'Employee: Comments\r\n\r\nFirst I have to thank that management for the opportunity to join this team, towards achieving the company\'s objectives as I gain experience in my line of study.\r\n\r\nSecondly I have to admit during my probation period there were some gaps which were observed in relation to seedlings production which is the core in forestry. I didn\'t manage to achieve my set targets and objectives however through continuous training and interactions with my supervisor I have gained experience and can be entrusted with production and processing of Mukau seedlings and plantation maintenance activities.\r\n\r\nThirdly, I have to appreciate the PMS team I have at site who has been respectful and committed towards their work. Through their unity we have been able to surpass our set targets especially in cleaning activities.\r\n\r\nI look forward to incorporating the whole team including the security and even casual to work as a team and through this we will be able to achieve the company\'s vision and mission and set objectives for every departments.\r\n\r\nSupervisor: Comments\r\n\r\nThe employee joined the company this year. He started at a slow pace but he has since improved after training on both production and maintenance activities. Improvement has especially been noted in the plantation maintenance activities supervision. Continuous training ongoing, however he has a good attitude and he has shown ownership of the project. He is encouraged to continuously communicate for continuous improvement. He has shown honesty through reporting of actual situation on the ground and the correct figures.\r\n\r\nHOD: Comments\r\n\r\nRecently confirmed after probation, Osore was green newly from school, and inexperienced. However, a lot has changed. he has shown that he has the potential to become an accomplished technician. He is young and has been managing a staff that is way older than him. There is, however, still room for improvement with regards to management, precise communication, planning, and monitoring and budgeting.', '2022-11-09 14:45:19', '2022-11-14 14:50:39'),
(146, 112, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'Diploma-Electrical engineering', 'Plantation Maintenance Staff Nyongoro', '4', '119', NULL, '4', '01/01/2022 - 12/31/2022', 'Employee: Comments\r\n\r\nI am satisfied with the evaluation process, it has been a learning process to understand my weakness and with a promise to improve.\r\n\r\nSupervisor: Comments\r\n\r\nThe evaluation process was interactive, the staff showed much interest towards achieving company vision, mission and objectives. He understand his weakness with calmness and promise to improve and be an assest to the company henceforth.\r\n\r\nHOD: Comments\r\n\r\nOkumu seems to understand his job well. He also has other skills that are not forestry-related like welding and has a background in electrical engineering. This could be useful to the company in the near future. It also comes out clearly that for his future career development, he\'d be interested to do something that is not in forestry.', '2022-11-09 17:10:28', '2022-11-10 14:19:58'),
