(149, 9, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'Diploma in Forestry.', 'Monitoring and Evaluation Officer', '5.5', '17', 8, '8', '10/11/2021 - 10/11/2022', 'Nelly is a passionate about the job. She has adapted well to the changes in her job. What is required for now is guidance in the internal policies and work instruction and trainings on using the corrective action system.\r\nOn tree verification, she has been in the field before therefore her interaction with farmers is not new to her. We hope to utilize this skill further in catching with forestry to verify all farms for correct tree stock.\r\nWe also encourage that solution on how to improve her work come from within.', '2022-11-09 19:31:38', '2022-11-14 13:37:43'),
(150, 55, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'Kenya Certificate of Secondary Education', 'Plantation Maintenance Staff Kiambere', '5', '68', 33, '4', '01/01/2022 - 11/10/2022', 'Employee: Comments\r\n\r\nFirst of all I thank the company for the opportunity and good relation so far. Through my daily activities as agreed by my supervisor I will strive to do my best and offer any suggestion necessary to help achieve the company\'s goals and objectives.\r\n\r\nLastly I would request the management company to consider this team in payment increment, life has not been easy and through this, workers will feel motivated and produce results as expected. \r\n\r\nSupervisor: Comments\r\n\r\nThe employee has been useful in tree counting where he has specialized in since he knows all the boundaries of the compartment. He indeed helped me to get to understand the whole of the plantation and where any special needs were required.  Through this we were able to achieve a lot in terms of maintenance since all these activities are core related. The gaps identified in terms of tree counting to get zero error has been agreed on and he is now aware that the company depends very much on the stock figures at all the time. \r\n\r\nHOD: Comments\r\n\r\nhe is skilled in all the maintenance activities within the plantation plus other activities in operations. this is a plus. He however was also part of the team that provided wrong tree counting information at the beginning of the year for whatever reason which is a huge non-conformance. It should also be noted that he acknowledges this by indicating that he needs continuous guidance and training on tree counting.', '2022-11-10 09:37:17', '2022-11-11 18:49:35'),
