(153, 108, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'KCSE', 'Plantation Maintenance Staff Nyongoro', '4', '119', NULL, '4', '01/01/2022 - 12/31/2022', 'Supervisor: Comments\r\n\r\nHashako is a good staff, ready to learn from mistakes and rectify. I am impressed with his work output, generally he is good. \r\n\r\nHOD: Comments\r\n\r\nHashako is well experienced in maintenance activities that are specific to forestry. He seems to be interested in improving in areas specific to forestry which is a good thing for the forestry department. However, his self-motivation is worrying and something that must be improved upon in the next working year for him to realize optimum or agreeable results by the company\'s standards.', '2022-11-10 10:05:56', '2022-11-10 14:28:49'),
