(218, 18, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'A Bachelor  Degree', 'Agroforestry Agent Dokolo', '3', '3', 4, '4', '11/17/2022 - 11/17/2022', 'The employee has the right attitude towards the job given that it was her first time to manage the over all process  of distribution but she did a good  job in monitoring, follow ups were to be made in time to ensure good exercise  accomplished.\r\nThe employee has promised to improve on communication,  team work, planning and organising to which the job need most.', '2022-11-17 14:39:34', '2022-11-22 09:50:15'),
(219, 3, 'HOD reviewed', 'yearly', 'Certificate in Forestry', 'Site Manager Dokolo', '7', '4', NULL, '4', '11/18/2021 - 11/19/2022', 'There is a need for improvement in the following areas:\r\n\r\n1. Ensuring that all the 7 forks staff understand the importance of working with groups and not individual farmers.\r\n\r\n2. That in as much as the team is trained in forestry/agroforestry and is capable technically, the farmers\' program success also depends on the creation of meaningful relationships with the farmers. \r\n\r\n3. Ensure that the team at all times provides correct information/feedback.\r\n\r\n4. Ensure that the team understands why we must plant and ensure that all the trees survive. Meaning, we have to do everything necessary within the scope of the company\'s guidelines to ensure this happens.\r\n\r\nConversely, there has been a tremendous positive change in 7 forks since he took over with regard to people management and better communication that has made it possible to get a clearer picture of what exactly is going on within the 7 forks project (important in making decisions for correction/improvement)', '2022-11-18 17:59:37', '2022-11-22 10:32:18'),
