(71, 36, 81, '<p>1. Continuous Training on different aspects and approaches of the project. This includes and not limited to Planning and organization, continuous communication, being keen to details and guidance</p><p>2. Follow ups and giving feedback to raised&nbsp; concerns related to the project&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1.Has a lot skills and knowledge in this project which he still need to share for more improved running of the project. He need to create time often for this.</p><p>2. Find time during sites visits to be together with him so that I can get know more and how things are done practically in relation to this project</p>', '<p>1.IT department has been proactive to issues raised and addressing them</p><p>2. Communication department has really opened my mind through few sessions through working parties we have been having</p><p>3. HR department has really support my team in sites during this covid 19&nbsp; pandemic</p><p>4. M&amp;E has helped a lot in project monitoring and getting to know what happening on the ground</p>', '<p>1.Operations has sometimes lost grip when it comes to fuel&nbsp; payment especially in Dokolo where my team had to halt field operations due to lack of field though the issue has not been consistent. There is need to address that</p><p><br></p>', '2021-11-11 15:28:15', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(72, 2, 60, '<p>The management team and other members of staff have been very supportive in regards to helping me understand how operations of the company policies works. They have always been r available&nbsp; to offer guidance at all times.<br>My supervisor understand the departments operations very well and links the departs with other departments so well for proper coordination and service delivery.<br></p>', '<p>n/a</p>', '<p>With good employee to employee interactions&nbsp; we have managed to move so swiftly.<br>All the departments are moving on well with one common Vision and Mission of the Company. So far no alarming situation.&nbsp;<br></p>', '<p>Communication from sites and staff giving feedback in the case they&nbsp; have reported an incident they should also be available when the support team are on their case.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-12 08:43:57', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
