(74, 93, 4, '<p>1. Excellent managerial and supervision skills</p><p>2. Always ready to listen to my challenges at work and assist in immediate possible solutions.</p><p>3. He is honest and transparent.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>1. Excellent provision and implication of health and safety measures.</p><p>2. Improved mechanization.</p><p>3. Payment of workers on time.</p>', '<p>1. Motivation to workers.</p>', '2021-11-12 10:24:26', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
(75, 4, 83, '<p>1. The management team meeting has been an instrumental platform for addressing issues, getting feedback and guidance on issues.</p><p>2. Takes his time to explain the various changes in strategy and the reason behind them. This makes it easier to convey changes to the team i manage.</p>', '<p>1. More field presence&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. Operations:- There have been massive improvements here in all aspects of operations.&nbsp;</p><p>2. HR:- Creation of the department has ensured that previously worker unaddressed issues have been dealt with. EG health and safety issues that have motivated workers.</p><p>3. Communication:- focus on communication that has helped us pinpoint specific issues that we have in communication (bottom down communication). Other aspects that have been put in place include minutes for all key meetings which we did not have and sessions on leadership and communication. The fact that we have a communication manager is also a signal that communication is key to our success.</p><p>4. IT:- previous use of hard copy records was challenging. we had many delays, in procurement, monthly reports, Corrective actions that were based on hard copy reports etc. which has made reaction time to issues shorter.</p>', '<p>N/A</p>', '2021-11-12 11:46:00', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
(76, 1, 63, '<p>Better guidance and good explanation of what an App should entail before the development, during, and after</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Ability to clearly explain challenges faced when using developed applications so as improvement can be done especially the Operations Department</p><p>Departments being positive in change from manual ways to digital ways without criticism</p>', '<p>Departments should understand the different roles of each individual in the IT Department</p>', '2021-11-12 13:02:27', '2022-05-20 16:21:38'),
