(88, 34, 93, '<p>I have got support and guidance from my supervisor which has helped me be in a position to well manage my department</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Forestry department: There has been great improvement in supervision, delegation and taking responsibility by the forestry team&nbsp;</p><p>Operations department: There has been improvement in managing company property especially on sites though there is still room for improvement</p><p>Finance department: There has been minimal complaints by staff for delayed payments</p><p>Communication department: There is a huge improvement in staff communication vertically and also when we visit the sites the staff can openly air their grievances.</p><p>IT department: Most of the manual work has been reduced immensely by the many APPS that have been developed and the ticketing system has really helped&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>We still have gaps in communication</p>', '2021-11-18 13:50:12', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
