(100, 148, 109, '<p>1. Supportive on the job which has enabled me to improve my performance from last time.<br></p>', '<p>1. Prompt delivery of requests. E..g. Donkey Medicines.<br></p>', '<p>1. Communication between the HOS, Site Managers and the Head office is good.<br></p>', '<p>1. Provision of Bee Suit so that immediate interventions can be implemented in case we have a hive that falls and is colonized.</p><p>2. Cleaning to resume in the plantation to control grass to mitigate incidences of fire.<br></p>', '2022-08-19 15:44:33', '2022-08-19 15:44:33'),
