(102, 73, 112, '<p>1) Respect to workers.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The supervisor has been paying attention to workers grievances such as following up on deductions of salaries.</span></p><p>2) Reporting to work on time by all security guards, this has helped in ensuring taking over of duty is done on time</p>', '<p>N/A</p>', '<p>Operations.</p><p>1) Ensuring communication gadgets are in place and working</p><p>2) Provision of grass to the local community has left the plantation very clean and this has reduced the effect of \"Unyoe\" grass to workers</p><p><br></p><p>Forestry.</p><p>1) The cleanliness of the plantation has been maintained throughout the year.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Operations/HR</p><p>To create ranks in the security uniforms to show the supervisors</p>', '2022-11-07 17:11:58', '2022-11-07 17:11:58'),
