(175, 66, 190, '<p>1) Good communication with workers.</p><p>2) Planning and organizing of work on site has helped maintenance activities on site.</p>', '<p>1) To be more observant on site and take time for any information given by workers, to avoid listening to rumors.</p>', '<p>1) Human resource- 1)Enhancing safety and wellbeing of workers 2)Creation of disciplinary code for listening to grievances.</p><p>2) Communications-Provision of communication platforms.</p><p>3)Operation-1)Provision of tools and equipment 2)creation of storage facilities. 3) Maintenance of tools and equipments</p>', '<p>Operation-1) Provide gutters for water conservation.</p><p>Human resource-Provide benchmarking for workers between sites for motivation and sharing of ideas.</p><p>Forestry-Create storage facilities for fruits and seeds.</p>', '2022-11-12 17:14:10', '2022-11-12 17:14:10'),
(176, 119, 170, '<p>1. Have great interpersonal and leadership skills.</p><p>2. Well versed with knowledge in Forestry especially Melia management.</p>', '<p>1. Work on being composed even when under pressure.</p>', '<p>1. Being innovative e.g constant working on development on melia management i.e seedling production for increased seedling germination %.</p>', '<p>1. Work under sufficient staff capacity.</p>', '2022-11-12 18:14:51', '2022-11-12 18:14:51'),
(177, 142, 191, '<p>1) Always follow up issues reported for.</p><p>2) Training and giving of guidance on working among the other guards.</p>', '<p>1) Need to spend equal time with security team same as that given to PMS. In explanation of policies or any form of training time spent with PMS should be equal with that given security team.</p>', '<p>1) Operations-Provision of walkie-talkies for communication</p><p>2) Communication- creation of communication platform.</p>', '<p>Human resource- Employment of more security guards.</p>', '2022-11-14 10:16:25', '2022-11-14 10:16:25'),
(178, 154, 193, '<p>1) The supervisors has been of great assistance in issues related to work.</p>', '<p>1) To follow up issues discussed on site for actions to be taken for instance the shelter required in A016 is not sorted yet.</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">1) Operations-Provision of walkie-talkie devices for communication within the site.</span><br></p>', '<p>1) Operations-To fast track provision of security uniforms, and line for communications.</p>', '2022-11-14 13:11:44', '2022-11-14 13:11:44'),
