(183, 4, 197, '<p>1. Management team meetings.</p><p>2. Digital systems for managing staff, communication and HR issues.</p><p>3. Microsoft project. it is a proper professional tool for managing projects.</p>', '<p>1. Field visits by the supervisor from time to time to Uganda.</p>', '<p>1. Communication has improved.</p><p>2. HR:- Management PPE has improved&nbsp;</p><p>3. IT:- Development of digital tools that have made work easier.</p><p>4. M&amp;E:- Has helped in checking if information/data provided in the forestry department is correct or not.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. We still had issues with security.</p><p>2. M&amp;E for Uganda. It could be better if we had a team on the ground.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-14 16:56:53', '2022-11-14 16:56:53'),
