(186, 122, 152, '<p>Continous communications and discussions</p>', '<p>Taking responsibility.</p>', '<p>Human Resource Department&nbsp;</p><p>Timely responses on issues which needed attention&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Human Resource</p><p>Finance employees whenever they need financial assistance to avoid higher interest earning credit facilities and deduct from their salaries.</p><p>Forestry</p><p>Always manage weeds at their juvenile stage to facilitate the use of machinery.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-14 18:39:58', '2022-11-14 18:39:58'),
