(204, 20, 217, '<p>The supervisor communicates so clearly and has alot of knowledge and experience about the program&nbsp;</p>', '<p>He still has to improve on building a team that is resilient and coordinated&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The bike repairs have improved with introduction of Nile fishing&nbsp;</p><p>Salaries are coming well&nbsp;</p><p>Communication has improved&nbsp;</p>', '<p>With bike repairs, there is need to improve on minor and emergency repairs as that\'s currently a challenge&nbsp;</p><p>Need to also be consistent with our programs, not starting and stopping always&nbsp;</p><p>Salaries need to be paid in time and if there is any delay, timely communication is paramount&nbsp;</p><p>Need to improve on visibility especially around the areas of operation&nbsp;</p><p>The groups should be supported especially in IGAS&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-17 15:36:12', '2022-11-17 15:36:12'),
(205, 18, 218, '<p>The level of supervision&nbsp; and follow-ups to bring employees to ensure the right thing done at the right time</p>', '<p>Time work&nbsp; across the company to ensure we live to meet the vision and mission</p>', '<p>Other departments&nbsp; being very supportive&nbsp; to forestry department.</p>', '<p>More employees in forestry department&nbsp; especially&nbsp; AAs for Dokolo site to help apportioning&nbsp; of work load leading to achieving of annual target</p>', '2022-11-17 17:09:01', '2022-11-17 17:09:01'),
