(211, 42, 220, '<p>The assistant head of security has been ensuring communication gadgets are well charged i.e. Walkie-talkies and tools required in patrols are given in good conditions.</p>', '<p>None.</p>', '<p>1) Operations- Provision of walkie-talkies for communications.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Fencing maintenance in the plantation has been of great assistance in ensuring plantation is well protected.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Adjustments of working hours for security guards from 72 to 52 hours per week.</p>', '<p>1) Operation- Provision of quality torches which can last the whole night.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Provision of quality raincoats for protection during rainy season.</p>', '2022-11-23 10:37:16', '2022-11-23 10:37:16'),
