(216, 157, 226, '<p>1. Advice received from the supervisor has enabled me to perform my duties effectively.</p><p>2. Teamwork from the outgrowers program team has encouraged me to perform my duties very well.</p><p>3. she has been giving me the clear guidelines on how to improve and work efficiently.</p>', '<p>1. To be more firm&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. provision of PPEs helps to achieve the targets.</p><p>2. Provision of monthly Airtime.</p><p>3. Operations, especially motorbike repair.</p>', '<p>1. Need to staff ID and BGF T-shirts.</p>', '2023-07-03 17:42:37', '2023-07-03 17:42:37'),
