(218, 160, 228, '<ul><li>-The work has been running very well.</li><li>-The supervisors have been available when in need.</li></ul><p><br></p>', '<p>-Everything is okay.</p>', '<p>-The community is cooperating e.g the grass collectors..</p><p>-Request made from security team have been delivered on time.</p>', '<p>-Delayed replacement of security uniforms to the old guards.</p><p>-Re-introduce issuance of airtime to the security guards.</p><p>-Construction of shelter structure in the plantation during night patrols when it is raining. This will also help protect walkie-talkies which can be damaged with water.</p>', '2023-08-22 14:11:16', '2023-08-22 14:11:16'),
(219, 161, 229, '<p>-Everything has worked well.</p>', '<p>-The assistant head of security to always communicate issues affecting her and other guards with the FT.</p>', '<p>-Operations-Installation of security lights in the nursery.</p><p>Provision of grass to the local community.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>-Forestry to plant more trees in unplanted areas.</p><p>-Handling of devices on site to be done by the device handlers rather than delegating to non-device handlers.</p><p>-Construction of shelters in the plantation for protection during rainy season.</p>', '2023-08-23 13:08:22', '2023-08-23 13:08:22'),
