(2, 135, 11, '<p>1. Carryout all plantation maintenance activities according to approved plans.</p><p>2. Provide accurate reports for daily forestry activities</p><p>3. Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'</p><p>4. Be communication link to the forest technician on plantation occurrances.</p><p>5. Provide any operational assistance as required by the supervisor.</p><p>6. Contribute to team effort by accomplishing related results as needed.</p>', '<p>1. Participated in masonry activities ( construction of site toilet)</p><p>2. Timber sawing.</p>', '<p>1. By carrying out&nbsp; plantation maintenance activities, there is an enhanced trees survival thus ensuring their will be many trees as people in the world. this directly relate my job to the company mission.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Trees survival through correct maintenance leads to provision of jobs to the local and me as an employee which assist in poverty eradication due availability of wages.</p>', '<p>1.Plantation cleaning and pruning well done in 2021.</p><p>2. Construction of PPE store and toilets.</p><p>3. establishment of electric fence to cushion plantation from damages.</p><p>4. Immediate response of workers grieviances by the management.</p><p>5.Retaining workers on full payment during Covid pandemic.</p>', '<p>1. Provision of transport to work stations in the plantation.</p><p>2.Stocking of spare parts for machinery tools to avoid affecting work plans.</p><p>3.Increased health coverage for staff family members.</p><p>4. Introduction of hardship allowance.</p><p>5.Provision of at least one meal in a day.</p>', '<p>1. Lack of transport to the plantation.</p><p>2. Risk subjected to by wild animals.</p>', '<p>1. Capacity building through benchmarking.</p><p>2. Salary increament to cushion increased living standard.</p><p>3.Establishment of servant houses within site.</p><p>4. Seedlings donation to staffs at least 20 seedlings once a year.</p>', '2021-11-06 06:25:26', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(3, 12, 7, '<p>Farm visits and farm verification&nbsp;</p><p>Compiling reports and sending electronically&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Conducted various trainings on covid-19 awareness with farmer groups&nbsp;</p><p>Being vetted by managing director&nbsp;</p>', '<p>By encouraging contracted farmers to plant many trees and ensure that they all survive so that when we buy from them they can be empowered by money got from it thereby reducing poverty.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>-Getting the right information from farmers for data base cleaning&nbsp;</p><p>-Identifying the root cause of low tree survival.</p><p>-Visiting farmers who are not in your own territory&nbsp;</p><p>-Mobilizing farmers for trainings within this covid-19 period.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Issuing farmers seedlings that are of good quality and at the right time&nbsp;</p><p>Having a local supplier for motorbikes who will in position to repair bikes timely whenever breakdowns occur while on field work.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>- Motorbike breakdowns while on field work activities and we don\'t have a local supplier to rescue you from that.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>-We need to have a local supplier for the repair of motorbikes&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-06 07:47:48', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(4, 14, 5, '<p>1. Farm visit and verification</p><p>2. Compiling and sending the reports electronically.</p>', '<p>1. Vetted by the Managing Director.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Conducting COVID 19 Training and protocols.&nbsp;</p>', 'When farmers plant more trees they will sell them and get money to reduce the poverty.', '<p>Some causes of mortality</p><p>soil conservation training implementation</p><p>&nbsp;Individual Farms visits&nbsp;</p><p>Mobilizing farmers to observe covid 19 protocols.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>continuous staff Refreshing trainings&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>distributing the quality seedlings to the farmers</p><p>timely seedlings distribution to avoid late planting staff e.g. giving out the bonus and some annual salary increment.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Poor roads.</p><p>2. mechanical break down - when the bike gets a problem sometime one has no money hence we should have a local suppler or given some field allowance.</p><p>3. Absent of farmers in there homes.</p><p>4. Miscommunication - changing of directions by the management.</p>', '<p>To re- introduce the the training allowance to the groups.</p>', '2021-11-06 08:07:41', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
(5, 115, 12, '<p>1.Always achieve assigned task \'task rate\'</p><p>2. Carry out all the plantation maintenance activities such as pruning according to approved plans.</p><p>3.Provide accurate reports for assigned activity on daily basis.</p><p>4.Communicate immediately any occurrence in the plantation.</p><p>5. Assist in any operational activities as assigned by the supervisor.</p><p>6. Handling clocking devices.</p>', '<p>1.Operate GPS device when doing compartment griding, stock assessment and prospection.</p><p>2. Handling store/recording keeping on site when delegated by the SLO.</p>', '<p>1. By doing duties and responsibilities assigned in accordance based on company policies and procedures to attain their objectives.</p><p>2. Support my families by providing employment to me. this helps to empower and allieviate poverty to the community.</p><p>3. By ensuring trees survival, ultimately there will be as many trees as there are people in the world.</p>', '<p>1. Through regular training thereby enabling task to be achieved in desired quality.</p><p>2. Provision of PPEs for safety at work place.</p><p>3.Investing on control measures for Covid-19 by the company.</p><p>4. Installation of electric fence, which shall reduce trees mortality.</p><p>5. Cushion of employees during covid pandemic. i.e no pay cut or lay off done.</p><p>6.Provision of clean drinking water from WIWA to all staffs on site.</p>', '<p>1.Provide reliable means of transport from site to work stations in the plantation.</p><p>2.Introduce capacity buildings/team building with other sites for learning purposes.</p><p>3.Introduction of competitions on the basis of best performing sites for awards.</p>', '<p>1.Lack of transportation means to the plantation from sites.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1.Security to do survey of assigned work areas before forestry workers. to avoid expose of risk to wildlife-human conflict.<br></p>', '2021-11-06 09:19:45', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
