(8, 3, 14, '<p>1.&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Implement, Supervise, and control all forestry activities on site</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Developing and implementation\r\n     of an approved work plan.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">3. Management of Human\r\nresource on site</span>', '<p>1.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Represent the company in the community/institutional workshops when called upon.</span></p>', '<p>By planting trees with farmers\' agroforestry social entrepreneurship program and ensure they survive, aimed at reducing poverty level and improve livelihoods.</p>', '<p>1. Verification exercise where a complete audit of all the farmers is currently ongoing. this will result in knowing the exact number of farmers, trees, and their geographical locations.</p><p>2. Participated in GIC V final evaluation.</p>', '<p>1. Timely communication of proposed assignments and providence of necessary support from other departments.</p>', '<p>1. Miscommunication - where activities are delayed due to a communication breakdown. e.g satellite nurseries seedlings were not bought.</p><p>2.&nbsp; Mechanical breakdowns of motorbikes which took time to repair</p>', '<p>1. Training on communication</p><p>2. Periodic training on motorbike riding and maintenance.</p><p>3. Training on advanced data management and analysis tools.</p>', '2021-11-08 08:32:09', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
(9, 68, 15, '<p>Management of Kiambere site ;&nbsp;</p><p>1) Implement, supervise and control all forestry activities on site according to the plan and budget.</p><p>2) Timely reporting of all activities on site.</p><p>3) Developing and implementation of approved workplans.</p><p>4) Management of Human resource on site according to company policies.</p><p>5) Represent the company as required.</p><p>6) Ensure that health and safety guidelines are implemented.</p><p>7) Give short training sessions to workers on specific subjects.</p><p>8) Permanent evaluation of staff performance&nbsp;</p><p>9) Make suggestions for continuous improvement of all operations on site and encourage all workers to do the same.</p><p>10) Carry out any other duties as may be assigned.</p>', '<p>Currently assisting in Operations department roles.</p>', '<p>Ensuring the company\'s objectives for the site are met thereby working towards achieving the vision and the mission of the company.</p><p>1) Ensuring production, establishment and maintenance targets are met.</p><p>2) Maintaining a corrupt free environment ( Giving equal chances to workers seeking work opportunities).</p>', '<p>I have helped strengthen the unity of PMS which has improved the team\'s self drive in relation to doing daily activities. This has enabled us to surpass the set targets as per the plan. Example of Cleaning of compartments having Mukau and currently in Neem.</p><p>I have gained experience in production of Mukau seedlings. It was a new adventure and right now am confident that I can be entrusted with the production process.</p>', '<p>I would need more training in leadership skills.</p>', '<p>Domestic Animal Encroachments in the plantation. I have reported many cases in relation to encroachment of animals in the plantation this is hazard to the trees.</p>', '<p>Fencing of the whole plantation using the barbed wire. This would help reduce cases of encroachments and trespasses in the plantation.</p>', '2021-11-08 10:12:1