(29, 106, 31, '<p>1.Lead the security team and ensuring the company property is protected at all times.<br></p>', '<p>1.KIT Handler.</p><p>2.Head of Security.<br></p>', '<p>1.Through my responsibilities, I ensure that the company trees remain standing and are not stolen.<br></p>', '<p>1. There be no theft cases.</p><p>2. The ongoing construction of the electric fence.<br></p>', '<p>1.Training.<br></p>', '<p>1.Conflict with cattle herders in the plantation.<br></p>', '<p>1.Employing more security guards.</p><p>2.Security training on a quarterly basis.<br></p>', '2021-11-09 07:55:35', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(30, 98, 26, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">1. Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">2. Carrying out all plantation maintenance activities such as pruning according to the approved plans.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">3. Provide accurate reports for assigned activities on daily basis.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences in the plantation.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">5. Assist in operational activities as assigned by the supervisor.</p>', '<p>Operation of motorized pruning sow.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Maintaining of all trees planted by BGF and ensure they all survive.</p>', '<p>Pruning has been done immensely, Trees are growing straight and plantation look presentable.</p><p>Staffs trained on first aid, first aid administered to workers who involve in accidents.</p>', '<p>- Motivation of workers who immensely perform well.</p><p>- Inclusion of all workers on task rate setting.</p>', '<p>- Long walking to and from area of work; areas of assignment are much far from site ie approximately 10 or more kilometers.</p><p>- Delay in availability of work tools and other necessities.</p><p>- Inversion by tsetse fly during wet season&nbsp; and ticks in the plantation during dry season.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Development of motivation policy for instance increment of salary, bonus award and promotion for staffs who immensely done well in their areas of assignments.</p>', '2021-11-09 08:05:25', '2022-05-20 16:23:45'),
(31, 99, 29, '<p>1.Carrying out all plantation maintenance activities such as pruning, weeding and cleaning according to the approved plans.</p><p>2. Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'</p><p>3. Provide accurate results for assigned activities on daily basis.</p><p>4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences in plantation to the FTP.</p><p>5. Assist in any operational activities as assigned by the supervisor.</p>', '<p>1. Handling of GPS devices during compartment stock assessment, prospection and marking of planting years activities.</p>', '<p>1. By ensuring that all trees planted are well maintained and survives to maturity through achieving all task rates, activities assigned according to work plans enables the company to achieve the vision and mission.</p>', '<p>1. Perfect status of the plantation in terms of cleaning and pruning.</p><p>2. Construction of PPEs and toilets for better hygiene status during Covid pandemic.</p><p>3. Provision of clean drinking water for all staffs on site.</p>', '<p>1.Provision of transport means to work station from site.</p>', '<p>1. Effects of bites from tsetse fly and ticks. this vectors causes a lot of fatigue and sickness.</p>', '<p>1. Awarding of bonuses to permanent staffs who overachieve task rates after every end month.</p>', '2021-11-09 08:08:59', '2022-05-20 16:23:45'),
(32, 58, 28, '<p>Field Plantation Maintenance Activities.</p><p style=\"text-indent: 0px; \"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Carry out all plantation maintenance\r\nactivities such as pruning, cleaning according to the approved plans.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provide accurate reports for\r\nassigned activities on daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Always achieve assigned task â€˜task\r\nratesâ€™<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communicate immediately on the occurrence\r\nin the plantation<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Assist in operational activities as\r\nassigned by the supervisor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>1.) Construction of site structures (PPE Store).</p>', '<p>By performing the above stated roles to the best of my knowledge. I fully dedicate myself to plant and maintain as many trees as possible towards achieving the mission of the company.</p>', '<p>Cleanliness in the plantation has been well done. This has been achieved through the unity of all the PMS.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Allocation of Good tools.</p><p>Most activity done in the plantation currently is manual cleaning, if we are provided by new pangas, it would make our work easier.</p>', '<p>Current tools we are using has become smaller and lighter hence making us use a lot of energy in doing the task</p>', '<p>Continuous training on maintenance activities</p>', '2021-11-09 08:09:34', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(33, 26, 27, '<p>1. Formation of Farmers Group&nbsp;</p><p>2. group reactivation, program sensitization &amp;&nbsp; capacity building&nbsp;</p><p>3. group verification</p><p>4. group Training and&nbsp; monitoring&nbsp;</p><p>5. preparation and implementation of Approved group&nbsp; Plan&nbsp;</p><p>6. interact&nbsp; with Authorities and administration&nbsp; in Matter related to groups&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. represent the company in meeting at district Level, or any organization eg&nbsp; I represented the company in&nbsp; Production meeting organized by Dokolo District Local government production head of department</p><p>2 . I represented the company on several occasion on Radio talk show&nbsp; &nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. to make sure farmers are in groups and they plant trees and survive&nbsp;</p><p>2. to make sure farmers group are involve in IGAs to boost their financial status&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Taking GPS Coordinates of all 143 groups in dokolo district&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Motivation of group leaders&nbsp; to make&nbsp; sure they provide group information,&nbsp; mobilization of members and participates in other group activities with ease eg. bicycles, gumboots, T-shirts, cap.</p>', '<p>Wider coverage of program area</p><p>Reason&nbsp;</p><p>am alone&nbsp; as group coordinator to do all the activities related to group</p>', '<p>more staff/ personnel&nbsp; to reduce the workload.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-09 08:29:49', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(34, 8, 25, '<p>1. Sound day to day financial Management with the necessary controls (Monitoring and Evaluation).</p><p>2. Allover supervision of the day to day operational logistics.</p><p>3. Guardian of the company quality systems.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>1. My mission is, together with Management, to make sure that everything related with my major roles (see(a) above) remains geared towards the vision of the company.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The improvements in the operations department in matters of structures, clean plantation and machines working without recurring breakdowns.</p>', '<p>1. Having the right staff with the right attitude towards life.</p><p>2. Implementation of the requested apps to be implemented by IT department.</p><p>3. Trainings of staff.</p><p>4. Have funds availed to acquire identified machines and software\'s.</p>', '<p>1. Staff turnover in KIA. The cost of training and retraining when staff leave is high and affecting the smooth operations on the site.</p>', '<p>As in point 4 above.</p>', '2021-11-09 09:09:05', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(35, 28, 30, '<p>1. Ensure all procurements for the site are done timely.</p><p>2. Ensure routine maintenance of machines are done periodically and make sure they are functional.</p><p>3. Ensure all company company licenses are operational and valid.</p><p>4. Ensure continuous communication among operations staff at the site.</p><p>5. Ensure continuous communication with other departments of the company.</p><p>6. Provide support for other departments in the company and ensure that they are operational.</p><p>7. Ensure staff trainings are conducted.</p><p>8. Ensure general site hygiene and cleanliness is maintained.</p><p>9. Ensure that the site structures are well maintained.</p><p>10. Ensure workers report to work on time by making sure the clocking devices are in proper working conditions.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Nothing special to report</p>', '<p>Ensure that I facilitate the entire process of planting trees and they survive and also eliminate unnecessary costs for the company, and adhere to the anti-corruption policy of the company.</p>', '<p>1. The operations staff have been disciplined and followed company policies, I have not had anyone receive warnings or get fired.</p><p>2. The new structures(Crates and PPE stores) at the site have greatly improved the site hygiene, organization and safety of company property.</p>', '<p>1. Better communication with all company supervisors and managers.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Along the way some suppliers had started losing interest in making supplies for the company thus delays in deliveries which greatly affected my targets for activities.</p>', '<p>Communication: Duration taken by management to make decisions and give feedback should take a shorter time. Sometimes it takes long and stalls work.</p>', '2021-11-09 09:22:01', '2022-05-20 16:21:43');
