(36, 122, 24, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Asses the effectiveness of forestry methods by close monitoring of the implementations of procedures and work instructions.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Make timely observations and promptly report non-conformances</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Verification of forestry reports e.g. Tree stock information and Nursery performance</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Directly follow upon all Corrective action requests for Nyongoro</p>', '<h6 style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 14px; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\">Other duties as requested by the Monitoring and Evaluation Manager. e.g. Attending training, analytical reports.</span><br style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"></h6><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Interactions with workers for human resource related feedbacks and queries.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>By close monitoring of the forestry processes, I ensure that forestry process that are being implemented meet the required standards. When the standards are met, quality trees that produce quality timber is produce hence fetching more income. When the income is projected to be high as a result of high quality timber, then more trees will be planted. Poverty is gradually eradicated as there is a financial flow making it possible for the company to higher more employees.<br></p>', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">A Promotion from internship to a full Better Globe Forestry Staff.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Identified non-conformances in plantation that led to Beacon installation and proper demarcation of boundaries.</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Identified the lack of signed work instructions and procedures hence the current process of developing a document control system by IT.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">A PPE store was constructed as a result of Non conformances touching on health and safety,&nbsp;<span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Employees were trained on Health and safety and</span><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;More PPE\'s were procured</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Counted all trees in the plantation and found the correct stock</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><br style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"></p>', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Training employees on how the BGF M&amp;E system operates</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Approval of CAR\'s by HOD\'s taking too long for follow up</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Training on all work instructions</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><br style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"></p>', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-c