-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Provision of GPS device for the Monitoring and Evaluation at the site.</p>', '2021-11-09 11:23:20', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
