(40, 18, 35, '<p>1. To distibute quality seedlings to interested and contracted farmers&nbsp; in groups</p><p>2. To monitor and supervise the distribution exercise</p><p>3. To link Better Globe Company and stake holders</p><p>4. To manage the Distribution Records</p><p>5. Toeradicate mortalities during&nbsp; seedling transportation.</p><p>6. To train farmers and farmer groups in line with BGF\'s policies</p>', 'Present the company\'s ideas during talk show and local authorities and relevant stake holders', '<p>Planting trees with the farmers and carring out monitoring, training farmer on farms to ensure that the trees survive and well managed</p>', '<p>Getting closer to our farmers , knowing the tress stock.</p>', '<p>Group re-activation and forming more groups so that its easeier to meet the farmers other than meeting them individually.</p>', 'identifying female farmers. with married women its hard to find them because they are not usually known in the communities with their surnames.', '<p>Introduction of house hold names for married women.</p><p>Work more to ensure the groups are participating actively in any ongoing activities.</p>', '2021-11-09 13:13:29', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(41, 94, 36, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">1. Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">2. Carrying out all plantation maintenance activities such as pruning according to the approved plans.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">3. Provide accurate reports for assigned activities on daily basis.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences in the plantation.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">5. Assist in operational activities as assigned by the supervisor.</p><