(42, 95, 37, '<p>1. Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'</p><p>2. carrying out all maintenance activities such as pruning according to the approved plans.</p><p>3. Provide accurate and correct report for assigned activities on daily basis.</p><p>4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences in the plantation.</p><p>5. Assist in any other operational activities as assigned by supervisor.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>By planting and maintaining trees assist in actualizing company vision and mission. through continous tree planting the company expands and increases his labour thus helping to eradicate poverty. Communicating correct and accurate reports on plantation activities helps in fighting corruption.</p>', '<p>1. Training on forestry related task.</p><p>2. Good coordination of workers with supervisors.</p><p>3. Team work</p>', '<p>1. Frequent training on various task done on site.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Introduce craft certificate training through linking with institutions to offer the courses.</p>', '2021-11-09 13:46:32', '2022-05-20 16:23:45'),
(43, 11, 38, '<p>To verify 4 farmers&nbsp; a day&nbsp;</p><p>To check and take correct/complete&nbsp; farmer&nbsp; details.&nbsp;</p><p>Report every Friday on the farms checked based on the approved&nbsp; template..</p><p>Work as a team in agreed upon Sub location.</p>', '<p>To train farmers on protection for the realization of better tree survival .</p>', '<p>To plant trees which will be sold at a higher price,and as a result the level of poverty&nbsp; will be reduced.</p>', '&nbsp;I was able to mobilize and train farmers during covid -19 pandemic&nbsp;&nbsp;', '<p>Motivation of staffs through salary increments.&nbsp;</p><p>Provision of&nbsp; farmers allowance.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Mechanical&nbsp; breakdown,there was no steady&nbsp; supplier.&nbsp;</p><p>Covid -19 restriction&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Each AA to be provided with emergency funds where the area is remote and&nbsp; suppliers is out of reach.</p>', '2021-11-09 14:28:34', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(44, 17, 42, '<p>Tree count verification in farms to ensure correct tree stock.</p><p>Checking and verifying compliance with internal policies and the outgrowers.</p><p>Raising corrective action request on non conformance and following up on the proposed corrective action.</p><p>Measuring impact of trainings on farmers and trees survival.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>On request,to check status of Kiambere site.</p>', '<p>From assessing and gauging the company\'s activities based on the agreed standards and ensuring they are adhered to the latter,the company will have the correct number of trees standing hence promoting the achievement of the mission of planting trees and the vision of eradicating&nbsp; poverty in Africa.</p>', '<p>Development of online Monitoring and Evaluation checklist that enhances data collection in the field.This has enabled paperless monitoring and evaluation which saves time and money.Reporting has been made easier.&nbsp;</p><p>I achieved a professional certificate in Monitoring and Evaluation at Corporate Staffing Services ltd.</p><p>Understanding how 7 forks farmers empowerment and land restoration program operate in record time to implement my objectives after transfer of roles.</p>', '<p>An increase of credit limit from 2000 shillings to 3000 shillings. This will help to contact more partner farmers therefore moving the same pace with forestry.</p><p>Provision of a&nbsp; laptop.The provided tablet doesn\'t have microsoft 365 hence submitting quality report is a challenge. Also the typing experience and ability to manage documents is strained.</p><p>Provision of system for tracking farmers using GPS coordinate to ease difficulty in locating farmers. e.g Avenza app</p>', '<p>Language barrier between Me and partner farmers who only understand Kamba language.</p><p>Difficulty in locating partner farmers without the help of a representative</p>', '<p>None</p>', '2021-11-09 16:49:47', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
