ns-serif;\">Organizing workshops\r\nand training logistics</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 18pt; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: none; padding: 0cm;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Symbol;\">Â·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Nurturing pupils and\r\nstudents on environmental conservation<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'By massively planting trees through the GIC project and inculcating the culture of tree growing to school going children leads to poverty alleviation among the neighbouring communities&nbsp; through sustainable livelihoods and economic empowerment .This in the long run will lead to reduced corruption.', '<p>Sustaining the GIC project and achieving a survival rate of 62.1% for GIC V despite the COVID 19 pandemic challenges</p><p>Conducting GIC VII registration, workshop and seedling issuance in the midst of tough restrictions and tight school calendar</p>', '<p>Timely approval of calendar of events&nbsp;</p><p>Timely and well coordinated repair of bikes</p>', '<p>Delayed approval of calendar of events by the technical committee</p><p>Strict school calendar and aligning GIC project to fit in the new school calendar.</p>', '<p>Replacement of old bike to increase efficiency since GIC operation area has become very expansive</p><p>Establishment of Key communication persons from each partner for well coordinated activities</p><p>Increased remunerations to cater for the rising cost of living</p>', '2021-11-10 04:19:30', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(46, 54, 43, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Carry out all plantation maintenance\r\nactivities such as pruning, cleaning according to the approved plans.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provide accurate reports for\r\nassigned activities on daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Always achieve assigned task â€˜task\r\nratesâ€™<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communicate immediately on the\r\noccurrence in the plantation<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Assist in operational activities as\r\nassigned by the supervisor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Performed as security guard initially</p><p>Building of site structures in the nursery</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">By performing the above\r\nstated roles to the best of my knowledge. I fully dedicate myself to plant and\r\nmaintain as many trees as possible towards achieving the mission of the company<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Tree counting figures. The figures given in the previous years were not correct and this year we have tried to give as accurate figures as possible.</p>', '<p>Good tools for maintenance activities.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;Corvid Out break. Working close with fellow colleagues was a problem and I feared coming to work.</p><p>Dismissal of the supervisors before we get to interact well, making us to work in fear of dismissal anytime.</p>', '<p>Training on how to handle Mukau plantation which is more advance than ours to identify any gaps.</p>', '2021-11-10 05:40:16', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(47, 25, 44, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">1. Implement, supervise and control all foresry activities at the site.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">2. Timely reporting of all site activities.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">3. Development and implementing approved plans.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">4. Management of Human resource at the site in accordance to company policies.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">5. Represent the company as required.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">6. Induction of new staff.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">7. Follow approved human resource policies</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">8. Ensure implementation of Health and safety guidelines</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">9. Give short trainings to workers on specific subjects.</span></p>', '<p>1. Ensuring a good working relationship with YICAFA</p><p>2. Organising radio talkshows</p><p>3. Closely working with district authorities in the program areas.</p>', '<p>Recruiting small holder farmers and ensuring they are issued with seedlings, plant and all trees planted survive from the field.</p>', '<p>1. Identifying and recovering farmers who had planted trees and were not in the company records.</p><p>2. Correcting farmers trees stock data.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Continous staff trainings by the supervisors and external bodies/organisations.</p><p>2. Following the plans initiated at the begining of the year without change in the course of the year/program.</p><p>3. Adding and replacing staff which resigned.</p><p>4. Motivation of farmers groups to get fully engaged in our program field activities.</p>', '<p>1. Getting wrong reports from the field team.</p><p>2. Delayed procurement of site requests needed at the site such as site stationary and fuel.</p>', '<p>1. Provision of the company\'s long term project plans.</p><p>2. Owning the site annual budget.</p><p>3. Close interraction with all department supervisors and other BGF site staffs.</p>', '2021-11-10 06:00:23', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(48, 22, 45, '<p>1. Ensure safety of company property.</p><p>2. Heading the security team.</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">3. Ensure proper welfare of all the staff at the site.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">4. Ensure safety of all staff at the site.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">5. Ensure all the clocking devices are well handled.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">6. Ensure </span>continuous<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;communication between the security team and site supervisors.</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Primary device handler.</p><p>2. Head of Security.</p>', '<p>As a security, I have to be trustworthy, honest, and work according to company policies.</p>', '<p>1. Timely monthly payment by the company for the work I have done.</p><p>2. Safe clean drinking water at the site for workers.</p>', '<p>1. Providing security with all requirements while on duty, for example buy for security a mobile phone and have airtime loaded for easier communication incase of emergencies.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Payment for work overtime not being received.</p>', '<p>Transport provision for security incase of emergencies.<br></p>', '2021-11-10 06:44:13', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(49, 55, 49, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Carry out all plantation maintenance\r\nactivities such as pruning, cleaning according to the approved plans.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provide accurate reports for\r\nassigned activities on daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Always achieve assigned task â€˜task\r\nratesâ€™<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communicate immediately on the\r\noccurrence in the plantation<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Assist in operational activities as\r\nassigned by the supervisor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Construction of site structures</p><p>Keeping of office records</p><p>Administrative role</p><p>Machine maintenance (Water Pump) maintenance.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">By performing the above\r\nstated roles to the best of my knowledge. I fully dedicate myself to plant and\r\nmaintain as many trees as possible towards achieving the mission of the company<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Manual cleaning in the compartments including Neem</p>', '<p>Cleaning maintenance in the compartment for effective tree counting process and pruning</p>', '<p>Covid cases which made life very difficult</p>', '<p>Cases of dismissal of workers to be replaced immediately for effective flow of work.</p><p>Provision of good and quality tools like pangas.</p>', '2021-11-10 07:11:40', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(50, 108, 47, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;1. Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">2. Carrying out all plantation maintenance activities such\r\nas pruning according to the approved plans.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">3. Provide accurate reports for assigned activities on daily\r\nbasis.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences in the\r\nplantation.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">5. Assist in operational activities as assigned by the\r\nsupervisor.<o:p></o:p></p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>By planting trees as planned by organization management and ensure they survive. Maintaining all trees planted by BGF by carrying out all assigned silvicultural practices.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Training on mechanical pruning; many trees pruned this year and the whole plantation is nearly completed. Plantation has been cleaned and sparkly presentable.</p>', '<p>Provision of transport means to and from areas of assignment in the plantation.</p><p>Increment of wages and award of bonuses to jobs done well.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Risks imposed by wildlife in the plantation eg Buffalo, snakes etc.</p><p>Timely replacement of overall, I operated with one overall thus cleaning it became challenge.</p>', '<p>All requirements for the job should be made available thus aid achievement of targets and quality objectives.</p>', '2021-11-10 07:41:59', '2022-05-20 16:23:46');
