(51, 62, 52, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Carry out all plantation maintenance\r\nactivities such as pruning, cleaning according to the approved plans.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provide accurate reports for\r\nassigned activities on daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Always achieve assigned task â€˜task\r\nratesâ€™<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communicate immediately on the\r\noccurrence in the plantation<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Assist in operational activities as\r\nassigned by the supervisor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Construction of site structures. E.g Toilet Constructions, PPE Store.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">By performing the above\r\nstated roles to the best of my knowledge. I fully dedicate myself to plant and\r\nmaintain as many trees as possible towards achieving the mission of the company<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Manual Cleaning/ Pruning</p>', '<p>Provision of Maintenance equipments like Pangas</p>', '<p>Covid 19 outbreak which made us fear to loss the job but God has been faithful</p>', '<p>Provision of required tools immediately without waiting for a longer period</p>', '2021-11-10 08:15:25', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(56, 32, 50, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\">Internally: <o:p></o:p></span></i></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To ensure that employees are aware of changes and projects within\r\n     the company.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To distribute executive messages, prepare presentations and\r\n     internal memos, and conduct meetings to share information.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To develop print materials and branding strategies for employee use.\r\n     <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To provide communications coaching for employees.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><i><span lang=\"EN-US\">Externally:<o:p></o:p></span></i></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><ul style=\"margin-top:0in\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To represent Better Globe Forestry Ltd. to stakeholders, interested\r\n     parties, and the public. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To serve as the company spokesperson to the media and the general\r\n     public. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To develop and distribute materials that may explain or convey the\r\n     company\'s policies or position on issues.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To handle public relations, information output, press releases and\r\n     media requests, social media, and/or advertising efforts. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To issue press releases, arrange interviews, and compile press\r\n     kits.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">To carry out any other broad communications-related functions as\r\n     the need arises. <br>\r\n     <!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>\r\n     <!--[endif]--><o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>Plan Better Globe AS and other visitors, visit in Kenya.</p><p>Day-to-day follow-up on vertical and horizontal communication throughout the company.</p><p>site visit related to permanent and continuous improvement of Communication.</p>', '<p>Fast and efficient communications at all levels of the company are key to keeping BGF focused on the vision through the well-understood performance of its mission.</p>', 'All management team members are now aware of issues that need to be addressed in matters of communication and are actively doing so with their subordinates.', '<p>More site visits, more interactions with staff at all levels, and more presence in the events related to the company.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Resistance to change especially in the implementation of new systems and tools.</p>', '<p>Support of ICT in the creation of supporting APPs.<br></p>', '2021-11-10 08:55:47', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(58, 23, 55, '<p>1. Ensure safety of company property and site safety.</p><p>2. Ensure welfare of staff at the site.</p><p>3. Ensure proper recording keeping of all that enters and goes out of the site.</p>', '<p>Secondary device handler.</p>', 'As security of Dokolo site, I must be honest and dedicated to my job. Also, follow all company policies so as not to go against company objectives, vision and mission.', '<p>No company properties have been lost this year</p>', '<p>1. Team work</p><p>2. Accord respect to supervisors</p>', '<p>Not having some PPEs like gumboots for security personnel.</p>', '<p>Management should purchase for security a mobile phone and load with airtime for easier communication.</p>', '2021-11-10 09:05:04', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
