(62, 7, 48, '<p>1 working according to plan</p><p>2 check 4 farmers a day meaning 20 farmers in a week</p><p>3 reporting everyday on the farms checked based on the approved template</p><p>4 check and take correct farmer detail.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;I&nbsp; help farmers sometimes to smear cow dung on trees to prevent animal damage and this will increase survive.</p>', '<p>To ensure that farmers plant as many trees as possible and ensure they survive</p><p><br></p>', '<p>working as a team in a given location and we finish verification of that area in time</p><p>most farmers have implemented income generating activity hence improvement in living standard</p>', '<p>Expansion on trainings of new ideas especially on animal husbandry</p><p>salary increment&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1 old age-some farmers are old and they think they will die before the completion of the contract</p><p>2 Hostility-some farmers are just hostile without valid reasons</p><p>3 gender-men sometimes make tough decisions to their wifes about the program and this makes their spouses to abandon.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>There is need for additional fuel since some areas we cover are very far that 7litres is not enough.</p>', '2021-11-10 09:50:23', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(63, 66, 59, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Carry out all plantation maintenance\r\nactivities such as pruning, cleaning according to the approved plans.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provide accurate reports for\r\nassigned activities on daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Always achieve assigned task â€˜task\r\nratesâ€™<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communicate immediately on the\r\noccurrence in the plantation<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Assist in operational activities as\r\nassigned by the supervisor.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Maintenance of mechanical tools</p><p>Building of site structure</p><p>Digging of the toilet</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">By performing the above\r\nstated roles to the best of my knowledge. I fully dedicate myself to plant and\r\nmaintain as many trees as possible towards achieving the mission of the company<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Unity by workers.</p>', '<p>Refresher trainings on the activities. More so First Aid training</p>', '<p>High cost of living</p>', '<p>Training of PMS in handling motorbikes to develop skills in various activities.</p>', '2021-11-10 10:54:21', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(64, 19, 58, '<p>Contract farmers according to a approve plan and policies</p><p>Ensure all contracted farmers received seedlings</p><p>Train all farmers adequately according to the plan</p><p>Continuously monitor farmers according to the plan</p><p>Continuously give feedback and proposals for improvement</p><p>Ensure timely and correct reporting/ communication at all levels&nbsp;</p><p>Maintain an excellent report with stakeholders/partners</p><p>Do any other task as assigned by your supervisor</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Contracting&nbsp; farmers and giving them seedlings&nbsp;</p>', '<p>According to my relation to the vision and mission to the company, I have contracted farmers and given them seedlings, timely provision of report.</p>', '<p>Farmer verification</p>', '<p>Proper planning&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Poor communication both horizontal and vertical</p>', '<p>Following the work instructions as given&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 11:24:59', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(65, 27, 54, '<p>1.Contract farmers according to approved plans and policies.&nbsp;</p><p>2.Ensure all contracted farmers receive seedlings, plants and they survive.&nbsp;</p><p>3.Ensure continuous monitoring and obtaining correct data that relates to the programme.&nbsp;</p><p>4.Ensure timely and correct reporting and communication at all levels.</p>', '<p>Participate in the radio talk shows&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Through taking up tasks of recruiting the right farmers, training and ensuring that they plant and have 100% survival,doing follow up to make sure we have good quality trees hence good quality timbers at the end of the cycle.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The major achievement this year has been coming up with correct tree survival and individual farmer informations.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Good communication channels/timely feedbacks.</p><p>- Availability of resources required to carry out field operations.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>- Communication gaps, relay of information from top to bottom and vice versa,especially on field activities.&nbsp;</p><p>- Scarcity and condition of field resources example conditions of motorbike and timing of service, quality of PPEs.</p>', '<p>Capacity building, quality field resources, and good communication channels.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 11:28:22', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(66, 20, 53, '<p>. contract farmers according to approved plans and policies</p><p>. ensure all contracted farmers receive seedlings, plant them and they survive</p><p>. train all farmers adequately and according to plan</p>', '<p>. attending working party meetings</p><p>. attending radio talkshows</p><p>. attending health and safety meetings</p><p>. conflict resolution</p>', '<p>I ensure that i properly mobilise, sensitise, recruit, group farmers, distribute seedlings to them, making follow ups&nbsp; and also train them on proper tree management that can help them in getting good money and hence get out of poverty</p>', '<p>farm verification</p>', '<p>Good communication</p><p>proper planning</p><p>proper time management</p>', '<p>communication gap especially lack of proper feedback from my bosses especially on health</p>', '<p>trainings</p><p>exposures</p><p>enough quality resources especially good tablet with enough capacity</p>', '2021-11-10 11:34:25', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(67, 9, 51, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Immediate follow up and\r\nchecks on farms to verify forestry tree counts</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Raise corrective action requests and do follow up on implementation</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Reporting findings on a weekly basis</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Special inquiries as\r\nrequested by management</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Checking farms and\r\nactivities implemented by farmers as planned to achieve high survival of trees\r\nhence planting as many trees as people in the planet.</span><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">I have gotten to know,\r\nvisit and interact with the greater farmers program which has increased my\r\nunderstanding.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">I have adjusted well to the changes in roles and strategies</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Rely on more physical visits than phone calls because its the only way to get correct information</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Shorter motorbike services or new motorbikes to avoid work dragging because of repairs- Sometimes we incur costs to save perfomance.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Increase M&amp;E officers in the ground</span></p><p><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">I need more airtime to call farmers. Last month I was deducted 3,000 Kshs from my salary</span><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;need more airtime to call farmers.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">A tablet is hard to work with when reporting. A computer works better and faster.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Motorbike breakdowns during work hence wasting time to repair</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Inaccessible roads in 7 Forks area</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Language barrier. I cannot speak the local language</span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The company should\r\nnot change employees to other roles without finding a replacement first.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '2021-11-10 11:34:57', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(68, 21, 56, '<p>Contract farmers according to approved plans and policies, ensure all contracted farmers receive&nbsp; seedlings, plant and that they survive,&nbsp; train all farmers adequately&nbsp; according to plan, continuously&nbsp; monitor his/ her farmers according to plan to obtain correct data related to program,&nbsp; continuously give feedback&nbsp; and proposal for improvement in their domain, ensure correct reporting and do any other tasks as it may be given from time to time buy supervisor.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Planting trees and they survive&nbsp;</p>', '<p>As employee I have to sensitized farmers on the project aim, objectives,&nbsp; goal and vision,&nbsp; contracting farmers,&nbsp; giving seedlings to contracted farmers for planting and ensure that they survive&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Reporting correct data for tree counting farmer information&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Proper planning and proper communication&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Poor planning and poor communication&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Proper planning and correct communication&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 11:36:12', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
