(70, 16, 62, '<p>- Training farmers on group dynamics&nbsp;</p><p>-Activate dormant groups&nbsp;</p><p>-Ensuring contracted farmers are part of the group</p><p>-Mobilize, train and check/ visit five groups per week</p>', '<p>Training groups on&nbsp; nursery management and production ( Setelitte nursery)</p>', '<p>Tree planting with the farmers aimed at increasing production of food crops which intern reduce poverty.&nbsp;</p>', 'Group formation and reactivation, proud of Verification&nbsp; after learning the mistakes that were Timdone previously and correcting them by providing accurate&nbsp; information.&nbsp;', '<p>Training&nbsp; farmers&nbsp; and motivation&nbsp; through&nbsp; groups meeting by providing&nbsp; training&nbsp; allowances&nbsp;</p><p>Timely&nbsp; provision of the required&nbsp; tools such pruning&nbsp; saw</p>', '<p>Using the current motorbike that are not favoured by terrains&nbsp;</p><p>Using low quality PPE</p><p>Delayed repairs ( No supplier in Embu&nbsp; region)</p>', '<p>Introduction&nbsp; of settelite nurseries/ Holding nurseries especially during&nbsp; distribution&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 11:59:02', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
(71, 110, 61, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">1. &nbsp;Always achieve assigned task \'task rates\'<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">2. Carrying out all plantation maintenance activities such\r\nas pruning according to the approved plans.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">3. Provide accurate reports for assigned activities on daily\r\nbasis.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences in the\r\nplantation.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">5. Assist in operational activities as assigned by the\r\nsupervisor.<o:p></o:p></p>', '<p>Motorized pruning sow operation.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>By Planting trees and maintain them till maturity.</p><p>By condemning all kinds of corruption at site level hence reduction unnecessary loss of resources and money which intern used to employ more workers.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Cleaning and pruning of the plantation. Nearly whole plantation pruned and cleaned. the plantation look presentable.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Provision of means of transport to and from assigned areas.</p><p>Provision of efficient tools per activities.</p>', '<p>Interference by wild animals during job.</p><p>Long walking distance to and from areas of assignment.</p>', '<p>Timely availability of tools and other requirements for job to be done at correct time.</p>', '2021-11-10 11:59:37', '2022-05-20 16:23:46');
