(83, 111, 74, '<p>1. Carry out all the maintenance activities ( pruning, tree counting, cleaning, weeding, plantation protection etc) according to the approved plan.</p><p>2. Carry out any other activity as required by the forest technician or the forester.</p><p>3. Provide accurate report for all the activities done daily.</p><p>4. Communicate immediately on the occurrences within the plantation.</p><p>5. Always achieve assigned task \'task rate\'</p><p>6. Provide any operational assistance as requested by the supervisor.</p><p>7. Contribute to team by accomplishing related resiults as needed.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Through carrying out plantation maintainance activities helps in achieving company mission on planting and maintaining many trees as people on earth this, in other hand leads to creation of employment opportunities which is key in poverty reduction. By providing accurate and correct reports on occurrences in the plantation assist eradication corruption.</p>', '<p>1. Cleaning and pruning of larger part of the plantation.</p><p>2. Getting correct figures of tree stock in Nyongoro.</p><p>3. Mechanization of pruning activity.</p>', '<p>For current performance, the company to facilitate by implementing salary increament and for future, the company needs to train people on most mechanical operation on site to increase reliability.</p>', '<p>Presence of wild animals in the plantation thus making workers uneasy while working.</p>', '<p>Company to provide means of transport to workers from site to the plantation.</p>', '2021-11-11 06:53:21', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
