GB;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">Provide a strong link between the sites and the head office by\r\ncontinuous, accurate and timely communication.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\r\nmargin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list .25in .5in\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-weight:\r\nbold\">Continuously track the effectiveness of trainings with the help of the\r\nmonitoring and evaluation team and immediately intervene with the recommended\r\ncorrective actions where need be.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Representing the company in any work related workshops and events</p>', '<p>I plant tree with trained farmers in active groups and make sure they survive through constant trainings and monitoring, follow ups. I do ensure farmers are involved in income generating activities to improve their livelihoods</p>', '<p>The verification exercise has been a great achievement. The data quality has improved, knowing our farmers geographical location has been a great thing also not forgetting the improved correct tree stock</p>', '<ol><li>1.In any project, exposure and learning from others doing what we are doing is a good thing which has not been there and if put in place it will be a good thing</li><li>2. More time to allocated in sites visits and training. this way, we get to be close and know more about the project we are running and be able to bridge gaps which are there</li><li><br></li></ol><p><br></p>', '<p>Covid-19 pandemic has forced to supervise the project virtually given this a project which actually needs constant field visits for trainings, monitoring and getting to be close to your team and to know them.</p>', '<p>1. leadership trainings should be done more often. Dokolo Site has not yet been trained and I believe it should be to all sites. This usually a eye open to most staffs</p><p>2. Personally am limited when it comes to calls to Sites especially Uganda because of airtime overuse. This should be relooked and addressed</p>', '2021-11-11 14:42:27', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(91, 2, 60, '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Management, support and troubleshooting of a BGF multi-user computing environment through Ticketing system</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Maintenance of the company\'s computer infrastructure.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Installing, configuring, monitoring and maintaining computer hardware, software, systems, networks, printers and scanners</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Managing hardware, software, networking and solving problems.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Providing technical support\r\nacross the company (this may be in person or over the phone</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">Testing of new applications after their configuration.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Carry out any other duties\r\nas may be assigned</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-image: initial; padding: 0in;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">to you from time to time by\r\nthe management</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p><p><br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Contact with\r\nExternal suppliers, eg Capture solutions, JTL</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;\">As a support department that allows other departments in fulfilling the Vision and mission of the Company</span><br></p>', '<ul><li style=\"border: none; --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; padding: 0in;\">1. Successful&nbsp; implementation&nbsp; of the in house created BGF Apps. (Preventative Maintenance app., Survey App., CAR system and Miti Magazine.)</li><li style=\"border: none; --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; padding: 0in;\">2. Solve all the synchronisation issues related to the Farmers Program.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"border: none; --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; padding: 0in;\">3. Introduction of&nbsp; Time Capture System for clocking in/out with embedded devices which now in final stages of implementation. This saves time for staff to clock in/out.</li></ul>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">To\r\nhave a course in Hardware Maintenance</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">System\r\nimplementation, Staff being resistance to the introduction of new applications.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">- To complete my BBA with IT (26 modules out of 56 remaining). Issue is financial.&nbsp;<br>- To follow short courses to stay in line with the current\r\nTechnology trends.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '2021-11-12 07:39:42', '2022-05-20 16:21:38'),
(92, 77, 82, '<p>1.Ensuring that there is cleared land available for tree planting.</p><p>2.Ensuring that all heavy equipment are in working condition.<br></p>', '<p>N/A<br></p>', '<p>Through my role ensuring that I have cleared enough land that will accommodate as many trees as there are people.<br></p>', '<p>1. Construction of the Electric fence.</p><p>2. Having been awarded a bonus.<br></p>', '<p>1. Allocation of a motorbike to commute to work from Site and back.<br></p>', '<p>1. Attacks from Squatters.<br></p>', '<p>1. To take me for a refresher course in CATs.<br></p>', '2021-11-12 09:26:07', '2022-05-20 16:23:43');
