nd horizontal: Staff at all levels are not always aware of the particular roles within the IT Department<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Corona affected seminars during the period of 2020/2021</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Technology changes so fast and learning becomes too intense</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">improved communications between IT and the staff:- refer to Point c in NO 4</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">ICT to have a budget in training and seminars</span></p>', '2021-11-12 12:25:56', '2022-05-20 16:19:37'),
(96, 105, 84, '<p>1. Farm tractor driving and ensuring that the tractor it is well taken care off in terms of cleanliness.</p><p>2.Assisting in carrying out Forestry and Maintenance Operations e.g. Mechanical Cleaning, Pitting, Seedling Transport, Chemical Spraying, Mechanical Watering.</p>', '<p>N/A<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Trough my work I am able to take care and provide for my family.</p><p>Mission: By actively carrying out Forestry operations in ensuring trees are planted and they survive.<br></p>', '<p>1.&nbsp; Being able to compete the mechanical cleaning cycle by September 2021.</p><p>2. Prompt repairs in-cases of minor breakdown.<br></p>', '<p>1. Fast track the construction of the company kitchen and the food program.</p>', '<p>1. Delayed supplies of some spare parts from suppliers. Eg. Steering Cylinder for KTCB 563N.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '2021-11-13 07:56:16', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(97, 124, 85, '<p>1. Drive the tractor with due care and undertake the various field activities as assigned.</p><p>2.Inspect the tractor before and after the job, and to record any defects found.</p><p>3.Perform basic preventive maintenance tasks, e.g adding oil and fuel, radiator fluid and performing minor repairs.</p><p>4.Couple or uncouple trailer, auger by changing trailer jack positions.</p><p>5.Checking the tractor to ensure that mechanical, safety and emergency equipment is in good working order.</p><p>6.Maintain logs of working hours and reports of work done.</p>7.Ensure that all relevant Health &amp; Safety measures are adhered to while working with the tractor.', '<p>1. I\'m good in Motorbike repairs.</p>', '<p>Vision: By working hard and getting paid to be able&nbsp; to provide for my family.<br></p>Mission: By carrying out operation activities, e.g Brush Cutting<br>', '<p>1.Learning how to install the electric fence which I initially did not know.<br></p>', '<p>1. Prompt repairs of major tractor breakdowns.<br></p>', '<p>None<br></p>', '<p>None<br></p>', '2021-11-15 06:53:53', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(98, 90, 86, '<p>1.Performing maintenance and minor repairs of company site structures,</p><p>2,Perform repairs on company appliances ,various machines ,and equipment.</p><p>3.Detect and report the need for major repairs.</p><p>4.Perform welding duties.</p><p>5.Assist in setting up storage and other facilities.</p><p>6.Provide painting services.</p><p>7.Maintenance and supervision of electric fence</p>', '<p>NSTD</p>', '<p>Ensure that always machine are working and no breakdown in such way the company will be able to plant as many trees as planned at any given time</p>', '<p>By constructing PPE store , new ladies toilet and to gained knowledge on how to install the electric fence</p>', '<p>To be taken to a recognized institution for refresher course in welding and on the digital in use.</p>', '<p>Delays in approval of the required materials due to consultations</p>', '<p>To train more&nbsp; people to get knowledge on different&nbsp; activities</p>', '2021-11-15 08:54:24', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
