(102, 116, 89, '<p>1. Identify faults on farm tractors and report.</p><p>2. Assist the mechanic in doing tractor repairs on site.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">3. Drive the tractor with due care and undertake the various field activities as assigned.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">4. Inspect the tractor before and after the job, and to record any defects found.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">5. Perform basic preventive maintenance tasks, e.g adding oil and fuel, radiator fluid and performing minor repairs.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">4. Couple or uncouple trailer, auger by changing trailer jack positions.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">5. Checking the tractor to ensure that mechanical, safety and emergency equipment is in good working order.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-width: 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin: 0px 0px 1rem; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">6. Maintain logs of working hours and reports of work done.</p><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;\">7. Ensure that all relevant Health &amp; Safety measures are adhered to while working with the tractor.</span>', '<p>1. Electric Wiring: E.g. Repairs of Tractor starters.</p><p>2. Diagnosis of tractor fault on the wiring system.</p><p>3. Alternator repairs.<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through my employment I am able to provide for my family and my dependents. This act has uplifted my family and I from poverty. <br></p><p>Mission: By exceeding my targets in allocated assignment to enable the company operations run smoothly in achieving their goal.<br></p>', '<p>1. Being part of the team that repaired KTCB 530T that had a valve seal malfunction.<br></p><p>2.Being part of the team that worked on repairing Tractor 154X\'s clutch malfunction.</p><p>3. Taking part in repairing Tractor KTCB 563N that had a lift pump issue and a faulty instrument panel.</p>', '<p>1. Availability of the right tools for handling major repairs on site. </p><p>2. Mechanic sections to be provided with a motorbike/vehicle to save on time and ease movement while handling breakdowns onsite.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '2021-11-16 09:16:42', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
(103, 117, 16, '<p>1.In-charge of maintenance of all mechanized equipment, tools and tools.</p><p>2. Examination of tractor, pick-ups and CATS.</p><p>3.Perform repairs and replacements of worn out or defective parts and take note of machine service hours.</p><p>4.Perform scheduled maintenance works which includes and not limited to oil change, tune-ups, wheel balancing, and pressure checks.</p><p>5. Determine the tools and equipment required for the job.</p><p>6. Adhere to all health and safety procedures.<br></p>', '<p>N/A<br></p>', '<p>Through my work as a mechanic, I am able to ensure that the machines are\r\n up and running to facilitate forestry operations, E.g. Bush clearing, \r\nPitting, Chemical spraying etc, and in return create job for the \r\nneighboring community who are normally contracted to work in the farm alleviating them from Poverty . \r\nAdditionally, By having working machine\'s with available land, The \r\ncompany is able&nbsp; to produce and plant seedlings in realization of its \r\nmission of planting as many trees as there are people.</p>', '<p>1. Training all&nbsp; the drivers on routine maintenance of the tractors.<br></p><p>2. Stocking service parts early enough prior to the due date.<br></p><p>3.Ability to handle some repairs without over reliance on key suppliers. E.g. For Tractor repairs.<br></p>', '<p>1. Provision of means of transport.</p><p>2. Provision of Air Time.</p><p>3. Trainings.</p><p>4. A workshop inclusive of all the required accessories.<br></p>', '<p>1. Mobility. Moving from one place to the next when handling multiple repairs on site.</p><p>2. Communication. Lack of enough communication resources e.g. Airtime, has increased the channel of message transfer from drivers &amp; operators.<br></p>', 'None.', '2021-11-17 05:44:25', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
(104, 31, 90, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">To monitor conformance to set policies, procedures and Work\r\nInstructions for continuous improvement towards quality achievement of the company mission</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">To monitor and report on approved plans and activities.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">GIS Mapping for reporting purposes</p>', '<p>To help management to achieve the mission by immediate monitoring and reporting of approved plans and activities for informed decision making and continuous improvement</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Made GIS a primary tool for decision making and reporting<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Have been guiding in development of different tools by ICT\r\nand M&amp;E<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Promoted use of cloud storage for back up and document\r\naccess and now one drive is the main storage used.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Took up innovation using digital data collection tools that\r\nare paperless for M&amp;E surveys.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">Carried out M&amp;E in more organized way that it is effective for continuous improvement.</p>', '<p>Availing all approved reference documents in time</p><p>To improve reporting and presentation of reports for effective decisions.</p><p>A dedicated MEO for Kiambere and Dokolo site</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Lack of full time M&amp;E in Dokolo site</span><br></p><p>Lack Acceptance and understanding the role of M&amp;E by staff</p>', '<p>Having MEO in Dokolo and Kiambere</p><p>Continuous support by management</p>', '2021-11-17 09:57:38', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(105, 41, 91, '<p>1. Posting of financial transactions in the accounting system</p><p>2. Procurement responsibilities</p><p>3. Accounts reconciliation</p><p>4. Stock management</p><p>5.Coordination of Uganda service providers</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>N/A</p>', '<p>Provision of accurate information for decision making</p><p>Accountability for funds received for planting trees.</p>', '<p>Learning to effectively use Sage</p>', '<p>Good communication amongst team members.</p>', '<p>Effects of COVID19</p>', '<p>Training in tax related Areas</p>', '2021-11-17 12:12:50', '2022-05-20 16:23:40'),
(106, 38, 73, '<p>1.Ensure machines, equipments and tools are in good and working condition at all times.</p><p>2. Ensure smooth operations within the company.</p><p>3.Creat and maintain good relations with our suppliers.</p><p>4 Implementation of approved policies, procedures and work instructions of operations all the sites.</p><p>5.Stock management of operational stock.</p><p>6. Ensure timely purchases .&nbsp;</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>By ensuring operations are done according to approved procedures without corruption and supporting all the departments to achieve the vision and mission of the company.</p>', '<p>1.Minimized breakdown of the motorbikes after introducing the quarterly servicing by Toyota Kenya.</p><p>2. Successful coordinated installation of the 1st phase of Electric fence.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Having stable leadership in Kiambere site</p><p>2. Improved&nbsp; upwards consultations and communication in all departments.</p>', '<p>1.Delays from suppliers in delivering required supplies.</p>', '<p>1.Requests done to Operations to be done on time to give Operations enough time to work on them.</p>', '2021-11-18 07:47:42', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(107, 30, 92, '<p>By ensuring that&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">1. Ensuring payments are done correctly and on time</span><br></p><p>2. Timely processing of accounts documents&nbsp;</p><p>3. Reconciliations in accounts</p><p>4. Custodian of accounts documents</p><p>5. Correct postings</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Handling clocking devices at the Head Office</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">By ensuring that there is a good relation with the suppliers and the temporary workers.</span><br></p><p>Ensuring there is proper accountability of funds received for planting trees.</p>', 'Having up to date correct reports', '<p>Support from other departments, by having complete information in the requests.</p>', 'Having to return back documents that are not complete or wrongly filled', '<p>Adequate training of other staffs on accounting documents and how they should be filled&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-18 12:11:47', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(108, 34, 93, '<p>1.Responsible for the day-to-day management of the HR Department inclusive of Payroll, implementation of policies, and ensuring that staff are motivated and have a good working environment.</p><p>2.Ensure health and safety of all employees</p><p>3.Followup on the yearly training schedule for all departments.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>80% of the success of the company depends on people. If we have the right people in all departments with the right attitude then, we shall be able to achieve the vision and the mission of the company.</p>', '<p>1.The staff are motivated to do the job and we have a good working environment</p><p>2.Site visits and interaction with staff has made them freely express themselves&nbsp;</p><p>3.The leadership training we have had for different categories of staff have led to understanding what is expected of them</p><p>4.The company has provided all the required equipment for the staff to be able to do the job</p>', '<p>1.HR staff on sites</p><p>2.An induction schedule for new staff for sites</p><p>3.More site visits</p><p>4.Increased awareness on HR policies and procedures by the site responsibles</p><p>5.We have a all-staff meeting at the head office where we can interact and discuss different policies, procedures and company vision and mission</p><p>6.Staff taking responsibility for their job</p>', '<p>1.Lack of interest by staff to take responsibility</p><p>2.Staff turnover</p><p>3.Resistance to change</p>', '<p>1.Increased support by other departments</p>', '2021-11-18 12:49:20', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(109, 129, NULL, '<p>1.To ensure that the office and whole compound is clean</p><p>2.To ensure staff have tea twice per day</p><p>3.Arranging office furniture</p>', '<p>NONE</p>', '<p>Your job entails dealing with staff welfare and this helps to motivate staff to perform the expected duties.</p>', '<p>I have managed to be at work on time&nbsp; to ensure I start my duties early enough</p>', '<p>1.Working as a team with the operations department</p>', '<p>1. Asking for housekeeping items and they are delayed e.g milk&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1.To have a locker where I can put and manage some housekeeping items which are mismanaged eg tissue and sugar</p>', '2021-11-26 12:25:22', '2021-11-26 12:25:22'),
(110, 129, 94, '<p>1.To ensure that the office and whole compound is clean</p><p>2.To ensure staff have tea twice per day</p><p>3.Arranging office furniture</p>', '<p>NONE</p>', '<p>Your job entails dealing with staff welfare and this helps to motivate staff to perform the expected duties.</p>', '<p>I have managed to be at work on time&nbsp; to ensure I start my duties early enough</p>', '<p>1.Working as a team with the operations department</p>', '<p>1. Asking for housekeeping items and they are delayed e.g milk&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1.To have a locker where I can put and manage some housekeeping items which are mismanaged eg tissue and sugar</p>', '2021-11-26 13:58:28', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(111, 138, 98, '<p>Conduct inventory of Kiambere plantation.</p><p>Conduct inventory of some selected farms.</p>', '<p>Help the forest technician in Tree measurement.&nbsp;</p><p>Help in clocking in and out of the workers.</p>', '<p>Through employment and providing correct data without any cook ups,&nbsp; it gets rid of corruption and eradicate poverty. Hence the company achieves its goal and I my personal goals.</p>', '<p>Delivering the required task prior to the deadline.</p>', '<p>This exercise should be done in dry season because rain affects the gadgets and gps accuracy.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Weather problems.</p><p>Gps accuracy was affected.&nbsp;</p><p>The electronic gadgets can\'t work with rain<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">s.</span></p>', '<p>The fallen trees in the plantation should maybe be collected and sold as timber cause some are rotting in the field.</p>', '2022-01-06 12:05:48', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(112, 139, 97, '<p>1. Taking and recording of Tree measurements of dbh, height and Crown diameter of selected sample plots in every compartment in Kiambere plantation.</p><p>2. Recording of GPS coordinates of every Tree measured in UTM format.</p><p>3. Reporting of the work progress to the supervisor.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Measurements of dbh and height of selected trees that had been measured previously for purposes of monitoring their growth rate over a specified period of time ( 1 year interval between subsequent Measurements. )</p>', '<p>1. Vision; the company targets to eradicate poverty and corruption in Africa, which in my view is through indiscriminate employment and remuneration of the company\'s employees, in addition to building capacity for them through community startup projects such as the savings society (FSA microcredit) established at Seven Forks, which enables them to save and acquire loans<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">. Corruption is eradicated through prohibition of bribes anywhere within the company transactions, tenders and recruitment of casuals.</span></p><p>2. Mission; the company targets to plant as many trees as there are people on this planet, and be able to sustainably finance its vision, and this is being achieved through mass establishment and management of plantations across East Africa, with focus being on the drylands of Kenya, Uganda and Tanzania.</p>', '<p>1. Earning the internship program at BETTER GLOBE FORESTRY&nbsp;</p><p>2. Performing the duties assigned by the management with minimum supervision and being able to beat the targets set for the assignments.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Fast and efficient relaying of information and feedback with respect to the assignment at the exact time of need.</p>', '<p>1. Adverse weather conditions. The long rains that started in the month of December affected the GPS accuracy and hindered the usage of gadgets such as phones and the tablets while working.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. Provision of extra working tools and gadgets incase of failure of the ones in use.</p><p>2. Timely feedback on issues raised.</p>', '2022-01-06 12:47:30', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(114, 140, 100, '<p>1. To verify that we have the correct number of trees as reported by forestry</p><p>2.To raise Corrective Action requests against non-conformances</p><p>3.To follow up corrective action requestsin Dokolo site for implementation</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>To ensure that we have the correct number of trees planted</p>', '<p>Managed to visist different farmers in different locations as tasked by supervisor</p>', '<p>Good working relationship</p><p>To raise clear corrective action requests</p><p>Better communication with my supervisor</p><p>Improving IT literacy.</p>', '<p>Difficult to meet farmers whose locations have been entered wrongly</p><p>Mechanical breakdown of the bike in the field are always a challenge</p><p>Some farmers demand funds from M&amp;E</p><p>IT application is a challenge</p>', '<p>Regular communication with my supervisor</p><p>Put effort into imroving computer literacy</p>', '2022-04-27 12:02:41', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(115, 73, 112, '<p>1) To protect company\'s property and staff by maintaining a safe and secure environment</p><p>2) Observe for signs of crime or disorder and investigate disturbances</p><p>3) Reporting in details all incidents in site</p><p>4) Adhere to company procedure and policies at all time</p><p>5) Monitor and control access at the nursery gate and around the perimeter.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>By maintaining safe and secure environment for the safety of company\'s properties and the planted seedlings survives.</p>', '<p>Training of guards on security etiquettes</p><p>1) Having parades every two weeks before security meetings</p><p>2) Putting on security uniforms accordingly</p>', '<p>Increment of salary</p>', '<p>1) During rainy season we get a challenge on reporting to work on time which affects the end month reports thereby resulting to deductions</p>', '<p>1) A temporary structures for protection during rainy seasons in the field.</p><p>2) Purchasing of quality PPEs especially raincoat.</p>', '2022-11-07 15:58:58', '2022-11-07 15:58:58'),
(116, 141, 119, '<p>Capacity building for the managers on FSC.</p><p>Internal assessment of BGF operations against FSC standards.</p><p>Understand the way the company works internally and externally within FSC limits.</p><p>Raise non conformances internally for non compliances against FSC Interim National Standard of Kenya.</p><ul><li><br></li></ul>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>By guiding the company towards FSC certification, I will be contributing to economic viability by attracting more investors through the certification, social benefits by making sure community rights are respected and lastly environmental sustainability through conservation. Also help the company further in eradication of poverty and corruption by ensuring managers are aware of FSC criteria against corruption.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Mastering FSC standards and BGF operations and how to incorporate FSC into BGF.</p><p>Understanding the importance of policies and the need to follow them.</p>', '<p>continuous guidance from my supervisor.</p>', 'Making sure everyone understood what FSC is. This is because FSC was perceived to be a whole new thing and adopting to change can be difficult.', '<p>purchase of a new laptop.</p><p>Getting the official FSC training from Soil Association as it covers broader aspects of FSC</p>', '2022-11-08 11:01:18', '2022-11-08 11:01:18'),
(117, 123, 118, '<p>1.Supervising Tractor Drivers, Site Mechanic, Security Guards &amp; Heavy Equipment Operators on site.</p><p>2.Project management at Site Level.</p><p>3.Overseeing the Implementation of approved company policies and procedures.</p><p>4. Site Tasks Planning and Implementation.</p>5. Operational Stock Management on Site.<br><p></p><p>6.Implementation, monitoring and measuring of approved procedures and work instructions on site.</p><p>7.Establishing and follow up of operational budget on site.</p><p>8.Maintenance of plant machinery.</p><p>9.Follow up on the overall performance of the machines and ensuring that the machines are always at work.</p><p>10.In charge of operational purchases on site with strict adherence to approved procedures.</p><p>11.Daily follow up of operations onsite including issues related to the H&amp;S of workers.</p>12.Offer Logistics support to CSR&nbsp; activities related to BGF.', '<p>1.Drone Piloting.</p>2.GIS and Remote Sensing Analysis of the Forest Management Unit.<p></p>', '<p>Vision: By implementing approved company policies e.g. The Anti-Corruption and Bribery policy. </p><p>Mission: Ensure that the human workforce on site and the plant machinery\r\n are always in good state to perform their duties optimally of planting,\r\n maintaining and protecting trees.</p>', '<p>1.Heading the construction of the CAT Shed and Nursery fence.</p><p>2. Reporting zero accidents on the Job this year.<br></p>', '<p>1. Increased human workforce. e.g. An SLO.</p><p>2. Provision of a Pick-Up for movement of materials on site.<br></p>', '<p>1. Sickness. (Dengue Fever &amp; Bronchitis)<br></p>', '<p>1. Inter site visits.<br></p>', '2022-11-08 11:23:49', '2022-11-08 11:23:49'),
