(139, 38, 124, '<p>1.<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Ensure smooth operations within the company.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Ensure machines, equipments and tools are in good and working condition at all times.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Creat and maintain good relations with our suppliers.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Implementation of approved policies, procedures and work instructions of operations all the sites.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">5.</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Stock management of operational stock.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">6.</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Ensure timely purchases</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;.</span></p>', '<p>Clocking device handler&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. By facilitating Forestry department and all other departments on time to ensure more trees are planted and survive.</p><p>2. By ensuring we have zero tolerance to corruption in operations department</p>', '<p>1.Participating in budget formulation process.</p><p>2. Learning more on excel from day to day interaction with work teams..</p><p>3. Introducing a HO garage which is reliable, affordable, with good service and good customer service as well.</p><p>4.Organized security schedules which have improved coordination in the security team</p>', '<p>1.Have a fully responsible staff on operation tasks (SLO) in both Kiambere and 7F sites.</p><p>2. Continuous improvement in communication upwards, downwards and vertically.</p>', '<p>1. Logistics at HO- With the absence of a company driver running errands, doing purchases and deliveries to sites has not been easy.</p><p>2. Dealing with security team 