(140, 13, 140, '<p>1 Group training&nbsp;</p><p>2 Ensure all contracted farmers are in groups and have planted.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1 Office data compiling&nbsp;</p><p>2. Attended FSA AGM&nbsp;</p><p>3 Office internal training&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Training group on IGAS to be self reliant and planting trees and makes sure they survive.</p>', '<p>Given new territory&nbsp; with dormant&nbsp; groups and reactivated them to active groups.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1.Timely&nbsp; communication&nbsp;</p><p>2. Stick to plan no abrupt&nbsp; changes&nbsp; on planned activity.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1.lack of fuel to attend&nbsp; field activities.&nbsp;</p><p>2.low or no group&nbsp; turn out during campaign&nbsp; period.</p><p>3.farmers who have/had given up on programme&nbsp;</p><p>4.Group conflicts.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1 .focusing on the self motivated&nbsp; farmers willing&nbsp; to&nbsp; plant trees.</p><p>2.Group motivation.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-09 11:03:59', '2022-11-09 11:03:59'),
