(144, 15, 141, '<p>1. Group reactivation&nbsp;</p><p>2. Farmer\'s visitation daily and ensure sending of factual reports&nbsp;</p><p>3. Training farmers/ groups on IGAs, pruning,&nbsp; Protection and S&amp;WC and ensuring they are well implemented.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Internal training and preparing training modules for AAs to be used in the field as a guide&nbsp;</p>', '<ol><li>1. Training farmers/ Group on tree planting and ensure they survive&nbsp;</li><li>2. Training farmers/ groups on IGAs&nbsp; to improve their livelihoods and eleviate poverty&nbsp;</li><li>3. Training&nbsp; farmers/ groups on S&amp;WC to improve soil fertility and hence increase crop production&nbsp;</li></ol>', '<p>Working in new territories with majority of the group being dormant or inactive and hence reactivated some of them and doing well.</p>', '<p>1.Timely&nbsp; communication&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;2. Sticking to the plan</p><p>3. Timely provision of operational materials&nbsp; such fuel</p>', '<p>1. Fuel shortage&nbsp;</p><p>2. Lack of PPE</p><p>3. Delay in&nbsp; motorbike repairs</p><p>4.Difficulties in tracing farmers in new territories&nbsp;</p><p>5. Transferred from my territories to a new area without&nbsp; relocation&nbsp; fee</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Good communication&nbsp;</p><p>2. Giving or sending&nbsp; actual&nbsp; reports to my supervisor&nbsp;</p><p>3. Provision of group training allowances&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-09 13:14:59', '2022-11-09 13:14:59'),
(145, 17, 127, '<ul><li>1.To manage the site monitoring and evaluation officers</li><li>2.To Implement the monitoring and evaluation tasks and recommendations.</li><li>3.To plan and schedule tasks in CAR system for the M&amp;E teams..</li><li>4. To follow up on approved corrective action request for implementation.</li><li>5.To submit reports to management through the HOD.</li><li>6. To highlight areas for continuous improvement during reporting.</li></ul>', '<p>None</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">By ensuring compliance to company policies, procedures and work instruction and reporting to management for continuous improvement,&nbsp; we are able to maintain track on achieving the mission of the company.</span><br></p>', '<p>Ability to manage the activities of monitoring and evaluation both in head office and site effectively, a task that came with my promotion.</p>', '<p>Immediate feedback on M&amp;E end week report. This shall help to identify areas to improve.</p>', '<p>The promotion came with a challenge e.g team management but I took it as a learning ground for career growth and I no longer view it as challenge.</p>', '<p>To incorporate additional M&amp;E plan components to the existing yearly planning module in the CAR application.</p>', '2022-11-09 14:25:45', '2022-11-09 14:25:45');
