(146, 17, 127, '<ul><li>1.To manage the site monitoring and evaluation officers</li><li>2.To Implement the monitoring and evaluation tasks and recommendations.</li><li>3.To plan and schedule tasks in CAR system for the M&amp;E teams..</li><li>4. To follow up on approved corrective action request for implementation.</li><li>5.To submit reports to management through the HOD.</li><li>6. To highlight areas for continuous improvement during reporting.</li></ul>', '<p>None</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">By ensuring compliance to company policies, procedures and work instruction and reporting to management for continuous improvement,&nbsp; we are able to maintain track on achieving the mission of the company.</span><br></p>', '<p>Ability to manage the activities of monitoring and evaluation both in head office and site effectively, a task that came with my promotion.</p>', '<p>Immediate feedback on M&amp;E end week report. This shall help to identify areas to improve.</p>', '<p>The promotion came with a challenge e.g team management but I took it as a learning ground for career growth and I no longer view it as challenge.</p>', '<p>To incorporate additional M&amp;E plan components to the existing yearly planning module in the CAR application.</p>', '2022-11-09 14:25:47', '2022-11-09 14:25:47'),
(147, 95, 144, '<p>1. To carry out plantation maintenance silvicultural activities.</p><p>2. Providing daily results and plantation status report to the relevant supervisor.</p><p>3. Communicate any occurrence in the plantation.</p>', '<p>1. Ensure adherence to health and safety measures while at work.</p>', '<p>By diligently performing my responsibilities i contribute to trees survival which in one time will get to the company mission of having many trees as people on earth. again through working with the company i get my salary in a correct way as oppose to resorting to stealing which is a form of corruption, hence getting employment opportunity has lead to reduce poverty and corruption at large.</p>', '<p>1. Good PPE management.</p><p>2. Frequent trainings by the supervisors.</p><p>3. Good leadership and management of the company.</p>', '<p>1. Carry out continuous fresh and refresher trainings which are forestry related.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>1. Company to have staff motivational programs e.g team building</p><p>2. Salary review to reasonate with current economic situation.</p>', '2022-11-09 14:30:38', '2022-11-09 14:30:38'),
(148, 87, 147, '<p>Protecting all Company Property.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Vision: Through my work I am able to get wages hence alleviating poverty in my family.</p><p>Mission: Through my work as a security guard I protect the trees from damage ensuring maximum survival.</p>', '<p>Minimal game damage due to the electric fence.</p>', '<p>The HO management when they come for site visits to make an effort of meeting the DO and OCS to address illegal grazing issue.</p>', '<p>Illegal Grazing.</p>', '<p>Company to resume operations and have them do plantation maintenance.<br></p>', '2022-11-09 17:28:33', '2022-11-14 12:45:40'),
(149, 41, 128, '<div style=\"border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-image: initial; padding: 0in;\">\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .25pt;padding:0in;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 1. Posting of financial transactions in the\r\naccounting system<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem;\">2.\r\nProcurement responsibilities for Kampala office<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem;\">3.\r\nAccounts reconciliation<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem;\">4.\r\nStock management<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem;\">5.Coordination\r\nof Uganda service providers on accounts related matters<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .25pt;padding:0in;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 6. Postage of Miti Magazine both abroad and\r\nlocally<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"border:none;mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .25pt;padding:0in;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0in 0in 0in 0in\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 7. Making LPOs for Dokolo site<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<p>N/A</p>', '<p>Provision of accurate information for decision making</p><p>Accountability for funds received for tree planting</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Eliminating errors in posting data in sage and being up to\r\ndate in international financial reporting standards and incorporating Miti Magazine assignments in my schedule and still be able to deliver results on time.<o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Continuous research to counter the everchanging work requirements\r\nand technology<o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Slowing down of operations in the company, it would take long to accomplish a task.<o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Continuous and effective communication among team members<o:p></o:p></p>', '2022-11-09 17:36:37', '2022-11-09 17:36:37'),
(150, 112, 146, '<p>1. To carryout all plantation maintenance activities as per approved plans.</p><p>2. Report daily achieved field/plantation task results.</p><p>3. Communicate any occurrences within the plantation promptly.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Adherence to health and safety measures at all times while at work.</p>', '<p>By doing my responsibilities effectively, trees survival will increase that will contribute to financial and ecosystem benefits. This directly helps to eradicate poverty through expanded employment opportunities and sustainable implementation of the company programs.</p>', '<p>Company gave priority to retain its staff inspite of scaling down their operational activities.</p>', '<p>Invest more on machineries as the plantation is expanding.</p>', '<p>Working tools are not in good condition e.g pruning saw. Workers use more energy while using the current tools.</p>', '<p>Replacement of working tools atleast once a year.</p>', '2022-11-09 17:59:31', '2022-11-09 17:59:31'),
(151, 112, 146, '<p>1. To carryout all plantation maintenance activities as per approved plans.</p><p>2. Report daily achieved field/plantation task results.</p><p>3. Communicate any occurrences within the plantation promptly.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Adherence to health and safety measures at all times while at work.</p>', '<p>By doing my responsibilities effectively, trees survival will increase that will contribute to financial and ecosystem benefits. This directly helps to eradicate poverty through expanded employment opportunities and sustainable implementation of the company programs.</p>', '<p>Company gave priority to retain its staff inspite of scaling down their operational activities.</p>', '<p>Invest more on machineries as the plantation is expanding.</p>', '<p>Working tools are not in good condition e.g pruning saw. Workers use more energy while using the current tools.</p>', '<p>Replacement of working tools atleast once a year.</p>', '2022-11-09 18:00:26', '2022-11-09 18:00:26'),
(152, 7, 148, '<p>1.Group trainings.</p><p>2.Group reaction.&nbsp;</p><p>3.Group sensitisation.&nbsp;</p><p>4.Group formation and registration.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Office internal trainings.</p>', '<p>1.Training farmer groups on IGA to be self reliance.</p><p>2.Training farmers on soil and water conservation to improve crop production .</p><p>3.Training farmer group on tree planting and ensure they survive.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Most farmers in the active groups have implemented income generating activity hence improving their livelihood.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1.Expansion on trainings of new ideas expecially animal husbandry.</p><p>2.Frequent supply of fuel.</p>', '<p>1.Rural to Urban migration-Energitic youths who can plant trees have migrated to towns to seek for jobs.</p><p>2.Gender-sometimes men make tough decisions to their wives about the program hence make their spouses to abandon program.&nbsp;</p><p>3.Hostility-Some of our farmers are just hostile without tangible reasons.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1.Continuos supply of fuel .</p><p>2.proper communication.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-09 18:11:56', '2022-11-09 18:11:56'),
