(155, 11, 151, '<p>Group trainings</p><p>Group sensitization</p><p>Group formation and registration&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Office internal trainings</p>', '<p>Training farmer group on IGA to be self reliance .</p><p>Training farmer group on soil and water conservation to improve crop production&nbsp;</p><p>Training&nbsp; farmer group on tree planting and ensure they survive.</p>', '<p>Group reactivation&nbsp;</p><p>Group sensitization</p>', '<p>&nbsp;1. Frequent fuel supply</p><p>&nbsp;2. Proper planing and timely communication</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1 .Rural to urban migration _this results to poor group attendance since members migrate to urban areas to look for jobs.</p><p>2. Unsufficient fuel&nbsp;</p><p>3.Hostility from some members</p><p>4.Low group turnout&nbsp; during the political campaign&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1 .Frequent fuel supply&nbsp;</p><p>2.Proper communication&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-10 10:33:46', '2022-11-10 10:33:46'),
(156, 11, 151, '<p>Group trainings</p><p>Group sensitization</p><p>Group formation and registration&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Office internal trainings</p>', '<p>Training farmer group on IGA to be self reliance .</p><p>Training farmer group on soil and water conservation to improve crop production&nbsp;</p><p>Training&nbsp; farmer group on tree planting and ensure they survive.</p>', '<p>Group reactivation&nbsp;</p><p>Group sensitization</p>', '<p>&nbsp;1. Frequent fuel supply</p><p>&nbsp;2. Proper planing and timely communication</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1 .Rural to urban migration _this results to poor group attendance since members migrate to urban areas to look for jobs.</p><p>2. Unsufficient fuel&nbsp;</p><p>3.Hostility from some members</p><p>4.Low group turnout&nbsp; during the political campaign&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1 .Frequent fuel supply&nbsp;</p><p>2.Proper communication&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-10 10:33:49', '2022-11-10 10:33:49'),
(157, 22, 154, '<p>Ensuring the whole and company property are safe.</p><p>Ensuring no outsiders/intruders or thieves get into the site.</p><p>Daily patrolling of the site while on duty.</p><p>Reporting occurrences or any other security reports expected.</p><p>Ensuring that the clocking devices are safe and functional at all times.</p><p>Ensuring effective communication within the security team and the supervisors.</p><p>Exhibiting discipline, honesty and integrity.&nbsp;</p><p>Ensuring the rest of the team is working diligently.</p><p>Ensuring conflicts are properly managed especially with casual workers which does not affect the output of the work they do.</p>', '<p>Primary device handler.</p>', '<p>If all company property are kept safe including the materials and seedlings at the nursery, this cuts un-necessary costs for the company, and the target objectives of the company to plant as many trees as there are people on this earth would be achieved because all the produced seedlings would reach the planned farmers.</p>', '<p>Salary comes in time.</p>', '<p>If all security requirements and trainings are conducted, this will better my performance.</p>', '<p>The fact that there was no production at the site, this left the grass to over grow which made it difficult to patrol.</p>', '<p>If a sentry box is constructed for the team by the gate, it would be easy to manage the entrances and exits that happen at the site.</p>', '2022-11-10 10:54:58', '2022-11-10 10:54:58'),
(158, 108, 153, '<p>1. Carrying out plantation maintenance activities such pruning, cleaning etc, as per the approved plan.</p><p>2. Provide correct daily field results achieved in respective task assigned.</p><p>3. Communicate any plantation occurrences promptly.</p>', '<p>1. Observe health and safety measures any time while at work.</p>', '<p>By ensuring that field activities assigned are quality done and 100% trees survival achieved, the company will be in a position to plant more trees with sustainable financing and employ more people hence eradicating poverty.</p>', '<p>Good management of PPE, this helps to save time and report to assigned work on time. Therefore,&nbsp; task rate are achieved.</p>', '<p>1. Provision of effecient working tools to ease the work.</p><p>2. Improve on quality of raincoat purchased as the current raincoat used allows passage of water.</p>', '<p>1. Long distances to assigned work areas i,e Nursery to say, I044.</p><p>2. Wild animals threats e.g buffalos, wild dogs etc.</p>', '<p>1. Provision of transport means i,e from site to the plantation.</p>', '2022-11-10 11:09:09', '2022-11-10 11:09:09'),
(159, 60, 156, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Carry out all the maintenance activities\r\n(Pruning, tree counting, cleaning, weeding etc.) in site<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Carry out any other activity as required by the\r\nforest technician or the forester<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Provide accurate reports for all the activities\r\ndone daily<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Communicate immediately on occurrences within\r\nthe plantation<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Always adhere to the health and safety policy\r\nrequirements by the company <o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->6)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->To always achieve assigned tasks task rates<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->7)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Provide any operational assistance as required\r\nby the supervisor<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->8)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->To always handle company property with care to\r\navoid losses.<o:p></o:p></p>', 'Assisting in operation activities like Fencing.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;\">By performing the above stated roles to the best of my knowledge. I fully dedicate myself to plant and maintain as many trees as possible towards achieving the mission of the company</span><br></p>', '<p>1) Cleaning maintenance in the whole compartments has been achieved.</p><p>2) Fencing around the plantation has been managed adequately.</p>', '<p>1) Salary increment would motivate workers</p>', '<p>1) Balancing family needs with the resources from the company has been a challenge.</p>', '<p>1) Strengthening unity of the whole team and following instruction given by the supervisors.</p>', '2022-11-10 11:12:22', '2022-11-10 11:12:22'),
(160, 89, 157, '<p>1. Protecting all the company property and ensuring they are all secured.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '<p>Vision:Through my employment I am directly benefiting from the company through wages eradicating poverty.<br></p><p>Mission: By protecting the established plantation.<br></p>', '<p>I have managed to take my children to school through this job.<br></p>', '<p>1. Training by KWS to learn on Human-Wildlife management.<br></p>', '<p>1. Illegal grazing. The trespassers pose a threat to the trees. E.g. Some start even fires while others are a hostile.<br></p>', '<p>1.&nbsp; Security supervisors to be recruited to assist in co-coordinating work especially during night shifts.<br></p>', '2022-11-10 11:38:49', '2022-11-10 11:38:49'),
(161, 9, 149, '<p>1. Verification of farmers contracting,group formation,group trainings and follow up on training implementation.</p><p>2. To prepare weekly plan from approved forestry work plan and check implementation forestry activities.</p><p>3. Raise and follow up corrective action request.</p><p>4. Verification of tree stock in partner farmers farm.</p><p>5. To highlight areas for continous improvement.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>To monitor the improved seedling experiment and other activities in Kiambere site once a week.</p>', '<p>By checking compliance to procedures,policies, work instructions and highlighting the areas that need improvement, we are able to track our progress towards achieving company\'s vision and mission.</p>', '<p>I have managed to monitor activities&nbsp; both in Kiambere and 7F sites even after Fredrick was promoted to Head Office.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Provision of a laptop that will improve my reports.</p><p>Additional M&amp;E Officers in both Kiambere and 7F sites.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. Sudden shift from my work place(from Embu to Kitui county).I incurred unplanned cost.</p><p>2. Delay of PPE procurements. My helmet doesn\'t have a protective glass.</p><p>3.Delay of motorbike&nbsp; service repair which made me to work from the office for two months.</p>', 'Provision of a new motorbike because the old motorbike breakdown oftenly while in the field.', '2022-11-10 12:26:18', '2022-11-10 12:26:18'),
(162, 120, 159, '<p>1. Protecting all Company Property.</p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through my work I earn a monthly salary.</p><p>Mission: Through my work I protect the existing trees to ensure they survive.<br></p>', '<p>1. Minimal damage from buffaloes and minimal fire incidences.<br></p>', '<p>1. Provision of means of Transport,&nbsp; a car on site to help address emergencies in the plantation quickly.<br></p>', '<p>1. Illegal grazing.<br></p>', '<p>1. Provision of heavy duty raincoats.<br></p>', '2022-11-10 13:19:09', '2022-11-10 13:19:09'),
(163, 24, 158, '<p>Ensuring safety at the site and of company property at the site.</p><p>Welcoming visitors who come to the site and taking their records in the visitors book.</p><p>Ensuring the clocking devices are fully charged so that workers are able to use the devices for clocking in and out and receiving random calls.</p>', '<p>Nothing Special to Report.</p>', '<p>Aside from being a security guard working for the company, I have also planted the trees as a partner farmer to BGF.</p>', '<p>The whole year as security guards we only registered one occurrence or incidence on theft which was even recorded by me, this makes me proud that I am very vigilant while on duty.</p>', '<p>A sentry box should be constructed by the gate so that it is easy to monitor who comes in and leaves the site.</p>', '<p>Delays in purchasing security items like PPEs (uniforms that were requested for) and even lack of airtime to communicate.</p>', '<p>New uniforms and batons should be purchased for all the guards at the site.</p>', '2022-11-10 13:30:51', '2022-11-10 13:30:51');
