ifferent compartments.</p><p>2) Cleaning maintenance in the whole plantation.</p>', '<p>Provision of gloves for hand protection during manual cleaning.</p>', '<p>1) Theft in site, where different items have been stolen. i.e. gumboots, pipes&nbsp;</p><p>2) Disunity among team members.</p>', '<p>1) Provision of enough and adequate tools for various activities such as pruning saw</p>', '2022-11-10 14:24:57', '2022-11-10 14:24:57'),
(165, 111, 160, '<p>1. To carryout plantation maintenance activities as planned.</p><p>2. Provide/Report correct daily field results achieved.</p><p>3. Communicate any occurrences in the plantation promptly.</p>', '<p>1. Observe health and safety measures any time while at work.</p>', '<p>By planting and maintaining trees to 100% survival rate, the company will be in a position to plant as many trees as required by the mission. Through this trees planted wil provide finacial and ecosystem services which will eventually manage poverty among involved communities.</p>', '<p>Plantation maintenance activities done in 2022.</p>', '<p>Purchase of efficient working tools.</p><p>Provision of means of transport for both seedlings and workers.</p>', '<p>Means of transport- long distances between nursery to work assigned stations.</p>', '<p>1. Salary review to equate with the current inflation.</p>', '2022-11-10 14:37:37', '2022-11-10 14:37:37'),
(166, 102, 165, '<p>Protecting Company Property<br></p>', '<p>None<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through the salary I get it alleviate poverty in my family and community.<br></p><p>Mission: Through my work of Protecting trees.<br></p>', '1. Reduction of Buffalo Population in the plantation hence reduced damages.<br>', '<p>1. Extension of the electric fence.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Illegal grazing.<br></p>', '<p>1. Install a buffalo wall towards the east to mitigate trespassers.</p>', '2022-11-10 14:54:27', '2022-11-10 14:54:27'),
