(170, 86, 168, '<p>Protecting the Plantation and Overall Company Property.</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Vision: Through my work I am able to get salary hence alleviating poverty in my family.</p><p>Mission: Through my work as a security guard I protect the trees from damage ensuring maximum survival.</p>', '<p>No major fire incidence this year.<br></p>', '<p>1.Expand the electric fence.<br></p>', '<p>Illegal Grazing.</p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '2022-11-10 16:58:19', '2022-11-10 16:58:19'),
(171, 23, 167, '<p>Patrolling of the site.</p><p>Ensuring the site is safe.</p><p>Ensure all the workers who are within the site are safe.</p><p>Ensure safety of company property.</p><p>Ensure my own safety while on duty.</p><p>Ensure records on whoever comes into the site and leaves is taken.</p><p>Observe all the workers who come to the site as casual laborers.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Secondary device handler.</p>', '<p>I am also contracted as a partner farmer to this company, therefore this will held eradicate poverty in my home and I have contributed to planting many trees.</p>', '<p>Salary has been paid in time by the HR department.</p><p>Security items have been provided e.g. shoe polish, torches etc.</p>', '<p>Being dedicated at my job so that in future I can still be apart of the BGF team.</p>', '<p>The solar blackouts in the night that kept happening, greatly affected my reporting.</p>', '<p>The company should be responsive to all security requests to ease our operations.</p>', '2022-11-10 17:08:16', '2022-11-10 17:08:16'),
(172, 56, 169, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Carry out all the maintenance activities\r\n(Pruning, tree counting, cleaning, weeding etc.) in site<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Carry out any other activity as required by the\r\nforest technician or the forester<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Provide accurate reports for all the activities\r\ndone daily<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Communicate immediately on occurrences within\r\nthe plantation<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]-->5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; 