(173, 134, 171, '<p>Protecting the Plantation and all Company Property on site.<br></p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Vision: Through my work I am able to get a salary hence alleviate poverty in my family.<br></p>Mission: Through my work as a security guard I protect the trees from damage ensuring maximum survival.<p></p>', '<p>1. Dangerous animal presence in the plantation eg. Buffaloes has reduced significantly .<br></p>', '<p>1. Increase in wages.<br></p>', '<p>1. Illegal Grazing.<br></p>', '<p>1. Get more advanced security torches for the team.<br></p>', '2022-11-10 18:04:12', '2022-11-10 18:04:12');
