(176, 98, 175, '<p>1. Carryout all plantation maintenance activities assigned as per the approved plan.</p><p>2. Communicate immediately any occurrences within the plantation.</p><p>3. Provide accurate results achieved from the field and ensures all task rates are achieved.</p>', '<p>1. Observe health and safety measures while at work.</p>', '<p>By ensuring planted trees are maintained through correct silvicultural operations, resources used are acquired locally which contributes to the local economy thereby eradicating poverty.&nbsp;</p><p>Future harvesting will provide employment opportunities.</p>', '<p>1. inspite of being few in number, the PMS team managed to do a commendable job especially in pruning. The staff acknowledge that, due to great team work the objective was achieved.</p>', '<p>1. Having effecient working tools.</p><p>2. Incentives (bonuses) for work well done and target surpassed in order to boost workers morale</p>', '<p>1. Lack of transport means-This leads to late reporting to work at the assigned stations.</p><p>2. Late deliveries of items, this affects the efficiency of the work. e.g pruning saw files.</p>', '<p>1. Mechanization of forestry activities e.g redeployment of motorized pruning saw.</p><p>2. Prompt replacement of working tools, to increase efficiency.</p>', '2022-11-11 11:49:19', '2022-11-11 11:49:19'),
