/p>', '<p>1. Lacking proper working tools and PPE ( pruning saw, raincoat and overalls)</p>', '<p>1. Quick delivery of requested items.</p>', '2022-11-11 16:39:32', '2022-11-11 16:39:32'),
(183, 1, 181, '<ol><li style=\"text-align: left;\">Development of internal application to assist other departments in executing their mandate</li></ol><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Managing company Servers and ensuring efficiency</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Support in training of newly developed applications</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Propose new solutions to current issues facing other departments</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 11px;\">ï»¿</span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">ï»¿</span>N/A</p>', '<p><b><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Mission</span></b></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">ï»¿Offer support to the forestry department by creating applications that they can use to ease their process of Tree planting</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Ensure communication is Key through mailing and other services (Mail server should always run 24/7 without downtimes)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><b>Vision</b></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">ï»¿By giving a good IT environment for the company to execute its mandate accordingly, More people get to be employed and farmers get to have contracts with the company. This helps in job creations</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">ï»¿</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><br></span><b><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><br></span></b>ï»¿ï»¿ï»¿</p>', '<p>Build my 1st application in modern Vue and Laravel (The Security Reporting App)</p>', '<p>Proper Communication between other departments and IT Dept through complete tickets</p><p>Proper communication where the Acting ICT manager goes down in detail to ensure we are on the same page</p><p>Friday&nbsp; weekly meetings where stakeholders give feedback and suggestion</p>', '<p>Change in technology where suppliers do the upgrade without communication and this ends up causing problems with current applications</p><p>Not updated on the latest changes thus we have users who are no longer part of us and new staff who we have not captured yet. Some change position and this is not captured</p>', '<p>Have our own server where we have full control of all updates and any changes required together with backups</p><p>Be looped in on staff latest updates so that this is effected in all applications</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-11 16:41:43', '2022-11-11 16:41:43'),
(184, 6, 177, '<p>1. Group trainings and implementations.</p><p>2. Training farmers o tree planting and ensure they survive.</p><p>3. By ensuring all contracted farmers are in active BGF groups.</p><p>4. To ensure all staffs always work and act accordingly in line with the vision and mission of the company</p>', '<p>1. Attending FSA annual general meetings.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Training farmer groups on IGA and being self-reliance</p><p>2. Training farmers on tree and ensure they survive.</p><p>3. Maintaining good teamwork with the staff.</p><p>4. Training farmers on soil and water conservation to improve soil fertility thus high crop production</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. FSC trainings</p><p>2. Group reactivation and sensitization</p><p>3. Promotion to SMFP</p>', '<p>1. Timely communication</p><p>2. Additional staff in forestry and operation.</p><p>3. Timely payments to suppliers</p>', '<p>1. Lack of fuel and motorbike maintenance this hampered all field activities.</p><p>2. Poor communication between GIC team&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. Group competition.</p><p>2. Farmers exchange visits</p><p>3. Field visits by HOD</p><p>4. Proper communication especially GIC Team.</p>', '2022-11-11 17:16:58', '2022-11-11 17:16:58'),
(185, 2, 183, '<p>To ensure that we have all the systems and applications up and running according to the Company\'s needs</p>', '<p>Getting the forestry department to a point the apps developed by Capture Solution is fully operational</p>', '<p>Having a stable IT infrastructure in place in helps the company to save much time in running their activities in terms of human resources hence concentrating in planning as many trees .</p>', '<p>Together with the Developer stabilizing the time management of the security staff.</p>', '<p>Increased knowledge in management through interactions with the ICT HOD.</p>', '<p>1. Access to the terms of reference with jobs with Capture solutions.</p><p>2. I was not able to travel to sites.</p>', '<p>Better access to information related to terms of reference with developers.</p>', '2022-11-11 18:10:09', '2022-11-11 18:10:09'),
