(201, 122, 152, '<p>Check compliance to company work instructions, policies and procedures for Nyongoro site.&nbsp;</p><p>Check that high quality seedlings are produced and dispatched for planting.&nbsp;</p><p>Check watering of then newly planted trees are watered and they survive.</p><p>Verify sites biological stocks both in the plantations and the nursery.</p><p>Check the cleaning and pruning of compartments and trees respectively.</p><p>Observe site activities and report non-conformances against company policies and procedures and raise CARs.</p><p>Check CAR implementation and update CAR logs</p><p>Enhance continous improvement.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">By checking compliance of the company\'s procedures, standards and policies, high quality seedlings are produced, planted, maintained thereby promoting the company\'s mission which is through social entrepreneurship, to plant as many trees as there are people in the world hence sustaining the vision.</span><br></p>', '<div>1. Thorough check of compliance to the Health and Safety policy, this year we have not had any accident at work.</div><div>2. Participation in the drafting of the Monitoring and Evaluation Work instruction for&nbsp; raising CARs and Tree counting. CAR work instruction formsed a basis for raising&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;complete CAR while tree counting work instruction aided to counter the challenges in the demarcation of compartments.</div><div>3. Initiated the drafting of M&amp;E tree counting form.</div><div>4. Added a skill in managing people.</div>', '<p>Timely provision of materials that will support me to do monitoring and Evaluation. These are PPEs like raincoat, stationaries and fuel.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Delayed response by the managers to CARs. Delayed responses led to lated approval of CARs for follow up.</p><p>Delayed approval of fuel for the motorcycle. Lack of fuel make it difficult to to monitor all activities in a day especially when they are happening in different compartments which are far apart.</p>', 'Training on Data management', '2022-11-14 17:53:25', '2022-11-14 17:53:25'),
