(211, 88, 209, '<p>Protecting all the company property.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through my work I make monthly earning and is able to take my children to school.</p><p>Mission: As a guard I protect the trees and ensure they\'re secured once planted.<br></p>', '<p>Minimal game damage from buffaloes.<br></p>', '<p>Extension of the electric fence.<br></p>', '<p>Illegal grazing.<br></p>', '<p>Provision of means of transport.<br></p>', '2022-11-15 16:39:32', '2022-11-15 16:39:32'),
