(214, 104, 212, '<p>Protecting company property and ensuring its protected including the employees.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through the wages I get I alleviate my family from poverty.<br></p><p>Mission: Through my work as a guard I protect the company property ensuring the company&nbsp; can continue expanding.<br></p>', '<p>No injuries sustained this year.<br></p>', '<p>Maintenance of the roads<br></p>', '<p>Illegal Grazing.<br></p>', '<p>Employing of more guards.<br></p>', '2022-11-16 10:22:59', '2022-11-16 10:22:59'),
