(217, 81, 214, '<p>Protecting company property and ensuring that it is secured.<br></p>', '<p>None<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through the salaries I am paid, It has enabled me to upgrade the status of my family.<br></p><p>Mission: As I protect the trees, I enable the company to plant more trees in realization of its mission.<br></p>', '<p>No major damages from buffaloes nor major fire incidences.<br></p>', '<p>Extension of the Electric Fence.<br></p>', '<p>Illegal Grazing<br></p>', '<p>Resumption of Activities and recruitment of more people.<br></p>', '2022-11-16 17:25:14', '2022-11-16 17:25:14'),
(218, 20, 217, '<p>sensitising farmers about the program&nbsp;</p><p>Grouping farmers and ensuring that groups function&nbsp;</p><p>Contracting farmers&nbsp;</p><p>Training farmers&nbsp;</p><p>Distribution of seedlings&nbsp;</p><p>Follow up to ensure that the right things have been done by the farmers&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Attending meetings&nbsp;</p><p>Attending radio talk shows&nbsp;</p><p>Conflict resolution&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Heating targets set before me to ensure that the company that I am part of does not fail&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Internal trainings and group reactivation&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Sticking to planned activities&nbsp;</p><p>Proper communication&nbsp;</p><p>Proper facilitation&nbsp;</p>', '<p>There was no any major problem except the breakdown in field work right from June that kind of hindered the smooth progress in group reactivation and trainings that were proceeding nicely&nbsp;</p>', '<p>More trainings especially on communication&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-17 15:00:50', '2022-11-17 15:00:50'),
(219, 18, 218, '<p>Recruitment of farmers in BGF groups</p><p>Timely, correct and accurate transmission</p><p>Time work</p><p>Training of groupson all aspects of agro forestry</p><p>Strict implementation&nbsp; of planned activities with immediate feedback on outputs</p><p>Prepare farmers for distribution</p>', '<p>Any other task assigned from time to time by the supervisors</p>', '<p>They are in co existence in that there is the aspect of financing the main activity that is planting of tree with farmers.</p>', '<p>Managed to reach groups and groups leaders as we lookfroward towards groups</p><p>Located the groups and help them to set their leadership&nbsp; structures</p>', '<p>Contineous engagement&nbsp; with the groups</p>', '<p>Inconsistencies&nbsp; in executing activities because there are alway adjustments&nbsp; in planning</p>', '<p>Built integrity with the farmers by providing&nbsp; them with feedback intime</p>', '2022-11-17 16:22:57', '2022-11-17 16:22:57');
