(220, 25, 216, '<ol><li>1. Together with the Site Manager, develop yearly, monthly, and weekly production work plans for review by the site manager.</li></ol><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">2. Implement approved nursery work plans according to schedule and within budget.</span></p><p>3. Responsible for seedling stock management in the Dokolo nursery by ensuring the inputs always match the outputs.</p><p>4. Management of plus trees.</p><p>5. Propagation, hardening off and production of the agreed upon number of seedlings.</p><p>6. Produce correct and timely stock reports.</p><p></p><p>7. Continuously provide Effective communications through agreeable channels (Emails, Phone calls, reports etc.) on the nursery activities at Dokolo site.</p>', '<p>Ensuring all site workers clockin and out, answering ramdom calls and inputing daily results.</p>', '<p>Ensuring timely production of good quality Melia azedarach seedlings at the site nursery.</p>', '<p>Evaluation, identification and mapping qualified Melia azedarach trees as plus trees for fruit/nuts collection.</p>', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">1. An environment for creativity and innovations.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">2. External trainings.</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">3. Open discussions and knowledge sharing with all the forestry department staff.</p>', '<p>1. Late communication of instructions from supervisors.</p><p>2. Delays in processing and delivering site requisitions.</p>', '<p>Timely deliverance of requisitions for poduction.</p><p>Sharing ideas with collegues on improved seedling production</p><p>Provision of the right items required and requested for production</p>', '2022-11-17 16:26:17', '2022-11-17 16:26:17'),
(221, 21, 215, '<p>1. Recruitment of farmers in BGF groups as per the approved group formation and farmers recruitment procedures&nbsp;</p><p>2.timely correct and accurate transmission about farmers groups and farmers activities&nbsp;</p><p>3.Training to groups in all aspects of the BGF agroforestry programme&nbsp;</p><p>4.strict implementation of planned activities with immediate feedback on output.&nbsp;</p><p>5.prepare farmer groups for distribution according to approved plans&nbsp;</p><p>6.oversee the timely and successful distribution of seedlings in planned areas&nbsp;</p><p>7. Follow up onthecpost distribution planting activities to ensure there no MORTALITY.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Training to groups in all aspects of the BGF agroforestry programme&nbsp;</p>', '<p>To work positively with the company to eradicate poverty and fight corruption in Africa&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. Training of farmers groups in the district of Dokolo and interacting with farmers Organ</p>', '<p>Organizing all the farmers who received seedlings into groups&nbsp;</p><p>Training farmers in groups and they appreciate the importance of being into group</p>', '<p>Communication was a big issue that hindered some activities to drag</p>', '<p>Provision of logistics materials in time to enable effective implementation of activities&nbsp;</p><p>Enhancement of salary because of the high cost of living&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-17 16:59:52', '2022-11-17 16:59:52'),
(222, 33, 115, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">1. Responsible for 2 sites, Kiambere and Nyongoro for production, establishment and maintenance.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:black;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2. At the beginning of the year there was planning and follow up of production activities.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">3. Later in the year the production </span>responsibility<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;was re assigned to a different manager and my responsibility is now plantations establishment and maintenance.</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">4. To ensure approved plans and policies are implemented accordingly.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">5. To ensure forestry and operations activities in the plantation are well coordinated.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone;text-autospace:none\"><font color=\"#000000\" face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\"><br></span></font></p>', '<p>None.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"X-NONE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I relate by making sure things are done right the first time\r\nand whenever non-conformances occur, corrections are done and corrective\r\nmeasures are put in place to ensure the non-conformances do not occur. I also\r\nunderstand that my duties and responsibilities are geared towards sustainable\r\nforest management of the company\'s plantations for economic, environmental and\r\nsocial benefits.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Tree stock verification, the activity of tree stocks\r\nverification has improved, and probability of errors reduced from systems put\r\nin place to ensure updating and reporting of correct figures. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Improved communication at all levels.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Continued training on identified areas of concern.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Mortality though this has reduced compared to\r\npreviously.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No establishment done according to plans. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Maintenance targets not met in Nyongoro due to reduced\r\nlabour.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Periodical (quarterly) employee evaluations to assist\r\nthe team improve on performance.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-19 13:19:21', '2022-11-19 13:19:21'),
(223, 3, 219, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">1. Implement, Supervise, and control all forestry and\r\nrelated activities like the nursery on Dokolo site.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">2. Train, enlighten and assist the team embrace BGF values<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">3.. Ensure approved plans and policies are implemented accordingly.<o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">4. Ensure smooth coordination with interfacing departments.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">5. Create a cohesive relationship between BGF and local administrators /community.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">6. Create a culture of professionalism which is not at per with Kenya&nbsp;</p>', '<p>None</p>', '<p>Through social entrepreneurship, plant trees with farmers and ensure they survive for betterment of the environment and uplift their livelihoods</p>', '<p>1. Training AAs in Dokolo site on BGF and farmers outgrowers program</p><p>2. Interface with Dokolo local community on giant lira maintenance.</p>', '<p>1. Incentivize farmers groups with soya beans that can act as a revolving crop</p><p>2. Group competition among groups within the same sub county</p><p>3. Have internal and external trainings on group dynamics, first aid, Motorcycle safe riding&nbsp;</p>', '<p>1. Different attitude from staff compared to Kenya</p><p>2. Farmers not embracing the program wholistically leading to cutting down of trees.</p><p>3. A culture that lacks professionalism, seeks short term gains through whining\'s and alarmists.</p>', '<p>1.Increased pictorial trainings in groups.</p><p>2. Continuous training of site staff on work ethics and attitude change</p><p>3. Immediate response from support departments when called upon.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-19 15:58:55', '2022-11-19 15:58:55'),
(224, 8, 113, '<p>1. To ensure sound financial Management of the company and its extensions. Efficient utilization of company funds as well as planning.&nbsp;</p><p>2. To provide critical financial information to management for decision making.</p><p>2. in Operations: ensure full support to our core department and other departments for optimum performance.</p><p>3. To train and to have the right people doing the right job at all times.</p>', '<p>1. Quality Management: extension of the position of finance, ensure we apply funds efficiently. To continuously close gaps for continuous improvement.<br></p>', 'Through achievement of the above tasks, the company is kept in the right direction towards the achievement of the company\'s vision and mission.', '<p>1. Being able to navigate the company through the very tough times of limited cashflows through out the year.</p><p>2. Overseeing the implementation of all the digital apps and seeing all improvements and efficiencies gained by having all the digital apps we have developed..</p>', '<p>1. Working with managers who have higher driver and ambition for success.</p><p>2. Have sufficient funds at the right time according to agreed approved plans.</p>', '<p>1. Unstable security workforce that has been changing all the time with a lot bad blood and bad things happening on sites.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Too many problem encounters with Time and Capture in management of security working hours especially and leaves.</p><p>2. Unstable cash in-flows that affect the company operations.</p>', '<p>1. Create a culture of getting work done same day before end of day in all areas of the organization.</p>', '2022-11-22 14:07:56', '2022-11-22 14:07:56'),
(225, 42, 220, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">1)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Protect companyâ€™s property and staff by maintaining a safe and\r\nsecure environment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">2)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Observe for signs of crime or disorder and investigate\r\ndisturbances.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">3)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Report in detail all incidents and occurrence in site.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">4)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;Always adhere to the\r\ncompany procedure and policies.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left: 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">5)<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Monitor and control access at the nursery get and around the perimeter.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>None.</p>', '<p>By performing the above roles and duties with the best of my knowledge to ensure planted seedlings survives.</p>', '<p>1) Plantation fencing and manual cleaning is well done.</p>', '<p>1) Management to fast track opinions and request made by site workers e.g. request to make a temporary structure in A016 is not yet implemented.</p>', '<p>Theft cases reported on site has been a challenge.</p>', '<p>1) Reporting after every 30 mins to be reviewed to 1hr to create enough time for guards to patrol fully in the plantation and to give a good report.</p><p>2) The company to provide a tractor on site to assist in transporting water for watering during establishments instead of relying on donkeys.</p><p>3) Windthrows and dead trees to be processed to produced timber instead of storing them on site.</p>', '2022-11-23 10:04:43', '2022-11-23 10:04:43'),
(226, 118, 221, '<p>1. Driving the farm tractor.</p><p>2. Conducting maintenance checks on the tractor and implements.</p><p>3. Working in the plantation doing maintenance activities: E.g. Mechanical cleaning.<br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>1. Pruning and Manual Cleaning: Assisting the forestry team in doing these activities.<br></p>', '<p>Vision:&nbsp; Through my salary I am able to provide and uplift my family and community.<br></p><p>Mission: As a driver doing maintenance work I am able to ensure the planted trees are surviving hence the company can plant many more.<br></p>', '<p>1. The company kept me in employment even when it scaled down activities, It also paid my salary on time.<br></p>', '<p>1. Caution while driving the tractor.<br></p>', '<p>1. Temporary transfer from Operations activities to Forestry activity. Learning and adapting the new activities was challenging.<br></p>', '<p>1. Effective communication.</p>', '2022-11-23 10:07:36', '2022-11-23 10:07:36'),
(227, 32, 173, '<p>Management identified communication as a major source of Non-conformances and consequently, BGF was losing a lot of money due to poor understanding and compliance with the principles of communication. My role is to translate the concerns and explain the workings and policies that regulate how people relate to each other and to all staff at all levels of BGF in order to avoid costly non-conformances due to misunderstandings or lack of talking to each other. The company, therefore, has developed follow-up tools that allow me to measure progress and intervene where needed in the name of the MD.&nbsp;</p><div><br></div>', '<p>Communication with external parties&nbsp;</p><p>Management of BGF social media</p><p>Management of Miti magazines subscription and database</p>', '<p>Communication is key to the vision and mission of the company hence my role is crucial in ensuring the smooth flow of information within BGF and ensuring policies and any new information is timely and efficiently communicated and understood by staff at all levels in the name of the management for adoption and implementation ensuring the company is on track with its mission and vision.</p>', '<div style=\"border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: none; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The\r\ncreation of a communication App. BGF staff from all sites and levels can easily\r\ncommunicate with HODs. And the creation of the meetings App will save me a lot of time which leave me more time to follow up on the implementation of upwards and downward communication.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<div style=\"border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: none; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">More\r\nsite visits and interactions with staff at all levels, and presence in events\r\nrelated to the company. This is in the future plans starting next year.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<div style=\"border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: none; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Due to\r\nbudgetary implications.&nbsp; We were not able to visit the sites as much as\r\nwas necessary.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '<div style=\"border-width: 1pt; border-color: windowtext; border-image: initial; padding: 0in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: none; padding: 0in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Continuous\r\nhammering as most staff are resistant to change especially in the\r\nimplementation of new systems and tools and faster reaction and feedback on CARs from the HODs</span></p>\r\n\r\n</div>', '2022-11-26 14:33:55', '2022-11-26 14:33:55'),
(228, 103, 224, '<p>1. Watch over and protect all company property.<br></p>', '<p>None.<br></p>', '<p>Vision: Through the salary&nbsp; I get, I am able to uplift the status of my family.<br></p><p>Mission: As I protect the trees and the rest of the company property, I ensure the trees planted survive and therefore others can be planted.<br></p>', 'The fence has assisted in Managing the Buffaloes.<br>', 'Cleaning in the plantation.<br>', '<p>Snakes. With clean roads it\'s easier to spot the snakes at a distance unlike now.<br></p>', '<p>Just cleaning in the plantation to be done.<br></p>', '2022-12-02 10:28:14', '2022-12-02 10:28:14'),
(229, 34, 225, '<p>1.Responsible for the day-to-day management of the HR Department inclusive of&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Payroll, implementation of policies, and ensuring that staff are motivated and have a</span></p><p>good working environment.</p><p>2.Ensure health and safety of all employees</p><p>3.Followup on the yearly training schedule for all departments.</p>', '<p>I am the focus point for all the people who have personal needs/guidance</p>', '<p>80% of the success of the company depends on people. If we have the right people in&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">all departments with the right attitude then, we shall be able to achieve the vision</span></p><p>and the mission of the company.</p>', '<p>1.Implementation of the policy to hire on contractual basis and to only give permanent employment to the best performance</p><p>2.Introduction of electronic management tools</p><p>3.Huge improvement in matters of comprehension by staff in matters of health and safety policies and implementation</p>', '<p>1.Need more electronic tools to manage the needs of the department especially in matters of trainings and health and safety</p><p>2.HR Site officers&nbsp;</p><p>3.More site visits to interact with the staff</p><p><br></p>', '<p>1.Staff resistance to change</p><p>2.The head of department should provide honest input for their team members for us to assist in the best way</p>', '<p>Support by other departments in introduction and implementation of the policies</p>', '2022-12-08 12:03:28', '2022-12-08 12:03:28');
