(154, 56, 'Communications Manager\r\nï‚ 	Together with Forestry, ensure that employees are aware of the Company strategy and projects for 2021.', 'Not Achieved', 'This is on the right track through interventions in the working party, scheduled and minuted meetings and site visits .', 'This has massively improved but from day to day occurrences it shows that knowing is not always understanding. It is a joint and permanent effort of CM together with the other heads of departments and one can never assume that all staff are aware unless we measure this knowledge regularly.', '2021-11-10 08:55:47', '2021-11-10 08:55:47'),
(155, 56, 'ï‚ 	To make certain that forestry and operations receive their planned communication inputs from sites daily.', 'Not Achieved', 'Big improvement due to increased activity and awareness of the HODs', 'Vertical upward communication is still a  huge challenge and needs to be addressed aggressively as it costs the company not only money but also opportunities for improvement.', '2021-11-10 08:55:47', '2021-11-10 08:55:47'),
(156, 56, 'ï‚ 	To put in place and initiate the fundamentals of communication through approved executive messages, presentations, internal memos, meetings, printed materials etc.', 'Not Achieved', 'We now have approved notices, nicely displayed on improved Notice board. Presentations on communications and planned and scheduled departmental meetings.', 'Much more need to be done here, but it is not only the CM effort. THe HOD\'s are now fully aware and get indeed regular presentations as eye openers.But the breakdowns are still present. THe effort needs to be continued all the time.', '2021-11-10 08:55:47', '2021-11-10 08:55:47'),
(157, 56, 'ï‚ 	To assert the importance of communications by planned site visits in 2021.', 'Not Achieved', 'Due to Covid19 pandemic there were travel restrictions. I only managed to visit Kiambere and Nyongoro site once this year', 'Correct and the one visit was an eye opener. It shows that this activity is important and shall be planned to happen regularly.', '2021-11-10 08:55:47', '2021-11-10 08:55:47'),
(158, 56, 'ï‚ 	To handle public relations, information output, press releases and media requests, social media and/or advertising efforts throughout 2021.', 'Not Achieved', 'We post ongoing activities on BGF Facebook every week and we have regular articles from HODs on BGF media. Much more needs to be done however.', 'More need to be done here indeed. Public relations is a mindset that requires relentlessly being alert. It is however everybody\'s responsibility to interact correctly and at the right time and that again  is the task of the CM to create staff awareness.', '2021-11-10 08:55:47', '2021-11-10 08:55:47'),
