(322, 93, '1.	To establish 75 ha of Mukau plantation (141438seedlings) by the end of 2021', 'Not Achieved', 'No establishment done in 2021.', 'Change of yearly plan from establishment to plantation maintenance only.', '2021-11-12 09:53:50', '2021-11-12 09:53:50'),
(323, 93, '2.	To reduce field mortality to less than 5% by undertaking appropriate silvicultural practices by end of 2021(i.e watering of seedlings, cleaning etc)', 'Not Achieved', 'Trees damage occured due to uncontrol wild animals i.e buffaloes.', 'All silvicultural practices done correctly as approved plans. mortality still a challenge due to damages by buffaloes.', '2021-11-12 09:53:50', '2021-11-12 09:53:50'),
(324, 93, '3.	To immediately gap all dead trees from Jan 2021 to maintain zero mortality in the plantation', 'Not Achieved', 'No gapping done in 2021.', 'Change of plan from establishment to plantation maintenance and stock record assessment.', '2021-11-12 09:53:50', '2021-11-12 09:53:50'),
(325, 93, '4.	To prepare monthly and weekly work plans and supervise their implementation: for all plantation forestry operations from Jan 2021', 'Achieved', 'Adequate planning and organizing of site activities.', 'Constant consultation accross all departments in order to have realistic work plans.', '2021-11-12 09:53:50', '2021-11-12 09:53:50'),
(326, 93, '5.	To Conduct all approved training sessions according to plan (seedling production, land preparation plantation establishment and maintenance) by the end of 2021.', 'Achieved', 'All required neccessity for training (time & tools) provided on time.', 'Being informed on training areas. good communication skills on disseminating necessary knowledge required.', '2021-11-12 09:53:50', '2021-11-12 09:53:50'),
(327, 93, '6.	To implement and supervise all plantation establishment and maintenance activities according to approved plans by end of 2021', 'Achieved', 'Availability of detailed and well informed plans and yearly budgets.', 'Frequent trainings and availability of effecient working tool. Good supervision skills and implementation procedures.', '2021-11-12 09:53:50', '2021-11-12 09:53:50'),
(328, 94, 'To have all agreed upon seedling numbers planted and surviving at the end of 2021', 'Not Achieved', 'The strategy changed and we focused on correcting all gaps that we have in the department.', 'We have a huge survival problem and consequently he decision was taken to focus on right figures correcting issues at sites related to staff. Consequently there was no planting;', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(329, 94, 'Eliminate the mortality in all sites by the end of 2021.', 'Not Achieved', 'Despite not planting, we still have mortality in older trees due to game damage in plantations, domestic animals with farmers due to poor protection of farms and some cases of rot rot in kiambere due to poor rooting systems. can be addressed by shifting responsibility of protection to groups, fencing in the plantation and producing seedlings with better quality in the nursery.', 'The biggest problem is that for years we got wrong inputs and figures if any from the sites. Consequently wrong decisions have been taken. The problem is that we know what to do but we don\'t do things right first time all the time. The exercise of this year is meant to close all the gaps leading to mortality. This includes also hard decisions with staff. We will also no longer budget mortality but aim for  planting more trees than what we get money for.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(330, 94, 'Have the existing T&A environment 100% functional by beginning January 2021', 'Achieved', 'We no longer have problems with results and bonuses in the back office. These are checked and signed by all persons responsible in the forestry department.', 'OK', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(331, 94, 'Have farmers contracting module fully functional by June 2021', 'Not Achieved', 'The modules development was completed after June. We also must complete cleaning of the data before uploading which is still an ongoing activity.', 'The delay is with the developers but as we have posponed the planting we can absorb the loss of time.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(332, 94, 'Have all approved trainings for all sites done by the end of 2021', 'Not Achieved', 'This is still ongoing. And some of the training could not be done because of COVID.', 'Correct', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(333, 94, 'To implement all maintenance activities according to plan by the end of 2021.', 'Not Achieved', 'This is still ongoing for Nyongoro. For Kiambere we have managed to accomplish this according to plan except for thinning. For the farmers program strategy changed to checking the farms individually', 'Planning and working the plan is part of the changes and reviews we are implementing. Along the way we have also created new tools that should allow shorter reaction times when timelines are not respected.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(334, 94, 'To have all farmers contracted issued with contracts by end of June 2021', 'Not Achieved', 'We changed the strategy. Those that were created for contracts all got back their contracts, the second and the third category are yet to get the ir contracts.', 'We all agreed that it was better to do this exercise correctly that rush and have the same problems. It is part of the decision to postpone planting to the second part of 2022.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04');
INSERT INTO `section_one_part_b_s` (`id`, `section_one_id`, `Objective`, `status`, `E_comments`, `S_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(335, 94, 'To have all the existing farmers in BGF groups by end of 2021', 'Not Achieved', 'This was slowed down by COVID restrictions. Also, most of the staff were involved in farm checks which is still a priority.', 'This was an ambitious objective! Moreover we know now that we did not have all the data that allowed to move into that direction. The whole forestry thinking has changed and will be geared towards prioritizing the working with groups. Staff is being restructured in that direction and new tools wil be used to achieve fast and correct registration and managing of groups.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(336, 94, 'To ensure the M&E always fully supports accurate decision making through checks, programme\r\nassessments, correct progress reports and other relevant M&E tools.', 'Not Achieved', 'M&E moved to finance and to concentrate on the checking of figures.', 'Monitoring and evaluation failed in making Management aware that figures are not correct. The biggest non-conformance BGF can occur is not having the tree numbers. Therefore the division was restructured under Finance and more staff was hired. They will play a huge role in the years to come as a support department for Forestry without foresty being bothered with the managment of the agents. What matters is that figures are checked and action taken within the shortest delays.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(337, 94, 'Ensure that we always have the right staff in the forestry department', 'Not Achieved', 'An ongoing exercise as we have already seen some staff leave because they were not fit for the job.', 'This is being addressed as part of the ongioing reingeneering of the Forestry workings. Getting to right staff at all levels through change, hiring or training takes time. That is probably why this objectives did not have a time line.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(338, 94, 'Ensure that all levels of staff in forestry and operations effectively communicate and coordinate\r\nat all times.', 'Not Achieved', 'We experienced improved communication between forestry and operations. How ever we could still do better. This is also a continuous exercise.', 'Communications are a big problem and the solutions are challenging. Forestry can now count on the support of a Communication Manager which will help but not solve everything. It is and will remain a joint effort from the Management team as goeed communications likewise quality strats from the top. We are improving massively though.', '2021-11-12 10:33:04', '2021-11-12 10:33:04'),
(339, 95, 'Migration of Emails and Websites to our own domain', 'Achieved', 'Continuous Monitoring', 'Good job done here!', '2021-11-12 12:25:56', '2021-11-12 12:25:56'),
(340, 95, 'Migration of Capture Application to our own domain', 'Not Achieved', 'In progress', 'We did not prioritise, no harm done here.', '2021-11-12 12:25:56', '2021-11-12 12:25:56'),
(341, 95, 'Secure Head office network and faster sage environment for Accounts department', 'Not Achieved', 'What remains is configuring the back up internet', 'As we found out the ball is now in Operations that needs to provide a new fiber optic connection. It is being addressed.', '2021-11-12 12:25:56', '2021-11-12 12:25:56'),
