(374, 104, '1.	To carry out timely (Weekly and Monthly) checks to ensure compliance to work plans, work instructions and Forestry Policies throughout 2021.', 'Not Achieved', 'The objective for the year was pegged on production and planting objectives. Focus was shifted to accurate stock take in all sites.', 'Ok, Noted. These were changes from management.', '2021-11-17 09:57:38', '2021-11-17 09:57:38'),
