(796, 222, '5.	Follow up and ensure all approved trainings for Nyongoro and Kiambere sites are done by the end of 2022.', 'Achieved', 'Follow up done on training as per schedule, objectives change also had an effect on the schedule with production targets reduced or no production done in Nyongoro hence nursery training affected.', 'Ok.', '2022-11-19 13:19:21', '2022-11-19 13:19:21'),
(797, 222, '6.	To implement all forestry maintenance activities as per approved plan and budget by the end of 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Objectives changes lead to changes in the maintenance plans. For Nyongoro temporary labour halted hence targets affected.', 'Only maintenance staff', '2022-11-19 13:19:21', '2022-11-19 13:19:21'),
(798, 222, '7.	To have the correct stock figures throughout the year.', 'Not Achieved', 'Stock verification done and updates with correct figures done weekly. Figures also verified by M&E to check on accuracy.', 'The site manager still gives wrong figures knowingly and unknowingly.', '2022-11-19 13:19:21', '2022-11-19 13:19:21'),
(799, 222, '8.	To ensure that all forestry staff always work and act according to and in line with the vision and mission of the company.', 'Achieved', 'Continuous communication and training and follow ups has aided in achieving this.', 'There is still an issue with communication.', '2022-11-19 13:19:21', '2022-11-19 13:19:21'),
(800, 223, '1.	To plant 230,000 seedlings and ensure they all survive by the end of 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'Relocated to Dokolo in March 2022', 'Ok', '2022-11-19 15:58:57', '2022-11-19 15:58:57'),
(801, 223, '2.	To have completed the Forestry Stewardship Councilâ€™s (FSC) certification process with two farmer groups by end of 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'Relocated to Dokolo in March 2022', 'Ok', '2022-11-19 15:58:57', '2022-11-19 15:58:57'),
(802, 223, '3.	Produce mukau seedlings in two satellite nurseries within 7 Forks groups by second rain season of 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Relocated to Dokolo in March 2022', 'Ok', '2022-11-19 15:58:57', '2022-11-19 15:58:57'),
(803, 223, '4.	Ensure there are at least 10 active Farmer Groups in a ward.', 'Not Achieved', 'Relocated to Dokolo in March 2022', 'Ok', '2022-11-19 15:58:57', '2022-11-19 15:58:57'),
(804, 223, '5.	Initiate and have a farmer group competition by December 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Relocated to Dokolo in March 2022', 'Ok', '2022-11-19 15:58:58', '2022-11-19 15:58:58'),
(805, 223, '6.	Have all approved trainings done by the end of 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Relocated to Dokolo in March 2022', 'Ok', '2022-11-19 15:58:58', '2022-11-19 15:58:58'),
(806, 224, '1.	Continuously Review and update all the procedures and work instructions in 2022 as need arises.', 'Achieved', 'This was achieved. Now documents are in document control pending another review.', 'It is a never ending process.', '2022-11-22 14:07:56', '2022-11-22 14:07:56'),
(807, 224, '2.	Make sure that there is a total mind and attitude change concerning doing things right first time all the time and the perception of quality.', 'Achieved', 'There has been improvement out the continuous interactions at different levels and inteventions by Management.', 'This is a collective work of management team.', '2022-11-22 14:07:56', '2022-11-22 14:07:56'),
(808, 224, '1.	To improve on efficiency and reduce cost by 30% by Dec 2022 on all operations activities', 'Not Achieved', 'There was minimal activities on-going during the year.\r\nWe consequently put up the preparations to achieve the goal.  Through digital apps, meetings, trainings etc.', 'Okay.', '2022-11-22 14:07:57', '2022-11-22 14:07:57'),
(809, 224, '2.	Ensure planned operations activities are done as per schedule throughout 2022', 'Achieved', 'The activities that needed to be done happened on time.\r\nWe have engaged in planning using project which will bring about more efficiency.', 'Okay.', '2022-11-22 14:07:57', '2022-11-22 14:07:57'),
(810, 224, '3.	Ensure smooth flow of forestry activities where forestry interfaces with operations throughout 2022', 'Achieved', 'This is has been achieved.', 'ok', '2022-11-22 14:07:57', '2022-11-22 14:07:57'),
(811, 224, '4.	To work with the right staff throughout 2022. To solve all staff related issues, including replacements, and hiring by June 2022', 'Achieved', 'This is achieved and the system has cleaned itself', 'This is a collective objective for all the Management team members', '2022-11-22 14:07:57', '2022-11-22 14:07:57'),
(812, 224, '1.	Have all the accounts documents processed on the day of receiving throughout the year.', 'Not Achieved', 'This has not been achieved however this has improved.', 'There is still room for improvement.', '2022-11-22 14:07:57', '2022-11-22 14:07:57'),
(813, 224, '2.	Have all requests for analytical accounting successfully addressed within one week throughout out the year', 'Achieved', 'Achieved', 'OK', '2022-11-22 14:07:58', '2022-11-22 14:07:58'),
(814, 224, '3.	Together and at advice of management\r\na.	To review the value of biological assets by March 2022\r\nb.	To have the accounts in their final format by March 2022\r\nc.	To have all KRA related issues addressed and resolved by March 2022\r\nd.	To have company audits done by March 2022', 'Achieved', 'Done', 'Well done', '2022-11-22 14:07:58', '2022-11-22 14:07:58'),
(815, 224, '1.	At all times, be assured that the figures received by forestry are checked and correct.', 'Achieved', 'With a weekly reporting system, it works well', 'The system is ok.', '2022-11-22 14:07:58', '2022-11-22 14:07:58'),
(816, 224, '2.	To follow up on CARâ€™s in such way that they are addressed and corrected in the agreed upon time.', 'Achieved', 'Ok', 'Ok', '2022-11-22 14:07:59', '2022-11-22 14:07:59'),
(817, 224, '3.	To make sure that requests for special inquiries are addressed immediately', 'Achieved', 'We have put systems in place that take care of all the assignments.', 'ok', '2022-11-22 14:07:59', '2022-11-22 14:07:59'),
(818, 224, '4.	To have a complete operational M&E team by January 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'This is work in progress. To be implemented fully in 2023.', 'ok', '2022-11-22 14:07:59', '2022-11-22 14:07:59'),
(819, 225, 'To guard the companyâ€™s plantation against human and livestock damage.', 'Not Achieved', 'Domestic encroachment has been contained and level of encroachment has reduced however there is much to be done.', 'Domestic animal encroachment is reported to local administration which has helped reduce cases of grazing in the plantation.', '2022-11-23 10:04:43', '2022-11-23 10:04:43'),
(820, 225, 'To ensure that company property is always free from theft and destruction.', 'Not Achieved', 'This has not been achieved due to loss of items such as Pipes, gumboots which is done by employees within.', 'Investigation of theft cases are ongoing.', '2022-11-23 10:04:43', '2022-11-23 10:04:43'),
(821, 225, 'To prevent the occurrences of mishaps and hazards that may cause heavy losses/damages to company property through reporting.', 'Achieved', 'Always reports on every occurrences on site.', 'Reporting is done by guards after every.', '2022-11-23 10:04:43', '2022-11-23 10:04:43'),
(822, 225, 'To eliminate apathy to everyone about reporting a crime to the head of security or the SLO.', 'Achieved', 'Reports have been given at all time without fear.', 'Reporting of incidents on site done on a daily basis.', '2022-11-23 10:04:44', '2022-11-23 10:04:44'),
(823, 226, 'To cut tractor breakdowns by 50% through careful driving and innovation.', 'Achieved', 'Achieved no major breakdowns.', 'Only worn out parts report from tractor\'s report but not breakdown.', '2022-11-23 10:07:36', '2022-11-23 10:07:36'),
(824, 227, 'Together with management, have a complete grip on internal and external communications for BGF in 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'This is on the right track. Internally; through scheduled meetings, creation of custom-made Apps interventions in quarterly staff meetings, working party, site visits and PP presentations. . Externally ensuring weekly postings on social media and monthly newsletters to keep our partners and stakeholders engaged. Communication is a continuous process and everyday we find out ways to enhance and improve communication in BGF.', 'It is a never ending process as people and work methods change in time.', '2022-11-26 14:33:55', '2022-11-26 14:33:55'),
(825, 227, 'Ensure BGF communications are consistent and engaging throughout 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Partially achieved. Downwards vertical communication is on the right track. Upwards vertical communication still some work to do.', 'Okay', '2022-11-26 14:33:56', '2022-11-26 14:33:56'),
(826, 227, 'Manage flows of articles to guarantee all content is publication ready for BGM throughout 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'The articles were sent but the publication is not on my hands.', 'Okay', '2022-11-26 14:33:56', '2022-11-26 14:33:56'),
(827, 227, 'Together with management implement and develop communication strategies that build staff awareness and satisfaction in BGF starting January 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Partially achieved.\r\nWe have a functional electronic communication App where BGF staff can at no expense on their end, pass information, give suggestions or ask questions using their mobile phones. We also have an electronic CARs App where staff can report any non conformances and action is taken. The use of the apps however is not optimized yet.', 'Use of electronic means of communication is not yet a culture and its something that staff need to be motivated and trained more intensively than the classic means of communicaition.', '2022-11-26 14:33:56', '2022-11-26 14:33:56'),
(828, 228, 'To protect all company property', 'Achieved', 'I\'ve managed to keep buffaloes at bay and keep away illegal grazers. No damages to company property this year.', 'Correct.', '2022-12-02 10:28:16', '2022-12-02 10:28:16'),
(829, 229, '1.	To have right staff for all the departments by June 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'There is great improvement, but we are not yet there', 'There is still some work to do at the level of the site responsibles and some head office managers. But that is not in the hands of the DDHR', '2022-12-08 12:03:28', '2022-12-08 12:03:28'),
(830, 229, '2.	To ensure vacant positions are filled within the set timelines throughout 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'Not achieved because we focused on the reorganization, and we had challenges with finances', 'Okay', '2022-12-08 12:03:29', '2022-12-08 12:03:29'),
(831, 229, '3.	To have 100% retention of all excellent performing employees throughout 2022', 'Achieved', 'This year we have retained all excellent staff and the ones who have left its due to their personal reasons and were not right for the job', 'Okay', '2022-12-08 12:03:29', '2022-12-08 12:03:29'),
(832, 229, '4.	Ensure that all approved training schedule per department happens and results measured by 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'Because of the reorganization and financial constraints. However, there is good progress as we have done quite a number of internal trainings.', 'Okay', '2022-12-08 12:03:29', '2022-12-08 12:03:29'),
(833, 229, '5.	Have every employee happily aligned to the vision and mission of the company throughout 2022', 'Not Achieved', 'There is still resistance because of personal reasons by site staff and even here at the head office', 'It\'s part of having the right staff at the right place. Its continuous improvement.', '2022-12-08 12:03:29', '2022-12-08 12:03:29'),
(834, 229, '6.	To create a conducive environment that benefit employees good feeling and the company vision and mission throughout 2022.', 'Not Achieved', 'We are on the way towards that goal and there is massive improvement and the people that were hiding can\'t do that now. Thats why some staff are leaving.', 'Okay', '2022-12-08 12:03:29', '2022-12-08 12:03:29');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(1, 135, 11, '<p>1. Evaluation process was smooth and clear on the objective of the company and personal growth. a single wish is to implement all suggestions as discussed.</p>', '<p>The evaluation was detailed an informative to serve the purpose of its intend on correcting and adjusting the needs of the staff in order to achieve the company vision and mission. The staff showed great sense of listening and positive critic during the discussion.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>There is little emphasis on his core tasks in forestry in terms of what he has been doing and intends to improve upon in the coming budget period. The transport issue is acknowledged and shall be addressed by the management in due time. salary increment is not automatic as continuously explained by the HR.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-06 08:07:24', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(2, 12, 7, '<p>-Despite the effects of covid-19 on employment the company ensured that we all are on work and paid on time and i really appreciate that.&nbsp;</p><p>-Through the ongoing farmers verification exercise i have realized that indeed there\'s low tree survival, and to mitigate this is to ensure that there is continuous sensitization on farmers ownership of the program through trainings on tree protection,identifying the dedicated farmers,issue them with quality seedlings on time and ensure that all planted seedlings survive so that we can our objective as a company.&nbsp;</p>', 'Antony has greatly&nbsp;improved on his attitude&nbsp;towards Bgf and the program&nbsp;.His team building&nbsp;skills and inquisitive&nbsp;nature has made&nbsp;him&nbsp;stand tal lamong his colleques.Communication skills&nbsp;need to be improved&nbsp;', NULL, NULL, '<p>Issues that still need to be addressed that have been missed in the evaluation</p><p>1. Emphasis on groups and ensuring all the farmers we work with are in actively functional groups.</p><p>2. That we must do all that is necessary to ensure the trees we plant with farmers survive</p><p>3. Need to have the correct information from the field at all times.</p>', '2021-11-06 09:27:08', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
(3, 115, 12, '<p>Evaluation has enabled me to know my strengths and weakensess. the process was smooth, justifiable and in depth discussion.</p>', '<p>Evaluation process was interractive and detailed, the staff understood the proposed corrections for better achievement of company objectives. Gideon is a discipline and workaholic staff.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The use of GPS shall be included in next year\'s training plan and this can be done internally. In the meantime, refresher training shall be done for the teams that do tree counting. In the meantime, strategies are being implemented to address the issues related to tree counting.</p>', '2021-11-06 10:05:09', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
(4, 14, 5, '<p>B.G.F has been good to employees since we have been getting all the services. We should improve on famers or group a fares. we should get some allowances.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>William\'s ability to converse in the local dialect and convince locals on the importance of trees&nbsp; maintenance is commendable.</p><p>His good attitude and drive has made him a good extension agent.</p><p>Need to improve on communication.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has shown great qualities in executing his duties both with groups and individual farmers. this is great value for his own personal career growth and working towards desired company\'s objectives. However, these qualities should translate into desirable results of having all our trees survive, all our farmers in groups and getting continuous feedback from the partner farmers for continuous improvement.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-06 10:09:39', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
(5, 91, 13, '<p>The evaluation process was informative and i have noted my strengths and weaknesses with a lot of concern. Much appreciation to the company for believing and giving me a chance to display my strengths.</p>', '<p>The evaluation process was smooth and to detailed, the staff showed a lot of interest on actualizing the vision and mission of the company. He was too passionate on forestry practice.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Based on the evaluation, he seems to be self-driven and handles all the tasks given to him well.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-08 07:44:33', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
(6, 78, 8, '<p>Evaluation was interactive and good, it has showed me areas of improvement as well as those I need to maintain for achievement of company targets.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Karisa Johnson is a well informed, full of ideologies and very discipline. He has interesting interpersonal skills that made working with him enjoyable.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>There was no production this year and as expected not much for Sulubu to do in the nursery apart from cleanliness and maintenance of the nursery structures, identifying plus trees. This being said, he could have done more in terms of proposing some trials with the aim of improving the production process especially in the areas he has mentioned he needs on in section three.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-08 08:44:01', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(7, 3, 14, '<p>Am grateful for the insights and continued support from my supervisor and HOD.</p><p>Through the many interactions with the management team, our vision has been broadened and our experience in handling the human resource improved leading to a feel-good attitude from the employees.</p><p>We aim at improving the adaptive capacity of our farmers which will translate to better survival.</p>', 'The employee is very dedicated and has a passion for the job. He is an asset to the company in driving the farmers\' program to the next level. He although needs to work to improve on planning &amp; organization, data analysis, and manipulation plus being keen on details.', NULL, NULL, '<p>There is a need for improvement in the following areas:</p><p>1. Ensuring that all the 7 forks staff understand the importance of working with groups and not individual farmers.</p><p>2. That in as much as the team is trained in forestry/agroforestry and is capable technically, the farmers\' program success also depends on the creation of meaningful relationships with the farmers.&nbsp;</p><p>3. Ensure that the team at all times provides correct information/feedback.</p><p>4. Ensure that the team understands why we must plant and ensure that all the trees survive. Meaning, we have to do everything necessary within the scope of the company\'s guidelines to ensure this happens.</p><p>Conversely, there has been a tremendous positive change in 7 forks since he took over with regard to people management and better communication that has made it possible to get a clearer&nbsp; picture of what exactly is going on within the 7 forks project (important in making decisions for correction/improvement)</p>', '2021-11-08 09:32:12', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
(8, 68, 15, '<p>First I have to that management for the opportunity to join this team, towards achieving the company\'s objectives as I gain experience in my line of study.</p><p>Secondly I have to admit during my probation period there were some gaps which were observed in relation to seedlings production which is the core in forestry. I didn\'t manage to achieve my set targets and objectives however through continuous training and interactions with my supervisor I have gained experience and can be entrusted with production and processing of Mukau seedlings and plantation maintenance activities.</p><p>Thirdly, I have to appreciate the PMS team I have at site who has been respectful and committed towards their work. Through their unity we have been able to surpass our set targets especially in cleaning activities.</p><p> I look forward to incorporating the whole team including the security and even casual to work as a team and through this we will be able to achieve the company\'s vision and mission and set objectives for every departments.</p>', '<p>The employee joined the company this year. He started at a slow pace but he has since improved after training on both production and maintenance activities. Improvement has especially been noted in the plantation maintenance activities supervision. Continuous training ongoing, however he has a good attitude and he has shown ownership of the project. He is encouraged to continuously communicate for continuous improvement. He has shown honesty through reporting of actual situation on the ground and the correct figures.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Recently confirmed after probation, Osore was green newly from school, and inexperienced. However, a lot has changed. he has shown that he has the potential to become an accomplished technician. He is young and has been managing a staff that is way older than him. There is, however, still room for improvement with regards to management, precise communication, planning, and monitoring and budgeting.</p>', '2021-11-08 11:43:49', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(9, 83, 17, '<p>I have learnt a lot on my strengths and with concern noted my weaknesess with ways of improving for greater results. The evaluation process was accommodative and fair to my better understanding.</p>', '<p>Evaluation process was smooth and relevant to the staff. All questions was answered to precision and detailed, excellent interpersonal skills was noted and the employee showed great enthusiasm towards overall vision, mission and objective of the company.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Ronald Mukhwana is a hard worker always giving his best to any task he is assigned in the plantation. He has a great attitude towards his work. Like the rest of his colleagues, he needs to be made aware of how important the work he does is for the company. How it is linked to the mission and the vision.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-08 11:56:17', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
(10, 113, 18, '<p>Evaluation was good, It has showed me areas of improvement as well as areas I\'ve performed extremely&nbsp; good.&nbsp; Thanks to my Supervisor. Not forgetting to thank the company and its management for standing with its employee during this time of Pandemic.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Mtawali Karisa is one among the best PMS interims discipline, Honesty, team work, hardworking and general performance.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He seems well trained and has the right attitude towards the job.</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">He should not however that the company shall not provide transport from their homes to the workplace but in the future, there are prospects for providing transport between the nursery and the plantations.&nbsp;</span></p>', '2021-11-08 12:29:56', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
(11, 13, 20, '<p><i>There is always room for improvement through training and guidance from the all departments.</i></p><p><i>management is doing good work on support of staff&nbsp; to perform the required task.</i></p><p><i>motorbike repairs not to be ignored at all after reporting by the person using it.</i></p>', '<p>James, has adapted well in his current duties. he has gained good rapport with farmers groups which for part has earned him a good standing ground in the community he serves.</p><p>He needs to improve on his planning and communication.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has shown great drive on the job. However, there is still a need to ensure all farmers are in groups, doing everything possible to ensure the trees survive and that correct information is provided at all times for accurate decision taking.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-08 13:14:00', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
(12, 6, 19, '<p>More training is needed to farmer groups on capacity building and group empowerment.&nbsp;</p><p>To have group motivation support, e.g. group exchange visit this will encourage our farmers thus high tree survival.</p><p>To have Toyota Kenya services on monthly basis.</p><p>To plan for more staff training on agroforestry practices.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>The staff is well self-motivated and has positive attitudes towards the farmers program. The employee though need to:</p><p>1. Have all farmer groups active&nbsp;</p><p>2. improve on planning and organization which is very key to this program</p><p>3. improve on data analysis and manipulation particularly excel</p><p>4. gear towards completion of group verification exercise which in turn will provide reliable information about our farmer groups&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>With her at the forefront of groups and group formation in 7 forks, we have seen hopeless farmers turn into entrepreneurs through the groups formed and guided by her. She is passionate about the job. She can however also with her experience help the other team members approach issues relating to groups like she does. There is also a need for improvement with regards to the development of a SMART strategy to fastrack group formation, motivation, and their activation.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-08 14:04:11', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(13, 15, 23, '<p>Despite&nbsp; the year being hard due to covid-19 pandemic,&nbsp; am so grateful and wishes to sincerely acknowledge the company for allowing and giving us an opportunity to work with us.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '<p><i>There is a positive change in attitude and general work environment exhibited by Arshiphord.</i></p><p><i>There is however,need to work on communication and work planing as we intergrate various community enterprises in the program.</i></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Arshiphord\'s reporting was bad at the beginning of the year. Inconsistencies with data provided either due to lack of ownership of the job or lack of concentration. </p><p>However, this has since changed in the past few months and he must keep it that way for his own good.&nbsp;</p><p>Going forward, there must be emphasis on ensuring all our farmers are in groups, activated, the trees that we plant must survive and improved bottom up communication.</p>', '2021-11-08 14:30:45', '2022-05-20 16:21:41'),
(14, 26, 27, '<p>The exercise was more interactive, where areas of weaknesses was identified and call for improvement , however some other areas which was also achieved was pointed out and appreciated as well, we agreed with&nbsp; supervisor to always work as a Team&nbsp; for us to&nbsp; achieved the set targets.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The Staff has good attitude for the job though a lot of training and improvement is needed on team management,, punctuality, communication and team work. Measure need to be put in place to make sure all pending backlogs as per target given is addressed and should not recur in the future. This can be addressed through proper planning and organization which currently lacking.</p><p>All farmers need to be active groups because they will be entry point for every activity being undertaken in relation to farmers, eg, trainings , seedlings distribution, Tree counting</p><p>The staff has agreed on improving on the weak areas and reach out for direction when need be.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Pope is good at mobilizing and talking to farmers (field work). He however needs to improve on his leadership, organizational and reporting skills. He is sometimes evasive and tells what you want to hear and always paints a picture that everything is going well which is not always true. He also needs to provide a useful strategic plan for the groups and group formation that shall ultimately give the desired results of having all our farmers in active and functional groups.</p><p>like for the rest of the project team, he needs to understand why it is important that we work strictly with groups, all our trees survive and that we have a meaningful feedback/communication with farmers for continuous improvement.</p>', '2021-11-09 10:19:19', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(15, 28, 30, '<p>The period I have so far spent in the company have been beneficial in terms of additional knowledge, skills and experiences the the operations field. And my supervisors and boss have continued to guide and encourage me at my place of work.</p>', '<p>A good staff with positive attitude and reliable. Harriet you can do better. You need to improve on punctuality especially reports submission.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Work on your weak areas to Keep it up.</p>', '2021-11-09 11:16:23', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(16, 58, 28, '<p>Through the unity of my fellow colleagues (PMS) in site we have been able to achieve a lot this year and I would like my supervisor to help bring this unity with all Kiambere site staff to enable us work together and this will help us achieve a lot as a team.</p>', '<p>The employee has been corporative for the past 9 months I interacted with him and he follows instructions as directed. He has gaps in terms of time management which we have agreed upon and will improve on. Through time management is when we can achieve our set task objectives at the end of the day.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He seems to be well trained and knowledgeable about all the maintenance activities. Apart from that he has shown that he can be used to do other non-forestry activities. being a PMS, he should be made to understand the importance of his role in the company and how this is in line with the company\'s vision and mission.</p>', '2021-11-09 11:21:39', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(17, 106, 31, '<p>1.The company to facilitate security training .</p><p>2.Company to provide for additional transportation. </p><p>3.Employ more security.</p><p>4.HOS to have an assistant.<br></p>', '<p>Employee has potential. He has shown willingness to learn. He can do better in his line of work.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Work on your weak areas and aim to deliver more on your work.</p>', '2021-11-09 11:30:34', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(18, 99, 29, '<p>The company has provided key procedure in evaluating its employees effeciently and organizing to support workers has been encouraging. the evaluation was detailed and informing.</p>', '<p>The evaluation process was on mutual agreement and pointing out of areas to improve on. the staff was over willing to be more resourceful to the company.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Salim is well aware of his responsibility and tries to do well all duties assigned to him. some issues raised by him in the evaluation have been addressed (salary scale and bonuses for permanent staff etc) and issues relating to transport shall be addressed in due time by the management.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-09 12:05:47', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(19, 98, 26, '<p>Evaluation was good, It has showed me areas of strength, weaknesses as well as areas to improve on. Thanks to my supervisor for the support he has provided to me since beginning of the year that has enabled be perform my duties efficiently. Thanks to the management and entire company for standing with us during COVID 19.</p>', '<p>Bakari is a polite, humble and hard working staff. He is among the top rated PMS interims of performance, truly he is a right guy to work with.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Bakari is a well-trained personnel in pruning plus other maintenance activities. Some issues raised in the evaluation relating to HR, bonuses and salary have been addressed by the HR department in previous interactions. He should also seek to develop more skills for plantation management (like cleaning, plant protection, thinning etc) instead of nursery.</p>', '2021-11-09 12:28:47', '2022-05-20 16:23:45'),
(20, 64, 32, '<p>I would like to thank the company for the chance in working as plantation maintenance staff at Kiambere site. I look forward to improving in my line of duty and help the company achieve its set goals and objectives.&nbsp;</p><p>Lastly I would like the management company to embrace motivation of workers as previously been seen, whereby each year there would be a small token added to the salary.</p>', '<p>The employee has been well disciplined in his work. He has been assisting in nursery production during this years GIC seedlings production where he has shown a great potential in seedlings production. He however needs to improve in the identified gaps of managing of people to ensure the set goals and objectives of the department and the company at large are met. More effort is needed in nursery production where he has skill and experience and moving forward with more training there will be an improvement.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>From the interaction above, he seems multiskilled and useful in various areas within the plantations. However, he needs to improve on his punctuality as this is a cost to the company.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-09 13:22:46', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(21, 120, 34, '<p>I thank the company for the 5 years and request to continue working with the company.<br></p>', '<p>Employee has the determination to perform optimally. <br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Good.</p>', '2021-11-09 13:41:59', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
(22, 122, 24, '<p>I will always do my best hence enabling continuous improvement and also prove an asset to the company as Monitoring and Evaluation is concerned.</p>', '<p>Ladislaus is highly motivated to develop in his career and make a great impact in Better Globe Forestry. He is keen in noting areas of non-compliance and improvement. This quality should be improved through constant feedback, collaboration with MEM and thorough grasping of internal policies and procedures.</p><p>In his objectives we shall include a training to have all internal quality standards in his fingertips so to enable m<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">onitoring prevent occurrences of non-conformances instead of solving </span>occurred<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;non-conformances.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>M&amp;E has become a pillar to the company\'s continuous improvement and the M&amp;E impact on the company\'s activities is evident and has led a lot improvement. This is from your tireless efforts to make impact to the company.</p><p>Keep it up.</p>', '2021-11-09 13:42:38', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
(23, 35, 33, '<p>The Interaction with my supervisor was fair&nbsp;</p>', '<p>You can do better you need to improve on your attitude , learn to follow instructions and take corrections in a positive way.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The performance is average. Your job requires a lot of listening and following of instructions which your are weak. Work on your weak areas for improvement.</p>', '2021-11-09 13:52:45', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(24, 18, 35, '<p>All was well&nbsp; and need to improve on some areas to achieve both company and personal objectives through execution and better communication</p>', '<p>The employee has the postive attitude for the job and with more coaching and closely supervised can make a big step in shaving her up to be a realiable and an asset nto the company. She has shown that she can do any other task outside her job description by working with the field team as an agroforestry agent.</p><p>The employee though need to work to improve on her week areas; communication, team work and planning &amp; organization.</p><p>the indvidual target also need to be achieved for verification activity of up to know the employee is on the right track only that she need to be keen to details and reporting the overall view of the farmers and the farms</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Harriet had previously shown great potential as she had great insight about areas for improvement in the Dokolo project, showed a passion for the job because the program would benefit the people living in the area she comes from. She also has/had a better understanding of the project area as she comes from there.&nbsp;</p><p>There was however a change when we started the farm checks exercise. Late reporting, provision of wrong figures, uncollaborative with the rest of the team. This came out clearly during the vetting exercise. Harriet must immediately learn to take responsibility and to be more of a solution finder than a complainer. She must improve on her leadership skills and stop using other underhanded means of painting a bad picture of her colleagues to try and prove that her mistakes are lesser in magnitude. Like the rest of the team, she also must work to ensure all the farmers are in active groups, have planted and all trees standing and that there is continuous feedback/communication from the partner farmers.</p>', '2021-11-09 15:21:27', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(25, 126, 40, 'most the planned objectives for the year have been met despite the challenges posed by COVID pandemic and change of school calendar. I would like to thank the management for the continuous support and improvement on working systems of the company', '<p>Despite of working in areas with poor terrains and at times unresponsive individuals/community, the officer has remained focused and has delivered to the best of his ability, maintaining a positive attitude and a good self drive.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Has done well in the GIC program. There however needs to be an improved interaction with the rest of the BGF team to avoid alienation.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 05:18:50', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(26, 95, 37, '<p>The evaluation was smooth and informative. I have learnt my weakensess and strengths from the laments made by my superviors.</p>', '<p>Evaluation process was interactive, the staff acknowledged to understand all the question raised.&nbsp; He was appreciative and pledged to be an assest to the company henceforth.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 'He seems to have skills in all the maintenance activities. He also shows genuine concern for the state of the plantation by suggesting that we need to mechanise more for efficiency and faster maintenance intervention. Like the rest of his colleagues he needs to be made to get a deeper understanding on the importance of his job and how that relates to the company\'s mission and vision.', '2021-11-10 05:34:01', '2022-05-20 16:23:45'),
(27, 94, 36, 'Thanks to my supervisor for always being there for assistance in order to achieve my tasks. Special thanks to my collogues, department as well as the entire organization for the effort and assistance to ensure the plantation is maintained. Trainings has been conducted sufficiently.&nbsp;&nbsp;', '<p>Shadrack is a hardworking staff, dedicated and always ready to learn and improve. His performance is amazing and I enjoyed working with him.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He seems ok with skills in all maintenance activities. He needs to be explained to and to understand why there are deductions.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 05:56:36', '2022-05-20 16:23:45'),
(28, 17, 42, '<p>From the discussion,I\'m able to gauge myself in terms of achievement and areas that need improvement.</p>', '<p>The overall performance of Fredrick is good judging from his short period at Kiambere site where he brought numerous improvements and clean up of the site, and now his tenure in 7 forks is proving fruitful as the endless reports can now be verified.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The M&amp;E presence and impact is felt on the two sites out of your good work. M&amp;E is a pillar for the company\'s continuous improvement and your value is felt.</p><p>Keep up the good work.</p>', '2021-11-10 06:19:01', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(29, 54, 43, '<p>First I thank the company for this far, I joined this company from 2007 as a casual worker and I have been able to achieve&nbsp; many of my projects from the resources I get from the company so am really grateful.</p><p>I look forward to improving in my line of work and as I have agreed with my supervisor come next year we will have the correct figure in terms of tree counting at Kiambere site and some of the differences in Stock figures will be eliminated.</p>', 'The employee has been good at his work, faithful and honest with the figures he gives. He has been useful in terms of tree counting and demarcation of the compartments in the site since he has been there from the time of establishment. There has been gaps however in having accurate figures in stock assessment which mostly is caused by human error, he however admits his weakness and willing to improve.&nbsp;', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has been involved in various activities within the plantations as assigned to him including tree counting. From the review, he comes up with good suggestions especially about sensitive activities in the nursery. He also acknowledges that he has had challenges in tree counting and put it as an objective that he needs to improve on.</p>', '2021-11-10 06:29:34', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(30, 10, 22, 'Am grateful to better globe forestry for giving me a chance to work in ASAL\'s , to learn and experience in this harsh areas also am grateful to them during this difficult times they were able to keep me and my fellow staff with full salary pay, its my duty as staff to make sure the aims and objectives of our company are met. This is by making sure there is 100% tree survival', '<p>Fredrick has been pivotal in the betterment of the program. His positive attitude is commendable though need for self drive and improvement in communication&nbsp; is needed for continuous improvement.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has the right attitude for the job. However, More emphasis needs to be put on groups going forward as that is the key to our success. There is also a need for improved bottom-up communication as this will help in the continuous improvement of the farmers\' program.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 06:31:17', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(31, 25, 44, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Most of the objectives were not achieved due to continous changes in company plans during the course of the year.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">There is need to improve on staff/ team management through being assertive and motivational. Further trainings in various skills and experience will be helpful in developing my career to achieve the company vision and mission through proper implemenation of the annual site objectives.</span><br></p>', '<p>The staff has improved alot in planning and organization. he has good attitude for the job. He is managing a very key exercise of farmers verificaton which currently is ongoing and is moving in the right direction. The data quality has progressively improved though more need to be done on team management and monitoring and being keen to details</p><p>There is alot to be done though in verification exercise given that we have alot of farmers yet to verified in differnt categories. The major focus that the SMFP is to put plans in place to ensure the verification exercise for the remaining farmers is completed in a timely manner.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>By being the site manager for the Dokolo project, Charles has in his hands a great opportunity for growth. There have been massive improvements in handling administrative duties in relation to farmer database. However, for him to successfully manage and implement the project, improvements must suffice in the following areas:</p><p>1. Leadership:- he must lead by example, be brave enough to check his people all times they go wrong, stop being lenient and focus on getting results, must be able to embrace responsibility and inspire his team to get the desired results.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Planning and followup/checking:- must learn to follow through with agreed-upon plans and continuously check his team and continuously communicate any changes.</p><p>3. Communication:- there seemed to be a continuous breakdown in communication that led to the team in Dokolo doing various actions contrary to instructions.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 07:21:32', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(32, 55, 49, '<p>First of all I thank the company for the opportunity and good relation so far. Through my daily activities as agreed by my supervisor I will strive to do my best and offer any suggestion necessary to help achieve the company\'s goals and objectives.</p><p>Lastly I would request the management company to consider this team in payment increment, life has not been easy and through this, workers will feel motivated and produce results as expected.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The employee has been useful in tree counting where he has specialized in since he knows all the boundaries of the compartment. He indeed helped me to get to understand the whole of the plantation and where any special needs were required.&nbsp; Through this we were able to achieve a lot in terms of maintenance since all these activities are core related. The gaps identified in terms of tree counting to get zero error has been agreed on and he is now aware that the company depends very much on the stock figures at all the time.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>he is skilled in all the maintenance activities within the plantation plus other activities in operations. this is a plus. He however was also part of the team that provided wrong tree counting information at the beginning of the year for whatever reason which is a huge non-conformance. It should also be noted that he acknowledges this by indicating that he needs continuous guidance and training on tree counting.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 07:48:14', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(33, 11, 38, '<p>I\'m very much grateful&nbsp; for being&nbsp; part of the company, have learnt a lot in terms of trainings and other agroforestry&nbsp; related issues, being provided with airtime shows how concerned&nbsp; company is .</p>', '<p>A lot need to be improved for her efficiency to be maximized. Need for self drive and working on planning/ general work enthusiasm&nbsp; will need to be prioritised.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Nancy works well but sometimes needs a lot of close supervision. She can also be better at this job if she exhibited a little more passion for the job rather than simply being driven by targets and supervision.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">There must be an emphasis on ensuring all our farmers are in groups, (activated), trees planted survive and improved bottom-up communication.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '2021-11-10 07:49:16', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(34, 22, 45, '<p>1. As security personnel of the company, we need to continue adhere to company policies for smooth running of our job.</p><p>2. Request the company management to continuously give feedback on the communication from security.</p>', '<p>Moses Ogwal as Head of Security has done a promising job, and has potential to improve and do better.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The performance is not good. Work on your weak areas.</p>', '2021-11-10 08:02:07', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(35, 62, 52, '<p>First I have to thank the company for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in my personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies laid off workers but we have been at work all through. I am committed towards my work and I will always strive towards achieving my assigned duties as already agreed upon by the supervisor.</p><p>The only thing I would request is to be given certificate for any training done example Building Construction, Carpentry, power saw handling e.t.c</p>', '<p>The employee has been committed to his work for the time I have known him, He however had weakness at the beginning of the year in terms of attaining pruning task rate where the excuse was the type of pruning saws were not good. However after provision of the tools, he indeed changed and always surpass the task rate. He is ready to accept his weakness and change towards achieving better results.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has been involved in various activities in the plantation apart from the maintenance activities. At some point at the beginning of the year, there was lux in commitment to work without close supervision by the team in pruning and cleaning. this has since changed. Some issues raised especially in HR on salary have since been addressed by the HR.</p>', '2021-11-10 08:48:21', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(36, 108, 47, '<p>The work has been good, challenges encountered and overcame.&nbsp; Thanks to my supervisor for all kinds of support he has been providing. Also I want to thank my department for standing with me throughout the year, not forgetting the entire management for standing with its employees during this time of pandemic.</p>', '<p>Hashako is a good staff, ready to learn from mistakes and rectify. I am impressed with his work output, generally he is good.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Hashako is well experienced in maintenance activities that are specific to forestry. He seems to be interested in improving in areas specific to forestry which is a good thing for the forestry department. However, his self-motivation is worrying and something that must be improved upon in the next working year for him to realize optimum or agreeable results by the company\'s standards.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 09:44:57', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(37, 44, 57, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies\r\nlaid off workers but we have been at work all through. I am committed towards\r\nmy work and I will always strive towards achieving my assigned duties as\r\nalready agreed upon by the supervisor.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lastly I would request the management team to consider making value of the trees which we do record as dead and windthrows from different compartments instead of letting them rot in the plantation.</span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The employee has been\r\ncommitted to his work for the time I have known him. He is well conversant with the whole compartments and has been useful for the interns currently in doing tree measurement. He is flexible and after training can do any chores required.&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Josphat has shown that he has immense knowledge of the Kiambere plantation and knows all the compartments by heart. However being part of the tree counting team, it must be noted that we got wrong figures at the beginning of the year due to incomplete counting and non-communication about areas that need to be cleaned before the tree counting is done.</p>', '2021-11-10 09:58:30', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(38, 112, 46, '<p>I am satisfied with the evaluation process, it has been a learning process to understand my weakness and with a promise to improve.</p>', '<p>The evaluation process was interactive, the staff showed much interest towards achieving company vision, mission and objectives. He understand his weakness with calmness and promise to improve and be an assest to the company henceforth.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Okumu seems to understand his job well. He also has other skills that are not forestry-related like welding and has a background in electrical engineering. This could be useful to the company in the near future. It also comes out clearly that for his future career development, he\'d be interested to do something that is not in forestry.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 10:11:50', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
(39, 23, 55, '<p>Management of the company should continue to be supportive to the staff especially security personnel.</p>', '<p>Lameck Obongi as a security personnel has a positive attitude towards his job and easy to supervise because he is very interactive and communicates well.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Average performance. Can do better.</p>', '2021-11-10 10:24:10', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(40, 66, 59, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies\r\nlaid off workers but we have been at work all through. I am committed towards\r\nmy work and I will always strive towards achieving my assigned duties as\r\nalready agreed upon by the supervisor.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The employee has been\r\ncommitted to his work for the time I have known him, He however had weakness at\r\nthe beginning of the year in terms of attaining pruning task rate where the\r\nexcuse was the type of pruning saws were not good. However after provision of the\r\ntools, he indeed changed and always surpass the task rate. He is ready to\r\naccept his weakness and change towards achieving better results.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has been involved in both forestry work and operations activities. it should also be noted that he helped in the set up of a trial for the PhD student which has since been a success with over 90% survival. Issues raised regarding salary have already been addressed by the HR department in recent interactions.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 11:22:18', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(41, 65, 64, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and I have managed to educate my three children just from the resources I get from the company. I am and will always be committed towards achieving by assigned task and willing to improve on any gasps as identified.</span></p>', '<p>The employee is very committed to his work. He has been willing to follow instruction and always advocates for unity among the other workers for effective performance. He is always ready for improvement and willing to work.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has been part of the cleaning team. This has since improved in the Kiambere plantation which is an indicator of recent good effort by individual staff in the cleaning team. However, like the rest of the cleaning team, it should be noted here that at the beginning of the year, there was provision of wrong data of the results and some cases of laxity.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 12:10:22', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(42, 20, 53, '<p>Working with BGF has helped me alot in achieving confidence since i always interact with many stakeholders and i have always tried my best to work hard and i will endeavour to improve on my weak areas with proper training so that i am within the vision and the mission of the company.</p>', '<p>The staff is ready to improve on weak behavioral competences and also when more trainings, skills and knowledge are acquired, he will be an asset for the company to achieve its vision.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Silas is a hard worker and always wants to do more than the rest which is a good thing. However, in some instances doing more has led to rushing the job and hence collecting wrong data or not getting complete information. He is too passionate about his job. he however needs to be able to take criticism positively because on the job, it is not about who is wrong and who is right but about what is wrong and what is right.&nbsp;</p><p>For him to also improve, he needs to always understand why we must work with groups, have all our trees survive and continuous feedback/communication from/with farmers for continuos improvement.</p>', '2021-11-10 12:15:20', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(43, 27, 54, '<p>The two years I have spent working and directly engaging with farmers has not personally impacted my life but also aimed at driving towards eradicating poverty,achieving company mission and vision, however with hope for improvement on areas of weaknesses both from my side a d the management, I strongly believe we shall together achieve mission and vision of the company.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Lameck is ready to improve on the areas of weaknes especially the behavioral competences and if well equipped with the required skills and knowledge, he will be in place to achieve both the site and company overall objectives.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He shows great passion for the job having joined later in 2019 but managed to catch on in a fast-paced work environment. He is self driven and takes criticism well. He however needs to tie this quality to get better results by having all the farmers in active groups, zero mortality, improved communication and feedback with/from the farmers.</p>', '2021-11-10 12:21:01', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(44, 21, 56, '<p>We need&nbsp; to improve on planing and communication because is key to all the project&nbsp; success and all the logistics should be delivered in time to field staff for effective implementation&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The employee is a resourceful person and with additional trainings,&nbsp; Skilling and knowledge&nbsp; equipping he will be useful for the company to achieve its annual objectives and overall vision.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Bonny was one of the hardest workers in the Dokolo team having recruited more farmers than any other person in the team. This year, however, embarking on-farm checks and verification exercises he gave inaccurate information, and in some cases where details were needed he provided little or none. Bonny must improve his leadership skills, be more of a team player and focus to provide solutions for the various challenges we have within the project.</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">He, like the rest of the team members, must also, embrace the fact that we must have all our trees surviving, through working with active groups and continuous engagement with them for feedback&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '2021-11-10 12:26:47', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(45, 19, 58, '<p>Agree with information above and promised to improve where there is need.</p>', '<p>Vicky is ready to improve in key areas such as punctuality, communication and team work. With more training and skills development,&nbsp; she will be a good asset for the company.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Vicky has gained much-needed skills for her to do the job over time. She however needs to improve on her self-confidence by appreciating that her opinion/views matter because she has first contact with the farmers. She can also be better at the job if she puts in a little more passion in what she does. </p><p>To succeed in this job, she must, if not yet already, understand the importance of providing correct figures/information, the need to work with groups, providing useful feedback and 100% survival of the trees.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 12:33:41', '2022-05-20 16:21:42'),
(46, 16, 62, '<p>Facilitating farmer\'s exchange&nbsp; visit will be a bost in the arm to the program. I am grateful to the BGF for containment measures especially during covid-19 pandemic.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>John has been a key player in the implementation of the farmers program especially through group mobilization and satellite nursery seedling production. Currently, he is reactivating dormant groups in the larger Embu region.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Has great mobilization and group formation skills and shows great passion in his job. These, should however now be directed towards the realization of zero mortality, having all farmers inactive and functional groups that find their own local solutions for the challenges that they face, and better communication/feedback from the farmers for continuous improvement of the program.</p>', '2021-11-10 12:45:13', '2022-05-20 16:21:41');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(47, 7, 48, '<p>Am happy with the regular trainings and farm verifications which are ongoing, various type of intergrated forestry approach with skills and experience that will bring a lot of development on the program and to the farmers in general.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>William, has improved in the delivery of the program through&nbsp; farm visits, monitorings and verification. there is need however for continuous&nbsp; communication&nbsp; and alot of self drive to improvement for efficiency of the program.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>William is driven to do his job out of a sense of duty. He can be better if he added a passion to it. He needs to be more direct in his communication to prevent misunderstandings.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">There must be an emphasis on ensuring all our farmers are inactivated groups, 100% tree survival, improved bottom-up communication. and continuous accurate and timely reporting.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '2021-11-10 12:55:23', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(48, 110, 61, '<p>Evaluation of employees on various aspects was great to get more intrusive issues which affects employees.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Evaluation was informative and the staff responded positively on negative areas that needs improvements.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Barisa has gained some useful skills in forestry maintenance activities and seems eager to improve further on them so that he can perform better. He must however improve on his communication skills for him to effectively perform at the tasks assigned to him. He needs also to be open enough to point out issues that did not work well for him with regards to his supervisor.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 13:30:21', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(49, 56, 67, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies\r\nlaid off workers but we have been at work all through. I am committed towards\r\nmy work and I will always strive towards achieving my assigned duties as\r\nalready agreed upon by the supervisor.</span></p>', '<p>The employee has been resourceful in the plantation activities. He has specifically taken part in tree marking of the years being that he was there from the time of establishments. He has helped other workers in getting to know the whole plantation.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has acquired various skills apart from maintenance activities. Efforts by HR in explaining issues have clearly had a positive effect and he now sees the company in a positive light. He clearly shows concern about the plantation. He however was still part of the PMF team that did not provide the correct figures at the beginning of the year. It should also be noted that it is ok to pray but even prayers have their place and time on sundays.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 13:34:43', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(50, 9, 51, '<p>I appreciate the company for the new role of M&amp;E</p>', '<p>Nelly is a passionate about the job. She has adapted well to the changes in her Job. What is required for now is guidance in the internal policies and work instructions and trainings on using the Corrective actions system.</p><p>On tree verifications, she has been in the field before therefore her interaction with farmers is not new to her. We hope to utilize this skill further in catching with forestry to verify all farms for correct tree stock.</p><p>We also encourage that solutions on how to improve her work come from within.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>There is room for improvement. There is a lot to learn and need for guidance and training from the supervisor.</p>', '2021-11-10 13:45:53', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(51, 63, 69, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies\r\nlaid off workers but we have been at work all through. I am committed towards\r\nmy work and I will always strive towards achieving my assigned duties as\r\nalready agreed upon by the supervisor.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The employee has been\r\ncommitted to his work for the time I have known him, He however had weakness at\r\nthe beginning of the year in terms of attaining pruning task rate where the\r\nexcuse was the type of pruning saws were not good. However after provision of the\r\ntools, he indeed changed and always surpass the task rate. He is ready to\r\naccept his weakness and change towards achieving better results.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has been involved in various activities in the plantation for both forestry and operations. It is clear that he needs to improve on his punctuality as this could be an indicator of a bigger problem.</p>', '2021-11-10 14:12:30', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(52, 24, 65, 'Company management should empower security personnel throughout the company, same treatment security personnel in Kenyan sites receive should be the same even Dokolo site security receive.', '<p>Paul Opio is a dedicated staff, loves his job and has a positive attitude</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p><i>Keep it up and worker harder.</i></p>', '2021-11-10 14:21:20', '2022-05-20 16:21:43'),
(53, 32, 50, 'I am happy with my job as a Communication manager, a very critical one for BGF. And I look forward to continuing to create a positive impact both internally and externally by spearheading the BGF communication department and continuously reminding staff of the importance of timely and accurate communication. And researching and looking for ways to ensure continuous improvement and thus making the company save money.', 'You are very much on the way to mastering the communication requirements of BGF. It is a matter of continuous improvement of the skills, the ability to develop and use newly developed tools, to get knowledge, but most of all to relate with people, listen to them, understand them and use that knowledge to make them communicate up, down and other directions the right way first time every time. This is already saving the company huge costs and it will even become more critical as we grow.<br>Keep on the good work!', NULL, NULL, '<p>See supervisor comments</p>', '2021-11-10 14:38:49', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(54, 60, 71, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies\r\nlaid off workers but we have been at work all through.&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The last thing i would like the company to check on the welfare of the workers in terms of salary increments</span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The employee has been\r\ncommitted to his work for the time I have known him. He is an old man but is willing to listen to any instruction given to him and has no issue despite the age differences. He has been willing to be assigned any duty and works with minimal supervision.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has been involved in cleaning which has improved over time. He however was part of a cleaning team that needed close supervision at the beginning of the year which is an unacceptable trait on the job.</p>', '2021-11-10 14:48:26', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(55, 29, 68, '<p>All ideas be considered and used where nessesary for the developement of the company</p>', '<p>The employee had an objective of managing moringa which was well executed but further training and knowledge development in moringa harvesting and processing will be a positive addition to his collection of exeperience and usefulness to the company.&nbsp; His further training in melia seedling production with a combination of production skills will be of help to achieve the company\'s mission and objectives.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He started as a casual worker and managed to become a Nursery technician. Though, there has been no production, he has shown great technical skills by producing successfully Moringa for the first time in our nursery and planting them out in the nursery compund. He still needs to improve on his communication and be more open in expressing his views.</p>', '2021-11-10 15:11:29', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(56, 59, 72, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . Indeed this company has enabled me to achieve a lot in\r\nmy personal daily activities and even during this covid outbreak most companies\r\nlaid off workers but we have been at work all through. I am committed towards\r\nmy work and I will always strive towards achieving my assigned duties as\r\nalready agreed upon by the supervisor.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>The employee has potential in doing hi work. He had some weakness at the beginning of the year in terms of task rates management but is ready for improvement. He has agreed to improve in his weakness and through training in tree counting will be able to perform the task.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Like the rest of the PMS, he has been involved in various maintenance activities in which he is skilled. These have been done well. It is however should be noted that Mutemi was still part of the maintenance team that did not give correct figures at the beginning of the year. He must therefore ensure that this doesn\'t happen again in the future by understanding why it is a must that correct information is submitted.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 15:29:23', '2022-05-20 16:23:42'),
(57, 127, 39, '<p>It is a great privilege and honour that the company has offered to serve in this position. as a fast growing company, continuous growth of employees is also key to the company development</p>', '<p>The effort exhibited by team is remarkable partly due to January\'s persistence. His good team playing ability and deliverance of GIC main mandate of greening schools is extemporal.&nbsp; However, there is a need to improve his communication skill for the betterment of his career.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has done well in the GIC program. However, like the rest of the GIC team he needs to interact more with the rest of the BGF team within the 7 forks.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-10 15:34:36', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(58, 128, 41, 'I wish to thank you the BGF management for continuous improvement on company\'s working systems. However, the company may also create an environment for innovation in forestry sector across the organization structure for better forest management and establishment.', '<p>Samuel has been a strong implementer and a believer of the schools green initiative challenge.&nbsp; Through his team building skills and self drive, the initiative has complimented his team with a good survival in the phases prior.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Samuel has caught on well with the rest of the GIC team and has a great passion for what he does. He also needs to interact more with the rest of the BGF staff within the 7 forks area.</p>', '2021-11-10 18:10:54', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(59, 111, 74, '<p>According to my point of view evaluation was fair and i do thank my supervisor and the entire company for the chance granted.</p>', '<p>Improved on having sense of self assessment, he understands his weaknesses and committed to correct where necessary in order to get work efficiency. He needs to improve on attitude towards achieving set targets.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>some issues raised like transport for workers is being looked upon by the management and shall be addressed in due time as it is not as straightforward as it appears. Salary increment is not automatic.</p>', '2021-11-11 07:32:04', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(60, 121, 66, '<p>Evaluation has been good and interactive. The process has showed me areas of weaknesses, strength and areas to improve on. Special thanks to my supervisor for always providing all supportive requirements for smooth and efficient running of my activities. Thanks to my department and entire organization for standing with all employees during this time of COVID 19 pandemic.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Tobias has shown great deal of interest of acquiring more knowledge, skills and experience of Melia production. Mortality in the nursery is a challenge&nbsp; and to correct this he has identified pathology as one of the areas he needs training. He is committed and a good in teamwork, however he needs to improve on punctuality in reporting and meeting set deadlines.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>There has not been much activity in the nursery other than Moringa and maintenance of structures. Despite of this, Tobias has a great attitude towards his work. However, a lot could have been done within this time by him in order to gain more skills and knowledge in production so that by the time we start production again, we would be better at it. Tobias should also be less idealistic and more of a doer by taking initiative. Having ideas alone is not enough, they must be actualised in trials.</p>', '2021-11-11 07:46:49', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
(61, 57, 75, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">First I have to thank the\r\ncompany for this far . When I was sick I was given some time off, got medication and then taken back. I am grateful and committed to do my work diligently as agreed by my supervisor.</span></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The employee has been\r\ncommitted to his work for the time I have known him, He however had weakness at\r\nthe beginning of the year in terms of time management which he accepts as a mistake and willing to change. Given a chance as someone who accepts his mistakes and improves on them, he can do better.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>he seems to have experience and knowledge about all the maintenance activities in the plantation. He should however aim to increase his skills in the maintenance activities and not nursery activities as pointed out in section 3 above.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-11 07:48:48', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(62, 8, 25, '<p>1. This year has been challenging and full of continuous improvement which is really motivating. Seeing things getting better, achieving more in short period, doing more with a small budget, has been fulfilling.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>We believe Lawrence is doing a great job as has been the case year after year. He is persistent and bites himself into a job until done. He has also grown in matters of managing people, not only in numbers but also in understanding the dynamics of managing. The last year was indeed challenging but Finance and operations in fact improved their workings. Today M&amp;E is also under finance (it should have been straight from the beginning) and we already see results. All over we can say that in Lawrence we have a great leader.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See supervisor comments</p>', '2021-11-11 08:49:27', '2022-05-20 16:21:40'),
(63, 92, 70, 'Evaluation was good. My strengths and weakneses revealed in the process and also areas of improvement showed. Thanks to my suppervisor for standing with me and supporting me in all aspects related to my job. Thanks to the company for standing with me and other employees during this hard strike time CORONA Pandemic.&nbsp;&nbsp;', '<p>Walter is a all round, informed, honest, reliable and hard working employee. He is among the best performing curently i have on site. He has been constantly requested by other departments within the company for assigning of special tasks due to his competencies. He is encouraged to continue with the same spirit of job he has established.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Walter is versatile and multiskilled in activities relating to both forestry and operations. He should however be able to honestly point out things that are not ok and need to improve even if it is about his supervisor.</p>', '2021-11-11 09:46:22', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
(64, 119, 76, '<p>The discussion was detailed and informative in terms of pointing out areas to improve on in order to achieve impressive results.&nbsp;<br></p>', '<p>For the year, Stephen concentrated on maintenance and plantation stock verification exercise. From this exercise he has been able to streamline his team to be more accountable about the figures of all activities they undertake and of the stocks. Mortality was still a problem in the&nbsp; plantation due to different causes including buffaloes damage. However, going forward it is expected that the team will work towards zero mortality and some measures are already being put in&nbsp; place such an electric fence round the plantation.&nbsp;</p><p>He is also expected to make better plans based on the reality on the ground and have periodic checks (daily, weekly, monthly, quarterly and yearly) to ensure the company meets the sites objectives thereby achieving its mission and vision.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Stephen has shown great technical skills in plantation forestry by managing to learn fast and adapting on the job. He has been able to manage people in a difficult environment with all kinds of challenges from the community and the wild animals. This is commendable. However, these qualities should now be channeled into giving the desired results of zero mortality in the plantation. He, therefore, needs to improve in the following areas:</p><p>1. Planning and continuous monitoring. Managing a plantation is not just about field work, but also thorough planning and continuous checks to ensure the activities are implemented and correctly.</p><p>2. Be more open to criticism and take it positively as an opportunity for improvement.</p><p>3. Communication</p><p>4. Be tougher with your team, pointing out their mistakes and punishing these mistakes as per the HR policy rather than trying to be nice to them or protecting them and ending up taking blame for other peoples mistakes.</p>', '2021-11-11 11:31:04', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
(65, 123, 78, '<p>I feel delighted for having been given an opportunity through my role as an SLO to demonstrate my skills in helping the company achieve its mission and vision. It is also an honour to have been selected to attend a drone training at KENDRONE LTD-Mombasa. I thank the company abundantly.<br></p>', '<p>Staff with a lot of potential and a positive attitude.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>You have potential to grow and achieve more. Keep working hard.</p>', '2021-11-11 12:40:58', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(66, 33, 80, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">The year\r\nhas been of corrections to ensure all aspects of the project/s go on well as\r\nplanned going forward. A lot of training has been received all aligned to the\r\ncompanyâ€™s mission and vision and a lot of explanations and elaborations done e.g.,\r\nwhy we need to always have the correct stock figures from the nursery to the\r\nplantation. The importance of communication and doing things right the first\r\ntime has also been elaborated and insisted on the team.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif\">This I\r\ncan attest has had a positive effect to me and the team and we are ready to\r\ntake on the coming yearâ€™s targets while maintaining and improving systems set\r\nin place to achieve the companyâ€™s objectives.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>N/A</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>There have been changes over the months in the objectives and the focus was on maintenance of the plantations, tree stock verification, and correction of all areas we have had challenges in. This required that plans are made for the maintenance activities, the teams being supervised are checked, guided accordingly, and made to understand the importance of the activities being carried out and how all these are aligned with the company\'s vision, mission, and short term objectives. Some of these activities were done well like stock verification in Kiambere, taking charge in the absence of a supervisor in Kiambere, improved pruning and cleaning by the teams involved. Some areas that had gaps but were addressed later in the year included the importance of tree counting and how all the activities we do are linked to the company\'s vision and mission. This however is something he must continuously address to his team. Other areas that need to be improved upon are as follows:</p><p>1. Managing of plans:- It is not enough to make a plan but they must be constantly followed up and implemented.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Being objective:- Focus should be on achieving the set objectives. Being nice or lenient to your team cannot help him in achieving the agreed-upon objectives. He should spend less time in back and forth explanations with his team that lead to delays in some instances and indecisiveness. Should focus on facts.</p><p>3. He needs to work towards doing more within his capacity so that he can grow as a manager. He should not limit himself to simply just taking instructions, , relaying information or simply following up with issues. At his level, he should put more initiative in thinking or motivating his teams of solutions to improve his domain.&nbsp;</p><p>4. Communication has also been an issue, however, this has been emphasized largely this year but should be something that he constantly addresses.</p><p>5. Delegating of tasks should be improved because this is one of the ways he can help his team grow in capacity.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-11 13:39:32', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(67, 37, 79, '<p>Generally, I\'ve improved but I still need to improve on the improvable areas</p>', '<p>There has been a lot of improvement in the department due to your positive attitude and hard work. There is room for improvement. Keep it up.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The department is on upward trend and your contribution if felt. Improve on the areas highlighted in the evaluation</p>', '2021-11-11 14:25:39', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(68, 36, 81, '<p>Am proud with the improvement have mad this year in this project especially in planning and organization though much need to be done to make sure proper planning is in place to accomplish the activities in hand. I do believe this possible not being alone but working as a team&nbsp; with other departments and more importantly my team in front line.</p><p>I will work on my weak areas and improve on them; communication, Drive for results, convenient. To improve on these areas, I will work closely with my supervisor and my team in the project&nbsp;</p>', '<p>N/A</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He has a better understanding of the farmer\'s program than he did at the end of last year. Much has not been done this year with regards to recruitment, group formation, production, planting, and training hence not much can be said about these aspects. However, with the checking of records, correcting farmer data, and managing of teams that were implementing these activities, a lot came out. It was clear that the teams in the field had not been doing their job truthfully or with the required commitment. This was hugely because of weak leadership especially in Uganda, lack of proper checks, lack of understanding of the importance of providing correct information, poor planning, or good planning with no clear structure for checking and correcting. Most of these issues have however since been identified and corrected but must continuously be monitored to prevent a backslide. Alex needs to put more effort into acquiring agro-forestry knowledge that shall help him easily find solutions for the issues we have in the farmers\' program. He needs to not only be more in the field but these visits must also create a significant impact. He must also improve at planning so that he can balance time between Uganda project and the Dokolo project. Too much time has been put into Dokolo and to some extent neglecting 7 forks.&nbsp;</p>', '2021-11-11 15:38:53', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(69, 5, 10, '<p>am grateful for working&nbsp; with Betterglobe forestry company and Acquired much knowledge&nbsp; in outgrowers programme&nbsp; in asal areas</p>', '<p>Onesmus has played an intergral role in dormant group reaction that is currently ongoing.</p><p>through his good mastery of the local language, he is able to interact with the young and the elderly in the groups.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Onesmus has been one of the most committed staff in the 7 forks team. From the vetting exercise, he showed that he had a passion for the job (groups formation, training and persuading farmers). However, like most of his team members, he still does not understand why it\'s important for us to count trees. He also needs to be able to connect his role on the job to what the company has as the vision and mission. That way, he will be able to use his strengths to ensure that all the trees that we plant survive.</p>', '2021-11-12 08:30:01', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
(70, 2, 60, '<p>For the years i have been at BGF I have learnt a lot from my Supervisor and my colleagues hence improved on my line of duty and service to the company.</p>', '<p>Alex has proven a valuable asset and he has grown in a job that was new in the first place. He has integrated perfectly in BGF and his support in matters of APP implementation, trainings, support and testing have hugely benefitted the company.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See supervisor comments</p>', '2021-11-12 08:53:30', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
(71, 77, 82, '<p>The discussion has enlighten me on my performance and where to improve. I thank the company for&nbsp; the bonus they gave me.<br></p>', '<p>Employee has demonstrated positive attitude towards work. He has in many instances aired out ideas that have impacted the decisions of the management in a positive way. E.g. The starting point of the electric fence.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Good work. Keep it up.</p>', '2021-11-12 10:25:03', '2022-05-20 16:23:43'),
(72, 93, 4, '<p>The evaluation process was interesting and detailed to get and address the needs of workers. i have learn my strengths and weakeness, thus provide commitment towards improving on them.</p>', '<p>Leonard is a great team player, dynamic, result oriented, have self drive and positive attitude towards any task assigned. He have good relationship with workers that he manages and do instill positive inspirational work spirit. However, he needs to improve on data reporting and verification skills on submitted results.</p><p>He have to take record on every tree lost through any kind of mortality in order to initiate their replacement for the company to get to zero mortality. Communicate on plantation dynamics to facilitate making of informed schedules and plans for approprite management of existing plantation areas.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Leonard has improved technically over the years, has gained more confidence and trust from the people that he supervises. Once a technician for both the establishment and maintenance but moved to the establishment after an analysis showed that the plantation area was too vast for one person. It should be noted, however, him having been directly responsible for plantations activities in the past few years he should have known the exact status of the seedling stock and provided accurate information or reported that there were some malpractices, Checked better the people that did the tree counting to ensure that they did it correctly and provided the correct information. The mortality and deliberate misinformation by staff on figures is the biggest non-conformance in the company and hence he needs to reconcile with this fact and going forward address this.</p>', '2021-11-12 10:50:32', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
(73, 4, 83, 'During the year, the focus was on correcting the issues that we have. A lot did not go well at the beginning of the year based on the analysis of the outputs done mid this year. It was an important discovery for the department as it led to taking tougher and better decisions. I am confident that at the end of this exercise we shall be able to concentrate strictly on matters relating to forestry and with desired results.&nbsp;&nbsp;', '<p>Another tough year has gone by but this one can be considered as the one that will make the difference for the future. When all will have been addressed and corrected a solid foundation for planting and survival of the trees will have been achieved.&nbsp; Samuel as the Executive Director of Forestry is the right person for spearheading the forestry department of the company towards the future.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See the supervisor comments.</p>', '2021-11-12 12:00:44', '2022-05-20 16:21:39'),
(74, 1, 63, '<p>A career in Technology takes time to master and it\'s a perishable skill that requires constant learning and support which the organization has ensured is accessible.</p><p>With continuous projects and the ability to solve more problems, we will end up in some place where we can be able to solve our problems using Machine learning possibly in the next 5 years to come</p>', '<p>Michael has done a great job in integrating into BGF and taking responsibility for challenging tasks. We will support his drive and together find a balance between performing (creating new applications) and learning which we agree is absolutely necessary.<br>It is also observed that he has a vision for the future that matches the direction in which the company needs to go.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See supervisor comments</p>', '2021-11-12 13:12:34', '2022-05-20 16:21:38'),
(75, 105, 84, 'The discussion with the supervisor has been productive. I have learnt areas of improvement and areas that I need to keep up the good work. I thank the company for allowing me to work even within this Corona pandemic. I lastly request for a salary raise after having served for 5years.<br>', '<p>The employee has a lot of potential and positive energy towards work.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Keep it up and work harder to achieve more.</p>', '2021-11-13 10:15:18', '2022-05-20 16:23:46'),
(76, 124, 85, '<p>Company to add more employees. Eg. Tractor drivers. I also thank the company for confirming me on permanent basis as a tractor driver.<br></p>', '<p>Worker is very hardworking. He has been a key player in the construction of the electric fence having been the 1st person to grasp the installation process in spite of his low academic qualifications. He is an important asset in the operations team on site.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Keep it up and work harder to achieve more.</p><p>You have the potential.</p>', '2021-11-15 08:30:29', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(77, 90, 86, '<p>I have learned a lot and know my week point now i can perform better.</p>', '<p>A self-motivated staff with a positive attitude. Impressed by his computer knowledge.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The company believes in you to deliver on your work. Keep it up.</p>', '2021-11-15 10:30:20', '2022-05-20 16:23:44'),
(78, 125, 87, '<p>Having gone to training at Sensei as a plant Operator, I request the company to be allowing me to work with the CAT Operators as an assistant to familiarize myself with the machines as well. I secondly thank the company for confirming me as a permanent staff member. I promise to continue working hard to assist the company meet its objective.<br></p>', '<p>Worker is honest and has the willingness to learn on the job. He achieved most of his set targets in mechanical cleaning. He did not record any breakdowns on the tractor. (KTCB 153X)<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Keep up the good job.</p>', '2021-11-15 12:54:59', '2022-05-20 16:23:49'),
(79, 118, 88, '<p>1. I thank the company for doing a good job in employing me even within the corona pandemic. I also thank the company for a good interaction with Head Office managers on site. I request the company for a salary raise.<br></p>', '<p>Employee is highly motivated and grateful for being part of the company.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Good job</p>', '2021-11-16 07:46:32', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
(80, 116, 89, '<p>I thank the company for all the good job they\'ve done this year and encourage them to put in more effort to the realization of its vision and mission as per my discussion with the supervisor. Lastly, I thank the company for the position I am as a Driver/Mechanic.<br></p>', '<p>The employee has shown positive energy towards work. He is highly motivated and has played a key role in machine repairs on site as per our discussion.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Keep up the good work and aim to achieve higher results.</p>', '2021-11-16 10:38:29', '2022-05-20 16:23:47'),
(81, 117, 16, '<ol><li>Discussion was successful and areas that need improvement has been enlightened.</li></ol>', 'Employee has significantly improved on his attitude. He is looking forward to achieve the objectives he did not meet this year.<br>', NULL, NULL, '<p>You have the potential to achieve more. The company recognizes your work and efforts to get work done. Work on your weak areas and Keep up the good work.</p>', '2021-11-17 08:00:21', '2022-05-20 16:23:48'),
(82, 41, 91, '<p>Maintaining team work and proper communication, continuous research is required to stay up to date with the requirements of my position.</p>', '<p>Keep it up, there is still room for improvement</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>You have much improved over the past period. Keep improving and work on the points that require improvement. You have need to gain more experience in accounting and good understanding of the IAS and IFRs, accounting principles that guide well in your current role.</p><p>Keep it up.</p>', '2021-11-17 13:44:42', '2022-05-20 16:23:41'),
(83, 38, 73, '<p>The evaluation session was very interactive.&nbsp; I have learnt a lot and the areas that need improvement. Operations work is very involving but my I\'m doing my best to understand everything to ensure we have smooth Operations.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>We expect you to swiftly grasp the operations and be able to lead the department and offer the solutions when needed. </p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">There has been improvement from the last evaluation which is a good trend. However there is still room for improvement.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">KEEP IT UP.<br></span><br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>You are new in the position (7Months) and we trust you are doing your best to have a grip on operations department. We expect things to only get better.</p>', '2021-11-18 10:01:55', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(84, 30, 92, '<p>I have gotten the right support and strive to give my all and be better</p>', '<p>You have really improved but you still need to work on the highlighted areas.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>This year has been low in terms of postings and it was a year to clean up and make corrections in accounts. This has improved from the previous year. We however still have work to do in accounts.</p><p>Keep the upward trend.</p>', '2021-11-18 13:17:48', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(85, 34, 93, '<p>HR Department was a new field to me but the support of my supervisor has made me improve on many areas .Also other departments have now understood the importance of the department and now I am good. I love the job.</p>', '<p>Lydia is a valuable member of the MAnagement team. The HR department is headed with the right spirit and is very efficient. The few improvable fields are nothing to worry about as they are normal. The integration of the HR department in BGF was completed seamlessly and staff is aware of its importance. Keep it up Lydia!</p>', NULL, NULL, 'See supervisor', '2021-11-18 14:02:05', '2022-05-20 16:21:45'),
(86, 31, 90, '<p>The year 2021 has focused on verification of data for which M&amp;E has been pivotal. We foresee a year of more impact in 2022. </p><p>The commitment received from management shall go a long way in achieving the objectives of Zero non-conformances.</p>', '<p>The department has been instrumental in complimenting the management to achieve continuous improvement in all departments. The mindset of staff has also changed and the reception of M&amp;E by other departments has improved.&nbsp;</p><p>The reliability of the M&amp;E work by Management has also improved.</p><p>Keep it up.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The performance of the department is pivotal to the achievement of the company Vision and Mission.</p><p>Keep up the good work.</p>', '2021-11-19 07:01:02', '2022-05-20 16:21:44'),
(87, 129, 94, '<p>I have understood areas that I need to improve to achieve my objectives</p>', '<p>Ann is motivated but she needs to improve on how she relates to people and attitude in order to do her job well.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See above</p>', '2021-12-01 10:19:58', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(88, 138, 98, 'I would love to keep working with Better GLOBE FORESTRY.', '<p>N/a</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Halima has shown resilience while doing the inventory activity by the fact that the working conditions are fairly difficult and that she was a fresh graduate. A fast learner, good communicator and shows great potential if given greater responsibilities within the company.</p>', '2022-01-06 13:03:07', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(89, 139, 97, 'I\'ve been able to comply with the company\'s policies under my contract with the company and achieved the targets. I\'m ready for similar or bigger tasks and assignments if offered by the company.&nbsp;', '<p>N/A</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Kelvin has done well in the activity of data collection in spite of him being a fresh graduate. He is a good communicator and showed drive for results. With his colleague, they exhibited great teamwork and adaptability to the tough field conditions. He is also a quick learner would and shows potential for handling greater responsibilities within the company.</p>', '2022-01-06 13:31:29', '2022-05-20 16:23:50'),
(90, 140, 100, '<p>When all the corrective action requests raised are responded and cleared, the farmers database shall be be without errors.</p>', '<p>Moses requires alot of support in&nbsp; the basic use of computer and some of the applications. When that gap is filled, he shall have the confidence too undertake all tasks related to data and computing which is most of the tasks at BGF. We have gone more digital than ever.&nbsp;</p><p>He is good at field work needs to be tried in reporting which at the moment is hampered by computer literacy.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He lacks the basics of a good employee. He is disorganized, does not plan, is not punctual and he is not computer. He had the opportunity to learn and improve in the last 3 months and it is evident from his evaluation, he did not learn a lot. He also does not follow instructions and does not communicate when he is&nbsp; needed to do so. The supervisor has to constantly remind him to share reports and results.</p><p>This makes him not ideal for this job.</p>', '2022-04-27 15:49:29', '2022-05-20 16:23:51'),
(91, 141, 101, 'FSC was new field for me and I got to learn a lot from my supervisor through continuous training. Generally BGF is a great place for professional growth as I had a chance to learn something new and I am ready to learn more. I would like to get a training on FSC provided by soil association of Kenya.', '<p>Halima has coped well despite having no prior experience in FSC. She grasped the concepts of FSC quite well without any formal training but through mostly self learning. This is proof that she has great potential in this field and maybe even other sections within the company if given the responsibility.&nbsp; More training for her will indeed be needed not just about FSC but also the intricacies of the BGF projects and how the company works. This shall put her in an even better position to identify gaps that are not usually obvious and have them closed as we inch closer to certification.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Same as above in the supervisors\' comments section.&nbsp;', '2022-06-10 17:14:44', '2022-06-10 17:36:09'),
(92, 142, 102, '<p>Firstly I have to thank the company for this opportunity. From the interactions with other security guards have managed to learn all the corners of the plantation and i look forward to improve on the identified weakness.</p>', '<p>However, the employee is the only lady in the team she has shown potential in delivering the work and has also worked in ensuring the team ins united and work towards achieving the company\'s goals.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">The above Employee is good in his duties however she needs improve on the points scored 3 and below. She also needs to improve on performance based on the discussion during the evaluation. She has the potential and can do Better.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">The security as a whole needs training on Security.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We recommend him for the JOB.</p>', '2022-08-03 12:01:29', '2022-08-17 14:07:17'),
(93, 144, 104, '<p>I can continuously improve on my day to day tasks, and integrate more with my colleagues.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Joel has made a good start at the company. He was thrown in and immediately had to design and layout the magazine which he fulfilled satisfyingly. Now, he has to give more attention to sales, applying his networks. Also, he will now start knowing more about forestry and be creative in how to improve the readability of the magazine. I wish him a good continuation.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Same as supervisor</p>', '2022-08-10 12:14:32', '2022-08-11 18:16:13'),
(94, 143, 103, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\">Firstly, I must\r\nthank the company for this opportunity for allowing me to join Kiambere team and\r\nI appreciate the whole team in Kambere as well for good orientation and for ensuring\r\nI got a better training to deliver the roles am expected to deliver as one of the security personnel.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\">I look forward\r\nto improving on the identified gaps during this discussion to ensure we protect\r\nthe whole plantation as a team, and the planted trees survives.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Lastly the suggestion\r\nI would like to make is if itâ€™s possible to cut down the Baobab tree next to\r\nthe site office, which is destroying the officeâ€™s roof. The branch of the\r\ntree normally brakes off easily and this has been hitting the iron sheet which I think will destroy the roof.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\">&nbsp;The employee\r\nhas a potential of working as a security guard and for the past three months he\r\nhas been able to understand the whole plantation including different&nbsp; &nbsp;compartments/blocks.<o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">He however needs\r\nto work hand in hand with the whole security team to prevent cases of theft which we\r\nhave observed in site for the past one month.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The employee\r\nalso needs to improve on his communication since most of the mistake recorded\r\nin site are because of communication breakdowns in site.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;line-height:normal\"><o:p></o:p></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">The above Employee is good in his duties however he needs improve on the points scored 3 and below. He also needs to improve on performance based on the discussion during the evaluation. He has the potential and can do Better.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">The security as a whole needs training on Security.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We recommend him for the JOB.</p>', '2022-08-13 13:00:23', '2022-08-17 14:05:16');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(95, 146, 106, '<p>I would like to encourage my supervisors to work together to ensure the security work is done accordingly.</p>', '<p>The employee needs to communicate promptly and report any case for proper decision making. The Assistant head of security also needs to learn the characters of all workers in site both PMS and&nbsp; Security personnel to ensure the company\'s properties are protected all the time.</p><p>The employee also needs to share the knowledge acquired as a trained security guards with other security&nbsp; team for effective performance.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The above Employee is good in his duties however he needs improve on the points scored 3 and below. He has the potential and can do Better.</p><p>The security as a whole needs training on Security.</p><p>We recommend him for the JOB.</p>', '2022-08-17 13:30:22', '2022-08-17 13:56:07'),
(96, 147, 107, '<p>1. I intend to address the issue of absenteeism and this is projected to be seen in a month\'s time. <br></p><p>2. I thank the company for offering me an opportunity to serve.<br></p>', 'To continuously work as a team with the Ass. HOS and uplift the performance of the whole security team.<br>', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">There is great improvement in the last 3 months however they can do.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">They require follow up and training.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We recommend them for for the JOB.</p>', '2022-08-19 13:11:04', '2022-08-19 16:12:20'),
(97, 148, 109, '<p>1.&nbsp; I thank the company for giving me a job.</p><p>2. Processing of requests has to improve. E.g. Donkey medicines.<br></p><p>3. I\'ll train my team in areas that I have not performed well in this evaluation for better results.<br></p>', '<p>Employee has the willingness to learn. He has a good attitude. He has shown improvement from the last assessment. He should work more on the areas highlighted and are showing weakness to have a team that is performing as expected.<br></p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>There is great improvement in the last 3 months however they can do.</p><p>They require follow up and training.</p><p>We recommend them for for the JOB.</p>', '2022-08-19 15:55:45', '2022-08-19 16:11:48'),
(98, 17, 110, '<p>From the discussion, I\'m able to identify the areas that need improvement for maximum output.</p>', '<p>You are on the right trajectory on your job, right attitude, and you can do better. You need to work on the areas highlighted for improvement in section one.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>He is good with the right attitude and fast to learn.</p><p>I recommend him for the job.</p>', '2022-09-01 11:49:23', '2022-09-07 14:23:54'),
(99, 73, 112, '<p>First I would like to thank the company for the opportunity to join this team in ensuring the company goals and objectives are achieved</p><p>&nbsp;Through this discussion, we have identified that most of the losses recorded in site were due to lack of patrols and some due to poor handing over of duty by all guards. We need to work as a team to ensure the company properties are well protected at all time.</p><p>To ensure this is also done, I would request the management team to employ more task force to ensure all the blocks has at least a guard especially during the night</p>', '<p>The employee has proven to be well dedicated to his work and only need to ensure he works with the team to bridge the identified gaps and ensure these theft cases in site are minimized.</p><p>The team in general also need special training in line with security work for better performance.</p>', '<p>Employee needs to point out any issues he is facing for them to be resolved on time, unresolved issues end up affecting employee performance which is later translated to the whole team.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Security in Kiambere is a problem although it has improved. </p><p>Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p>You need to improve on security.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-07 17:52:19', '2022-11-15 18:32:53'),
(100, 123, 118, '<p>Based on my evaluation report, I am going to work on my shortcomings including strict adherence to deadlines to have a better assessment in the next evaluation.<br></p>', '<p>You have to work on your efficiency. You are partially there, but you need to do better.<br></p>', '<p>The SLM needs to improve on his punctuality, he rarely observes deadlines given on reports, assignments and minutes.</p><p>Management of the security team needs to be worked on. We have many cases of lateness and absenteeism in the team which affects overall performance of the security team.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Despite having few activities on site, your performance has not improved and with many warnings to your teams.</p><p>Kindly work on your weak areas and improve your performance.</p>', '2022-11-08 13:02:42', '2022-11-14 18:53:28'),
(101, 83, 120, '<p>Evaluation process was good. i have learnt my weaknessess and strengths. i will make remarkable effort to improve on my weaknesses.</p>', '<p>Ronald is an outgoing staff, he is always ready to sacrifice his time to company benefit. He has been instrumental staff on seedling survival through provision of his noble skills on plumbing works and water pump operations. i have no doubt to recommend him as a valuable staff to the company.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>1</p>', '2022-11-08 13:27:52', '2022-11-10 11:25:55'),
(102, 28, 117, 'I can improve on all my weak areas.', '<p>Improvement noted but you can still do better.</p><p>A note is expected from you in guiding the security team to ensure that they are conversant with the digital apps i.e., communication app and digital OB recording.</p>', '<p>Improve on communication- Communication and updates of all happenings in the site to the OM should be timely.</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>You have the potential.</p><p>Improve on the weak areas that are pulling you down such as communication.</p>', '2022-11-08 14:49:01', '2022-11-14 17:56:46'),
(103, 29, 122, '<p>I have&nbsp; improved on the mark and still hope for more improvement on the areas that i did not do well.much as production was not going on i have appriciated the management decison to take me to farmers programe for a while that has exposed more to the field.</p>', '<p>There was no seedling production this year which is the employee\'s major role. However, he was assigned a special task of checking/verifying and grouping farmers which was successfully done. This has shown that he is flexible and able to execute any other task assigned to him related to the company\'s mission. There is still room for improvement in&nbsp; communication and managing people which are key in seedling production when it resumes. On addition to trainings recieved this year, he further needs refresher trainings in conflict management and resolution.</p>', '<p>See HOD comments</p>', '2022-11-18', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">New in field work: - He had a\r\ndifficult time at the start but adjusted well with guidance from his supervisor.\r\nIt was important that he joined the rest of the team in the field as there was\r\nnot activity in the nursery. This is added experience and skills.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Need for regular communication by\r\nsupervisor:- The staff has always been encouraged to seek information through\r\nother avenues if they feel they are not satisfied by the communication of their\r\nsupervisors.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><span style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\">c.&nbsp; &nbsp; A general observation is that some responses or comments by Bonny are not completely clear making it difficult to ascertain what he really meant. This being said, it is important that the reviewing supervisor makes the evaluation exercise an open discussion in which the employee being reviewed feels free to express themselves. This exercise is not an exam but should be a beneficial exercise, for both the staff and the supervisor.</span><br></p>', '2022-11-08 14:58:02', '2022-11-22 09:42:19'),
(104, 78, 121, '<p>Evaluation is good since it highlights the areas worked well as well as those areas that need improvement. Interaction has been good and going forward I am going to improve on the areas of weakness.</p>', '<p>He is discipline and hardworking staff, However, he should improve on honesty and communication.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>1. Communication:- From the assessment of the comments and reviews by both the Supervisor and the employee, there seems to be a communication breakdown both ways. The supervisor must give clear instructions with explanations as to why things have to be done in a certain way for the Sulubu to do his tasks with the seriousness they deserve. The Supervisor must also follow up constantly and give feedback to Sulubu so that corrections can be done immediately.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Lack of activity in the nursery leading to loss of skills/experience:-&nbsp; A skill cannot be lost simply because of lack of activity. however, Sulubu must be proactive and bring such issues up in the course of the year so that they are addressed immediately rather than waiting until the end of the year to bring them up.&nbsp;</p><p>3.&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff.</span></p><p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: -18pt; font-size: 0.875rem;\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-08 15:11:38', '2022-11-10 13:08:08'),
(105, 115, 125, '<p>The evaluation was good and interactive. Willing to improve on the areas that&nbsp; was highlighted during evaluation process.</p>', '<p>Gideon is an all star staff, always willing to perform beyond expectation. He has shown encouraging attitude and zeal to learn new things. However, he needs to work on ability to guide other staff while working together to bring out quality output. I positively recommend him as a valuable staff to the company.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - Plans To\r\nmake a camp in the plantation in the future and provide a means of transport\r\nto far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by DDHR\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-08 15:19:02', '2022-11-10 13:16:27'),
(106, 10, 126, '<p>Am grateful&nbsp; to better globe forestry for giving me a chance to work in ASAL\'s, to learn and experience&nbsp; in this harsh areas also am grateful to them during this difficult times they were able to keep me, its my duty as staff to make sure the aims and objectives&nbsp; of our company are met.This is by making sure there is 100% tree survival.</p>', '<p>He is self motivated in performing his dutity he has managed to organize groups working under minimal supervision.&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Increase of staff: - Increase of\r\nstaff or replacement, shall no longer be based on rushed assumptions but\r\ncritical analysis of the workload and priorities. We shall also work more with\r\ntools, strategies and approaches that shall maximize available resources to obtain\r\noptimum results. These tools shall include farmers app that shall manage all\r\nfarmerâ€™s information, ensure all farmers are in groups and that way we do not\r\nhave to deal with individual farmers. Etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - Issues concerning\r\ncommunication can be addressed with the immediate supervisor and if that doesnâ€™t\r\nwork reported to the supervisor to the immediate supervisor. We also have a communications\r\napp where staff can raise their concerns. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Timely motorbike repairs as per the schedule\r\nand Lack of fuel: - All these arose because of the transition explained in\r\npoint (a) above. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Introducing more farmers\' incentives: - The\r\nkey to the success of this farmers\' program is not offering more incentives to\r\nfarmers. If the program is explained well to the farmers, then we would not need\r\nto even think of adding more incentives. The extension team needs to take their\r\nresponsibilities seriously and get the job done through means that shall have long-term effects and not easier lazy means that only have short-term impact.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">f.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Planting\r\ntrees with active farmer groups: - It is the responsibility of the AA to ensure\r\nthat everything is done according to the agreed-upon procedure/structures. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; g. Frequent visits by HR: - The field visits by HO\r\nstaff have been put in the plan beginning next year.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager.</p>', '2022-11-08 15:56:55', '2022-11-12 19:23:41'),
(107, 149, 116, '<p>There has been a continuous interaction of the supervisor and team members and we have been able to improve on the quality of the magazine in terms of content and outlook despite the challenges in printing.&nbsp;</p><p>With the launch of the digital subscriptions, I hope to target more of the international organizations.</p><p>Since I represent the company in Uganda, there is need for continuous interaction with the Dokolo office in order to be well conversant with the company operations.</p>', '<p>Diana continues to be of good value in the Miti operations in Uganda. She provides the interactions that keep the editorial committee dynamic and interested in the well- being of the magazine which has known the challenge of&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">(i) continuation of digital meetings, (ii) delays in producing printed copies of the magazine. Diana\'s editing qualities has improved over the past years, notably </span>English<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span>grammar.</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Sales, both of subscriptions and advertisements have to go up and this has to be bolstered by the confidence that Miti indeed is the best forestry magazine of East Africa. It is not easy to find good quality photos and this will also be worked </span>upon<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;in the months to come.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Participation in external events both inside and outside of Kampala is a requirement for further promotion of the magazine. The full </span>realization<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;of digital subscriptions has taken time in Uganda but is now accomplished and now Diana has to take maximum advantage of this opportunity.&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-11-08 16:28:46', '2022-11-08 16:28:46'),
(108, 135, 129, '<p>The evaluation process was free and fair. I commit myself to correct on the weaknesses pointed out&nbsp; during the evaluation i,e improvement on teamwork, honesty and effective management of leaves to avoid affecting forestry work plans.</p>', '<p>Elijah is a hardworker and reliable staff and can be assigned in various tasks with confidence of effectively implementing the activity with minimal supervision. He is perfect when it comes task rate achievement. I regard him as all round star and valuable staff to the company.</p><p>He has committed to improve on the highlighted issues during the evaluation process to ensure quality result output in 2023.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wild animals:- We have plans to\r\nextend the fence in an appropriate way to keep away the animals<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - Plans To\r\nmake a camp in the plantation in the future and provide a means of transport\r\nto far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by DDHR\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"1\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Training</span></font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">f.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Increase\r\nof staff: - Increase of staff shall be based on the number of activities that\r\nneed to be done. We have not had many activities in the past year. However, plans are underway to get relevant staff when we commence with the other activities\r\nthat had halted.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-08 17:26:08', '2022-11-10 13:27:59'),
(109, 90, 130, '<p>I\'m motivated with advice on how to achieve&nbsp; my duties<br></p>', '<p>A dedicated staff with positive attitude. keep up<br></p>', '<p>A self motivated staff, very good in communication and sharing daily updates.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Wachira, your have done well in your position. You have always found ways to achieve your daily targets even where you face challenges.</p><p>Work on the weak areas highlighted in your evaluation.</p>', '2022-11-08 17:53:36', '2022-11-14 19:47:34'),
(110, 37, 111, '<p>There has been an improvement this year but I need to improve on the highlighted areas</p>', '<p>There has been indeed a significant improvement on postings and reporting compared to former years. This has improved on the reliability of accounting reports. There is however room for improvement in this coming year.</p><p>Keep it up and work on the weak areas.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The department has been very supportive to other departments.</p><p>Next year, we expect a continuous improvement higher in the highlighted areas.</p>', '2022-11-08 18:58:43', '2022-11-08 19:02:09'),
(111, 35, 123, '<p>The overall session was fair and informative&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Impressed with improvement of the staff in carrying out her duties.&nbsp; Keep up!</p>', '<p>Improve on punctuality- When not visiting suppliers in the morning adhere to the reporting time.</p><p>Manage relationship with our suppliers to ensure our deliveries are done on time.</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-14', 'You can improve on your performance by working on your weak areas.', '2022-11-08 19:08:42', '2022-11-14 19:05:59'),
(112, 121, 132, '<p>Evaluation has been good, it was based on interaction and I am contented with the outcome. Special thanks for forestry department for retaining nursery team despite suspension of production. Thanks to all support departments for their support ie HR, Operations and communications.</p>', '<p>Over the period of this evaluation has been no much activities in Nursery operation but with the few activities within nursery, the employee has managed to tackle them; mapping and assessment of plus tree, participation in site manual development and management plan. all in all the road has not been smooth and the employee needs to work on his weak areas as highlighted in the interactive session of this evaluation:</p><p>1. being&nbsp; pro-active</p><p>2. moving with the change</p><p>3. taking initiatives</p><p>4. following instructions and consulting incase of information gaps</p><p>5. meeting deadlines</p><p>6. taking ownership and lead.</p><ul><li><br></li></ul>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Tobias\'s Supervisor is spot on. </p><p>In addition:</p><p>1. He needs to improve on leadership skills that way he can have a nursery team that is motivated.</p><p>2. Improve on communication skills. Should be more precise, clear, and assertive.&nbsp;</p><p>3. Should frequently check the work his staff is doing and give feedback.</p>', '2022-11-08 19:14:19', '2022-11-10 15:09:01'),
(113, 12, 134, '<p>Through the ongoing farmer group sensitization activities, farmers are willing to plant again and need to be motivated.Also to ensure that the farmers get quality seedlings on time during planting season. To add on i appreciate the company for the opportunity offered to me to serve as an agroforestry agent and therefore promise to work hard to help the company achieve its objectives.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>he is self driven in performing its duties, he has managed to activate some groups in mumoni ward and still performing its duties under minimal supervision, he is also a team leader whenever am on leave he manages the team well and ensure all activities are done as required,&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Issuing farmers seedlings that are of good\r\nquality and at the right time</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">: - we did not produce nor distribute\r\nin 2022. However, the distribution had already been streamlined the last time\r\nwe did it in 2022. Farmers were issued with seedlings in time but from your own\r\n(field reports) some farmers did not plant immediately, there were cases of\r\npoor mobilization and farmers who were issued with seedlings and had not even done\r\npitting. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools, Equipment and PPE: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards digital management/maintenance of tools, equipment and\r\nPPE to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack of them or poor\r\nquality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely replacement of\r\ntools, equipment, and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">General comment: - Anthony has shown\r\ncapacity for leadership. He has stepped in to supervise the 7 Forks team whenever\r\nthe site manager was away on leave.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-08 19:25:08', '2022-11-12 19:24:20'),
(114, 99, 135, '<p>Evaluation was well done, comparing with previous evaluation 2022 was outstanding. it highlighted positive critique that will ensure work improvement in the coming years. i.e punctuality, unnecessary absence from work and effective communication.</p>', '<p>Salim is disciplined and staff that easily follow instructions. He has thrilling attitude towards what he does and the company activities at large. however, he needs to be more vibrant and outgoing to ensure effective communication on his challenges and achievements.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-08 19:26:30', '2022-11-10 13:36:16'),
(115, 16, 136, '<p>Am grateful to BGF company for the opportunity to work for&nbsp; the period of 14 years, interacting with different&nbsp; people in different levels and also interacting with farmers.i therefore promise to work hard to ensure company achieve its objectives.</p>', '<p>John is a role model in my team he work very hard to achieve&nbsp; its targets. He is self motivated in working with farmers and has good relationship with farmer,he is a good mobilizer.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Introducing farmers incentives: - The\r\nkey to success of this farmers program is not offering more incentives to\r\nfarmers. If the program is explained well to the farmers, then we would not need\r\nto even think of adding more incentives. The extension team needs to take their\r\nresponsibilities seriously and get the job done through means that shall have long\r\nterm effect and not easier lazy means that only have short term impact.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Timely salary payment:- salary has\r\nalways been paid on time sometimes even earlier than 30<sup>th</sup>. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as requested\r\nby employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training\r\nschedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-08 20:46:59', '2022-11-12 19:25:02'),
(116, 5, 137, '<p>am grateful for working in BGF company&nbsp; as agroforestry&nbsp; agent interacting with farmers and other stakeholders has let to improvement in my career of agroforestry. Am therefore working&nbsp; hardto ensure all BGF farmers are in active groups, plant trees&nbsp; and maintain them.</p>', 'Onesmus is team player, self motivated in ensuring farmers program is whell undertaken within the community around, he is a good group mobilizer and whenever he forms a group it should have IGA to be self reliance.he works under minimal supervision to achieve its objectives.<br>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - Issues\r\nconcerning communication can be addressed with the immediate supervisor and if\r\nthat doesnâ€™t work reported to the supervisor to the immediate supervisor. We\r\nalso have a communications app where staff can raise their concerns. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as requested\r\nby employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training\r\nschedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Timely salary payment:- salary has\r\nalways been paid on time sometimes even earlier than 30<sup>th</sup>.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-08 22:27:33', '2022-11-12 19:25:54'),
(117, 150, 138, '<p>There is a serious need to ensure there is unity between workers to ensure there is conducive work environment for all. The PMS and security team to come hand in hand and in case of any problem all the Kiambere team to be part of the problem instead of one team feeling like the other team is setting up the other.</p><p>The supervisors as well need to work as a team since they show the way to their juniors, a scenario where the supervisors don\'t get along should not be there.</p>', '<p>However being aged, the employee has been obedient and committed to his duties. During security meetings twice monthly, he has been actively taking part and always urge the guards<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;to work together for effective performance and for better delivery of their responsibilities.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The whole team however need special training in line with security work for better </span>performance<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">.</span></p>', 'A dedicated and honest staff who always speaks his mind. Always pointing out misunderstanding in the security team for them to be resolved.&nbsp;', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere is a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security.</p>', '2022-11-09 10:54:36', '2022-11-15 18:34:09');
