(118, 13, 140, '<p>Well so far so good despite the challenges&nbsp; encountered, I believe&nbsp; all is not lost ,we still can recover and achieve&nbsp; our objectives,&nbsp;</p><p>However&nbsp; that to happen&nbsp; we Need&nbsp; all department&nbsp; working&nbsp; as a unit for it to be a succes.</p>', '<p>James is team player interms of field activities, he is good group mobilizer heworks hard despite the challages to achieve his objectives. he need to improve on communication&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - Issues\r\nconcerning communication can be addressed with the immediate supervisor and if\r\nthat doesnâ€™t work reported to the supervisor to the immediate supervisor. We\r\nalso have a communications app where staff can raise their concerns. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as requested\r\nby employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training\r\nschedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-09 11:41:59', '2022-11-12 19:26:38'),
(119, 117, 131, '<p>The discussion was of benefit since areas I need to improve on were highlitened by my supervisor.</p>', '<p>Employee has shown a steady improvement in his work. The attitude towards job has also improved from the last assessment. He now needs to address the areas he has not performed well for better results.</p>', '<p>Improvement noted on the employee attitude towards work.</p><p>Employee to improve on punctuality and reliability his weekly reports are rarely shared on time.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>You do not willing accept challenges as learning steps. E.g, lack of interest to learn on Petrol Engines and repair of canopies.</p><p>You should always have open mind and positive attitude to learn and find solutions to our emerging challenges in our operations.</p>', '2022-11-09 11:54:17', '2022-11-14 19:37:03'),
(120, 38, 124, '<p>I have taken note of the areas which need improvement and I will work on them.</p><p>I\'m grateful to my supervisor for continuously pushing me to maximize my potential.</p>', '<p>There is always room for continuous improvement in every process.</p><p>During the past one year, you have shown great improvement on your managerial abilities.</p><p>We expect that the areas highlighted for improvement shall improve in the coming year.</p>', '<p>N/A</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>You have shown an understanding and improvement in the performance of your duties.</p><p>Keep it up.</p>', '2022-11-09 12:09:34', '2022-11-14 17:35:29'),
(121, 110, 139, '<p>The evaluation process was fair. i have learnt areas to improve on and i am committed to correct for better results in 2023.</p>', '<p>Barisa is a skillful staff when comes to trained aspects areas and always willing to learn more concerning forestry activities. However, he needs to improve on communication skills for the betterment of daily assigned activities.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wild animals:- We have plans to\r\nextend the fence in an appropriate way to keep away the animals<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - Plans To\r\nmake a camp in the plantation in the future and providing a means of transport\r\nto far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by DDHR\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; text-indent: -18pt;\">e. Slow response to accidents/injuries:- All teams\r\nusing tools in offsite locations within the plantations should have a portable\r\nfirst aid kit and at least one person that is trained on administering first\r\naid</span></p>', '2022-11-09 13:09:55', '2022-11-10 13:52:58'),
(122, 15, 141, '<p>Am so grateful and wishes to sincerely acknowledge the BGF fraternity for allowing and giving&nbsp; me opportunity to work&nbsp; with&nbsp; them.</p>', '<p>Arshiphord is a performer in field activities, he was allacated some dormant groups the current area of operation he has managed to reactivate them. He only need to improve on communication otherwise he can perform better.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - Issues\r\nconcerning communication can be addressed with the immediate supervisor and if\r\nthat doesnâ€™t work reported to the supervisor to the immediate supervisor. We\r\nalso have a communications app where staff can raise their concerns. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools, Equipment and PPE: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards digital management/maintenance of tools, equipment and\r\nPPE to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack of them or poor\r\nquality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely replacement of\r\ntools, equipment, and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as requested\r\nby employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training\r\nschedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">However, the Knowledge requirement\r\nby Arshiphord in section three is questionable, Arshiphord says he needs a\r\ndegree or diploma in his field. However, in his CV during application for this\r\njob he indicated that he had a Diploma in forestry from Londiani and on top of\r\nthat a BSc. In Environmental science from Egerton. Were these fake\r\ncertificates?<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-09 14:10:53', '2022-11-12 19:27:05'),
(123, 64, 143, '<p>Firstly I would urge my supervisors to ensure the team is united as we had done from last year. The past few months we have noted a situation where the whole team are divided such that when an incident occurs and a PMS or a security personnel has to report, the unaffected team feels as if they are being set up which should not be the case.</p><p>Through unity I believe, we will ensure that seedlings planted will certainly survives and the objective of the company will be achieved which is the main goal for all staff.</p>', '<p>The employee has been well disciplined in his work. He has been taking active role in production of improved seedlings and different maintenance activities delegated for supervision in several occasions when FT is not around. During last years evaluation he had major problem with punctuality but he has improved on it and there still room for more improvement.</p><p> More effort however, is still needed in nursery production where he has skill and experience since from next year we will be producing more seedlings and we have to reduce mortality recorded during improved seedlings production this year.<br></p>', '<p>On tools and equipment, a schedule of replacement after assessment is available and a&nbsp; system of maintenance put in place where maintenance of all tools for planned activities is done weekly. Provision of extra tools to be planned in accordance to planned activities.</p><p>Teamwork is important for targets achievement, workers are free and encouraged to present their grievances to the site responsible (FT) for resolution to enhance unity among them and foster team work.&nbsp;</p><p>On replacement of PMS who retire, addition into the work force is need based according to planned activities. When the need arises according to planned activities a decision will be made on engaging more workers both on permanent and temporary basis.&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">The employee years of of service are 5 years and not 0.5 as indicated above.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Theft and discord among workers:-\r\nthe company is working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the\r\nright positions in which they have the capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly\r\nand, or prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"1\"> Training</font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;shall be mandatory as\r\nrequested by employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training\r\nschedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><br></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:54.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2022-11-09 14:21:31', '2022-11-11 18:44:20'),
(124, 105, 142, '<p>The discussion has been informative. I am looking forward to addressing the issues raised by my supervisor.<br></p>', '<p>Worker has shown improvement from the last assessment. Your self motivation on the job is okay keep it up. Work on addressing the three key issues discussed&nbsp; that needs your attention.<br></p>', '<p>Obedient and disciplined employee who always follow instructions. With slowed operation activities he was moved from operations department to M&amp;E department to assist in tree counting and he took it very positively. He fitted in very fast and adjusted to performing the task.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>You are always positive with work and have the right attitude.</p><p>Keep it up.</p>', '2022-11-09 14:51:51', '2022-11-14 19:56:47'),
(125, 95, 144, '<p>The evaluation process was good, i have noted the positive critiques e.g on attitude and drive for the results. Much improvement will be notice by end 2023.</p>', '<p>Komora have expressed himself very well on all issues raised during the evaluation process, he is well conversant with how his roles relates to the company vision and mission. However, he needs to improve on his communication skills and increase his reliability scope by having self motivation to learn other machines operations such as power saw, this will be instrumental during thinning and harvesting.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by DDHR\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><s