(126, 17, 127, '<p>The performance evaluation has been fair, I shall work on the areas that needs improvement with my team.</p>', '<p>Your performance has been good over the period under consideration and on your new role. We expect an upward improvement of the Monitoring work and new ideas to get things done right first time.</p><p>You are on the right trend.</p>', '<p>You have the right attitude and Mindset to learn and grow within the department.</p><p>You are hardworking and reliable as you have demonstrated in your assignments.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Keep it up. You are on the right path.</p>', '2022-11-09 16:11:33', '2022-11-14 13:36:29'),
(127, 129, 133, '<p>I have understood the importance of my job and what channels i have to use when reporting in order to get assistance.Also the importance of communicating with my supervisor incase of challenges.<br></p>', '<p>Ann is motivated and we have discussed and agreed she improves on all the areas that she has 3marks and below and especially on communication. <br></p>', '<p>see supervisor comments</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-16', '<p>I trust the supervisor/manager on this</p>', '2022-11-09 17:21:55', '2022-12-08 12:53:34'),
(128, 87, 147, '<p>I wish the company to continue expanding and I will continue working diligently as a security guard.<br></p>', '<p>Worker has shown resilience in his duties and addressing matters relating to work including managing illegal grazing.<br></p>', 'Security team needs to motivate each other to ensure we are on the right track, with all the absenteeism and late reporting to work performance of the team is affected.', '2022-11-14', '<p>Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p>Keep up the good work, work as a team, honesty and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-09 18:15:34', '2022-11-23 16:33:27'),
(129, 7, 148, '<p>Am excited with the continuous group trainings, farm visits which are ongoing ,various type of Intergrated forestry approach,skills and experience which will bring numerous development on the program and to the farmers generally.</p>', '<p>Odede is a performer in farmers program especially group sensitization, he intract with farmers very well. He is self motivated and works under minimal supervision, to improve of communication and reliability&nbsp;</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 