 place to ensure timely replacement of\r\ntools, equipment, and PPE.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-09 19:00:10', '2022-11-12 19:29:30'),
(130, 112, 146, '<p>Evaluation was well conducted, Areas of improvement pointed out are planning, organization, communication and decision making. I commit myself to improve on this highlighted areas for better performance.</p>', '<p>Daniel is a deddicated staff who have excellent attitude and understands his job very well. However, he needs to separate family issues from work for him to perform better.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by DDHR\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:108.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-108.0pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.0pt;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span>i.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">These\r\nshall be done according to the relevant training schedule that shall be put in\r\nconsideration after reviews within the department. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:108.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-108.0pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.0pt;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span>ii.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Training\r\non Microsoft project:- I do not see how relevant training on Microsoft projects is for Daniel Mukhongi is. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; d.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Provision of transport: - Plans To make a camp\r\nin the plantation in the future and provide a means of transport to far\r\ndistances.&nbsp;</span><br></p>', '2022-11-09 19:07:54', '2022-11-10 14:19:58'),
(131, 55, 150, '<p>Firstly I would like to thank the management for creating different platform which has helped in ensuring issues from site are heard and listened through provision of communication app.</p><p>I would only urge the management to ensure replacement is done once workers retires from site or some get laid off for easy implementation of activities.</p><p>Lastly I would request the management company to consider this team in payment increment, life has not been easy and through this, workers will feel motivated and produce results as expected.&nbsp;<br></p>', '<p>The employee has been useful in performing various maintenance activities especially in tree counting which we haven\'t got any ambiguous variance this year especially after creating rows within the compartments. He however needs to be very keen in site to avoid losses of items which has been recorded in site on several occasions. Most of the activities are delegated to him and he needs to be more responsible and very observant at all times. These theft cases has caused the company a lot of money.</p>', '<p>On training and refresher training, a schedule is available. The training schedule has considered the identified gaps and planned activities and the employee will have his training needs met for better delivery.&nbsp;</p><p>The highlighted challenge with the grass, better use of the PPEs can assist, further the option of modifying a number of overalls to fit the exercise will be considered.&nbsp;</p><p>On replacement of retired PMS; availed work force is based on the current needs and changes in the work force is based on planned activities.&nbsp;</p><p>On reported cases of theft on site leading to loss of company properties, all employs are required to adhere to company policies and theft on site is unacceptable.&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 10:57:47', '2022-11-11 18:49:35'),
(132, 11, 151, '<p>I\'m very much thankful&nbsp; for the company for <span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">airtime provision&nbsp; and salary,have also gained a lot of experience on training .I therefore&nbsp; promise to&nbsp; work hard to ensure the&nbsp; company achieve it\'s&nbsp; objectives.&nbsp;</span></p>', '<p>She has improved&nbsp; &nbsp;in her attitude towards the program, she need to improve on planning and organizing for improvement of her performance.she also need to do personal revision for all internal training we have done. Otherwise she can do better.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of forestry plans: - This was\r\nbecause of transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at\r\nthe BGF group level. This not only affected the farmers program but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">(Lack of proper facilitation) Timely\r\nmotorbike repairs as per the schedule and Lack of fuel: - All these arose\r\nbecause of the transition explained in point (a) above<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - Issues\r\nconcerning communication can be addressed with the immediate supervisor and if\r\nthat doesnâ€™t work reported to the supervisor to the immediate supervisor. We\r\nalso have a communications app where staff can raise their concerns. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Hostility, Cultural issues affecting\r\nthe program:- this is an issue that should be addressed by the AA and should\r\nnot be a reason for poor performance or not achieving objectives. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools, Equipment and PPE: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards digital management/maintenance of tools, equipment and\r\nPPE to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack of them or poor\r\nquality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely replacement of\r\ntools, equipment, and PPE.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-10 11:52:17', '2022-11-12 19:30:16'),
(133, 60, 156, '<p>Plantation maintenance activities targets for the past one year have been achieved, we look forward to have major production and in planting of 250,000 seedlings from next year.</p><p>The company to kindly look forward to salary increment to all workers considering the high cost of living.</p><p>I would also appreciate a chance to get power saw operation training for future use within the company and at home.</p>', '<p>The employee has been involved in various plantation maintenance activities such as cleaning and pruning with ease. He also assisted&nbsp; in operations activities like fencing and watering of Kei-apple. However a lot of trainings in the nursery has not been done this year considering no production done over the year. Refresher training will be required before commencing production and establishment activities from next year.&nbsp;</p><p>The employees will also be sensitized on FSC principles and standards.</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">On the worker\'s concern on pay increment, he needs to improve his performance for this to be considered. His training needs will be considered and a training schedule is available which will address the highlighted training among others identified including refreshers based on the planned activities.&nbsp;</span><br></p><p>The employee to note that production and establishment are based on plans for a specific year on addressing his view on what needs improvement.&nbsp;</p><p>Various platforms for communication have been put in place for the employee to communicate and get feedback. Likewise the issues bringing disunity among the workers should be communicated for a resolution to be reached for better teamwork.</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers:- the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and,\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Production and Planting:- production\r\nand planting is based on companyâ€™s objectives and best suited site. It is not\r\nautomatic. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 12:16:03', '2022-11-11 18:52:39'),
(134, 22, 154, '<p>The evaluation has been a success and I am going to follow all company policies and procedures, and put in more effort into my work so that I can be of a positive impact to the company.</p>', '<p>Moses is a good team player who has the potential to improve and do better.</p>', '<p>Employee to train on relevant trainings to his job like timely communication, importance of communicating and importance of discipline in security e.t.c requested seedling production and chemical application&amp; mixing will not help in improving his performance.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Focus on your security Job and deliver. Delayed communication is not good for security.</p>', '2022-11-10 12:32:01', '2022-11-16 19:16:23'),
(135, 108, 153, '<p>The evaluation process was good, the employee appreciate where he did not perform and he is willing to improve on. I seek to understand all company policies to avoid any further non conformances.</p>', '<p>Suleiman has expressed himself clearly on what affect his output, this is a good thing on work improvement in terms of performance. However, he need to improve on punctuality and decision making to ensure his full potential is utilised. He has improved on communication and he is encouraged to use all relevant platform to ensure the information is well recieved.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - Plans To\r\nmake a camp in the plantation in the future and providing a means of transport\r\nto far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wild animals: - We have plans to\r\nextend the fence in an appropriate way to keep away the animals<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:108.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-108.0pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.0pt;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span>i.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">These\r\nshall be done according to the relevant training schedule that shall put in\r\nconsideration after reviews within the department.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 12:47:34', '2022-11-10 14:28:49');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(136, 89, 157, '<p>I\'m committing myself to work diligently in achieving the company\'s objective.<br></p>', 'Worker has a very good attitude towards work. He is determined in being better at his job. You now need to work on the issues that have come out of this evaluation including improving on communication.<br>', '<p>Employee to improve on communication which was pointed out as his major weakness. To be included in the trainings requested because its missing, the employee can also add it in his objects and learn more on communication online.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-10 12:59:39', '2022-11-23 16:34:04'),
(137, 68, 145, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Plantation maintenance targets for the past one year have been achieved tremendously however, in the nursery production there is a lot of work which needs to be done&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; to reduce seedling losses resulting due to mortality. New approaches are identified to ensure the seedlings produced are of quality and once planted no losses occurs.<o:p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"></o:p></span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">In plantation protection there has been a challenge with encroachments reported because of local community entering the plantation by force however, this was solved by engaging the community in Barraza\'s which will be adopted annually for promotion of community relation based on FSC principles.<o:p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"></o:p></span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">For the team on site however, there is need for close interaction to bridge the gap of disunity which occurred in the past two month between the PMS and security personnel, this is a result of theft cases in site which has been reported occasionally.</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; margin-top: 1rem; margin-right: 1rem; margin-left: 1rem; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Moving forward we have done work plans for extension of 400 ha in 2023 and preparations have been put in place to commence production process.</span></p>', '<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">For the year, in Kiambere the focus was on plantation maintenance, plantation protection and a trial on improved seedlings production.</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">From the activities undertaken on site for the year, the employee had numerous corrective action requests (CARs) raised to him pointing to the fact that he needs to ensure he does things right the first time to avoid many corrections which have time and monitory cost implication.</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">On the other hand, there was improvement on the communication of activities happening on site and punctuality. He has also exuded good attitude towards his job and can be relied on to run the siteâ€™s activities. &nbsp;Going forward the employee requires more training and improvement on people management, planning and further improvement on communication. &nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(36, 36, 36); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Web&quot;, sans-serif; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\"><span style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 10.5pt; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Additionally, the employee is expected to complete the siteâ€™s management plan by end of Nov for sustainable forest management in line with FSC.</span></p>', '<p>Further comments from above supervisors comment are;</p><p>The 3 supervisors together with the FT shall have a weekly meeting at the to map out assignments implementation timelines for the FT to have better concentration of the varied assignments. Additionally proposal has been put in 2023 plans to hire an extra staff to work together with the FT as the plantation will be extended with the planned establishment.&nbsp;</p><p>The FT should verse himself with conflict resolution skills to be able to handle workers grievances and have a united team.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-13', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Employing of supervisors: - placement\r\nand replacement of staff done on need basis after thorough assessment of the\r\nproject plan/activities. Activities at Kiambere site were limited to pruning,\r\ncleaning, tree counting and a few seedlings that were produced for research in\r\nthe nursery. This should have been easy for Osore to manage.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Management of people and Leadership skills:\r\n- The FT needs to work on his management and leadership skills. Over the past\r\none year he has had difficulties bringing the workers together and ensuring\r\nthey delivered the expected results. This is clear from the responses of the Permanent\r\nmaintenance staff evaluations. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication: - The communication\r\nbetween the FT and the Plantations manager at the head office needs to improve.\r\nOver the past one year on various occasions what has been communicated from the\r\nHOD has not always been implemented. Changes were made (esp. on the research for\r\nimproved seedling production) at implementation that had not been communicated\r\nwhich led to an inconclusive outcome. Which was a cost.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">General comment:-\r\nOsore has gained the necessary technical skills and knowledge to do the job, However,\r\nfor him to grow within the department, he must develop his ability to manage\r\npeople, be more assertive, communicate better and have a sense of ownership (He\r\nmust change his attitude towards responsibilities and stop complaining about\r\nhow he has a lot of work which is not true) for the responsibilities in his\r\nposition.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 13:47:49', '2022-11-14 14:50:39'),
(138, 120, 159, '<p>I am going to work on the areas pointed out that needs improvement.<br></p>', 'Hardworking and a Co-operative employee.<br>', '<p>Employee to be trained on communication which is missing out in the training needs because it was pointed out among his major weaknesses.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-10 13:49:30', '2022-11-23 16:34:29'),
(139, 9, 149, 'I will work on the areas that need improvement.', '<p>Nelly has been instrumental when it comes to monitoring of activities in 7F and Kiambere. However, she needs to familiarize herself with the procedures,work instructions and have an open mind when it comes to learning&nbsp; monitoring and evaluation.</p><p>Work on the areas that need improvement.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p>', '<p>You&nbsp; have a tendency to complain and&nbsp; giving excuses instead of finding solutions to Challenges. This is in your attitude and affects your abilities to learn and grow in the department.</p><p>You need to improve on reporting also.</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Observe all the comments above and work on the shortcomings to improve your performance.</p>', '2022-11-10 14:45:25', '2022-11-14 13:37:43'),
(140, 62, 162, '<p>I would like to appreciate the kind of work the site team has done throughout the year in terms of plantation maintenance. We look forward to start production activities from next year and through team work we will achieve the set targets.</p><p>Lastly I would urge the management team to consider salary increment due to current high standard of living&nbsp;</p>', '<p>The employee has been actively involved in all the plantation maintenance activities on site with ease and is more efficient in operating other machineries such as water pump and brush cutter.</p><p>There will be further training on FSC principles to implement all activities on site based on FSC standards.</p>', '<p>Hand gloves are part of the PPEs required for the activity of manual cleaning as stipulated in the work instruction, they have been considered in the plans of the activity and will be provided as per the plans. Any missing PPE&nbsp; should be immediately communicated to the site responsible to make a follow up to have them in place. An activity should not be undertaken without the right PPEs.</p><p>Theft on site as commented by the employee is unacceptable and there is a disciplinary code to deal with it. The code is readily available on site for reference by all employees. Employees should always report incidences which go against the company policies.</p><p>Disunity breeds from unresolved grievances, all employees are encouraged to communicate their grievances using various channels and platforms for resolution and fostering teamwork.</p><p>The company has provided enough tools for undertaking all activities on site, an assessment will be done for repair, replacement or addition in accordance to planned activities.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers: - the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and,\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment, and PPE.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 15:12:29', '2022-11-12 16:03:32'),
(141, 24, 158, '<p>Evaluations are good because they give employees a chance to assess oneself as per the set goals and objectives of the year.</p>', '<p>Paul is a dedicated staff who loves his job, exhibits discipline and a good team player, though challenged when it comes to reporting since he is unable to speak, read or write English.</p>', '<p>Employee to push himself to severally interact with the available BGF apps relevant to the security team by doing so he will learn through on job training.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p>Keep up the Good work and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-10 15:15:19', '2022-11-16 19:18:07'),
(142, 102, 165, '<p>The discussion has been positive. I have taken note of what I need to work on.<br></p>', '<p>Worker is positive minded. Shows a lot of enthusiasm to comply with the company\'s guidelines and procedures in an effort towards achieving the company\'s objective.<br></p>', '<p>Employee to work on the weak areas pointed out in the interaction part of it been communication to be added in the training need list.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also take up the good suggestions.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-10 16:40:08', '2022-11-23 16:35:32'),
(143, 44, 166, '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">I would like to appreciate the kind of work the site team has put in place throughout the year in terms of plantation maintenance, especially for tree counting adoption of rows and boundaries within the compartments has help reduce errors in tree counting.</span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I also have to appreciate HR department for providing disciplinary procedure to guide workers in solving disputes on site. For a long period of time workers have been working in fear of dismissal without being taken through any trial but with such policies, it shows that management has good faith on their employees.</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I would also urge Forestry department to&nbsp; try as much as possible to participate in production annually and to create new research for developing new ideas such as using improved seedling production method as done this year.</p>', '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">The employee has been actively involved in all the plantation\r\nmaintenance activities on site with ease and is more efficient in tree counting. He is one of the oldest staff on site and has been taking active role in </span>refresher<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;trainings to other team members to ensure work is done efficiently.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">There will be further\r\ntraining on FSC principles to implement all activities on site based on FSC\r\nstandards.</span></p>', '<p>An assessment of tools on site will be done to determine the needs for repairs, replacement or addition based on plans, then the required of the 3 will be implemented.&nbsp;</p><p>On theft of items on site; this is a major non-conformance and the HR department has provided a disciplinary code to deal with it.&nbsp;</p><p>Annual production and establishment is based on specific year\'s objective of the company.&nbsp;</p><p>Salary increment is based on performance and employees are encouraged to improve on their performance to get a raise after their performance has been appraised. FSC principles will be incorporated in the activities undertaken for the company to be FSC certified.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure the timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment, and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers: - the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on-site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have the capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and,\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"1\"> Training</font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;shall be mandatory as\r\nrequested by employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant\r\ntraining schedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Production and Planting:- production\r\nand planting are based on the companyâ€™s objectives and best-suited site. It is not\r\nautomatic.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 17:17:27', '2022-11-12 16:10:01'),
(144, 127, 161, '<p>Appreciate the opportunity to serve in the organization. The growth of a company is measured by the growth of its employees. The changing landscape especially in climate change and carbon credits require more exposure in current issues relating to forestry managment.</p>', '<p>January is one self motivated staff, driven to achieve the set goals, he works under minimal supervision. He need to improve in planning and time management for efficiecy of achieving his objectives.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - there have\r\nbeen a lot of issues relating to communication that has incapacitated the GIC\r\nprogram over the past year. Late communication, lack of approved plans e.t.c.\r\nThis shall be streamlined by having a preapproved yearly Workplan by project\r\npartners and probably initiating regular technical committee meetings.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-10 17:31:35', '2022-11-12 19:29:53'),
(145, 86, 168, '<p>I will continue to take my job seriously. I would like the company to clean the plantation to facilitate patrols.<br></p>', '<p>Mr. Kulisa is a highly motivated hardworking employee. He should continue to consult and ask questions related to the job to be able to updated on the company procedures and policies to make his work more efficient considering he can not write or read in English/kiswahili.<br></p>', '<p>Increase interactions with your supervisor for continuous guidance because you have several areas which need improvement.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also take up the good suggestions.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-10 17:41:03', '2022-11-23 16:36:27'),
(146, 111, 160, '<p>The evaluation process is satisfactory, mistakes pointed out and possible solution highlighted on how to address them.</p>', '<p>Ali has improved in terms of general behaviour since having an open interaction with DDHR &amp; HOD, He is dynamic, follow instruction but he must learn how to cope up with family issues without affecting his work output. He should also improve on absentiseem and honesty for him to get to his full potential.</p>', '<p>On efficient tools; an assessment will be done and the need to repair, replace or add to the tools established and implemented. On transport the matter will be deliberated on and feedback given but meanwhile the employees should ensure they report to work early.&nbsp;</p><p>On salaries, reviews are done based on performance and the employees are encouraged to improve their performance to qualify.</p><p>The employees performance in the last appraisal was unsatisfactory, he has however improved but he still has an issue with honesty and&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">absenteeism, this should be rectified and followed up by the supervisor and feedback given.&nbsp;</span></p><p>The electric fence is an ongoing project based on analysis of the damage by wild animal.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - The\r\nmanagement is aware of this challenge and in our plans for the future we shall\r\nhave a camp in the plantation and also explore possibilities for provision of a\r\nmeans of transport to far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wild animals: - We have plans to\r\nextend the fence in an appropriate way to keep away the animals<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 17:43:08', '2022-11-12 15:32:08'),
(147, 128, 164, '<p>I wish to thank you the BGF management for continuous improvement on company\'s working systems. However, the company may also create an environment for innovation in forestry sector across the organization structure for better forest management and establishment.</p><p>Better the coordination of various projects and timely approval of work plans.</p>', '<p>Samuel is one of the implementer in the GIC program, interested in working with pupils to implement the objectives of tree planting and ensuring&nbsp; they survive. He has a passion in the field of forestry and works very hard to achieve his objectives. Although he need to improve on communication.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication issues: - there have\r\nbeen a lot of issues relating to communication that have incapacitated the GIC\r\nprogram over the past year. Late communication, lack of approved plans e.t.c .\r\nThis shall be streamlined by having a preapproved yearly workplan by project\r\npartners and probably initiating regular technical committee meetings.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-10 17:56:51', '2022-11-12 19:29:00'),
(148, 56, 169, '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">I would like to appreciate the kind of work the site team has\r\ndone throughout the year in terms of plantation maintenance. We look forward to\r\nstart production activities from next year and through team work we will\r\nachieve the set targets.</span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">I would also like to urge the management team if possible to create a barbed wire fence around the plantation to avoid scenarios recently recorded on site </span>when the<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;local community were allowed to cut grass from the plantation. In most cases they were passing through every corner in the plantation even after we have worked so hard in ensuring fencing </span>maintenance<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;are met.</span></font><br></p>', '<p>The employee has been actively involved in all plantation maintenance activities without any challenge . He always follows up with his colleagues to ensure task rates are achieved and on several occasions he has taken part on refresher trainings on site especially in tree counting.</p><p>There will be further training on FSC principles to implement all activities on site based on FSC standards.</p>', '<p>On salary; reviews are done based on employee\'s performance, for one to get an increment it should be matched with improved performance. Also on the few instances if any when the payments are delayed, a communication is done to the employees.&nbsp;</p><p>In case a worker gets injured while at work, care is given in form of first aid and later they are assisted to a health facility for further medical attention, communication is done to the respective departments and where it warrants the employees to get a sick off they are granted and later they apply for a sick leave in the TimeCapture.&nbsp;</p><p>The site supervisor is available to all staff on site and whenever there are issues they should be communicated to them for resolution.&nbsp;</p><p>Community relations shall be addressed in the management plan and FSC, additionally already there is a system of engaging with the community; an example being the recent baraza held by the company, TARDA, the community and the the local authority on grass collection which resolved the issue.</p><p>On the retired workers, the company engages work force based on need and according to plans.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - these shall be done\r\naccording to the training schedule that shall put in consideration all the\r\ntraining requests by the staff<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers:- the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and,\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-10 19:01:46', '2022-11-11 18:48:14'),
(149, 23, 167, '<p>The company should continue working with me and trusting me as a member of their security team, and I shall also deliver as expected of me.</p>', '<p>Lameck Obongi has exhibited dedication and commitment in his area of work, however he is also challenged with reporting as his reading and writing skills need improvement.</p>', 'Focus on trainings relevant to your work to improve on performance. Some trainings requested like pruning and seedling production are not relevant to your work.', '2022-11-14', '<p>Improve on the weak areas more especially on communication</p>', '2022-11-10 19:05:08', '2022-11-16 19:20:36'),
(150, 141, 119, '<p>Working here has helped grow professionally because of the great guidance I received from my supervisor and the company in general.</p>', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Halima has adopted\r\nwell within the company, managed to understand the workings of the company from\r\nthe perspective of FSC and its requirements. FSC certification has become key\r\nto the company\'s short term and long term objectives. This means that the FCS domain\r\nwithin the company shall grow exponentially and I believe that she has the\r\ncapacity to guide this growth.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Supervisor is HOD.&nbsp;', '2022-11-11 12:11:06', '2022-11-11 12:13:28'),
(151, 98, 175, '<p>1. the evaluation process was good, i request that all concerns raised in the evaluation will not be just written documents but actions. i have noted all areas that i need improvement and i will put great effort to perfect.</p>', '<p>Bakari is a well trained forestry staff in all field activities except compartment demarcation which he has highlighted in the training section, this shows how much concern he has towards improvement on being a reliable staff. As a supervisor, i will indicate that, this is commendable.</p><p>In the following year much will be expected from him, in terms of improvement on planning &amp; organizing i.e effective leave planning in order to avoid affecting forestry plans towards achieving set targets.</p><p>Additional area to improve on will be communication, Bakari need to expressed himself fully for any supervisor to know his concerns that might affect his result output.</p>', '<p><br></p><p>The company has provided adequate tools to undertake all activities on site and considers requests put across based on plans. For the provided tools to be efficient, the company has provided for maintenance. Whenever you find a tool you are working with to be inefficient, immediate communication to the site responsible should be made for change or repair of the tool.&nbsp;</p><p>On delivery, the company has an IPR system where delivery of required items can be tracked by the site manager who should then give feedback and follow up on delivery.&nbsp;</p><p>On transport, this will be considered and a possible way forward given.&nbsp;</p><p>On giving priority to certain areas of the plantation; plans implemented are based on prospection, you are encouraged to communicate to the site responsible if you see an area of concern.&nbsp;</p><p>The company has invested on mechanization and use of motorized pruning saws is in the work plans.&nbsp;</p><p>The employee is encouraged to continue communicating regularly on issues that may be affecting his work delivery.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Additionally workers are encouraged to do quality work and surpass set targets where possible and there are incentives associated with that.</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - Plans To\r\nmake a camp in the plantation in the future and providing a means of transport\r\nto far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:108.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-108.0pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.0pt;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span>i.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">These\r\nshall be done according to the relevant training schedule that shall put in\r\nconsideration after reviews within the department.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-11 12:56:20', '2022-11-11 18:38:31');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(152, 36, 114, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I have over the\r\nyear learned new things through the guidance from my supervisor. Itâ€™s the year\r\nhave got the new assignment of Nursery Manager and I was very green in matters\r\nrelated to melia volkensii but with continuous interactions and training by my\r\nsupervisor have come to gain a lot of knowledge in this field. I have noted the areas of concern which i need to work on: taking initiatives, knowledge management, drive for results and team management plus continuous improvement on communication.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p>I will also do more research to get to understand my domain for the benefit of myself and the people i will be supervising.</o:p></span></p>', '<p>The Nursery Manager position is a new position created this year after assessment of the various sections of the forestry department. The nursery section was identified as an area of absolute importance in the value chain and that it was necessary for it to be separated from the plantations to better address the issues that arise in the nurseries. Alex was moved to this position from the farmers program. Since he took over this position in March this year, there has not been any significant activities in the nurseries. There were only approx. 1800 seedlings in Kiambere nursery at that time (for research). It is important to note that these seedlings were not managed well by the Ft for kiambere hence we ended up planting half of the seedlings. In Nyongoro, there were no production activities, but we had marking of plus trees and at first, he had a difficult time with the site manager for Nursery who was not responsive but within a short time he managed to get him in line to do what he had instructed him to do. </p><p>This being said, he needs to work on the following aspects of nursery management for him to succeed in this position for when we resume production:</p><ol><li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">1. Mukau production. (From managing of fruits to planting out, pathology)</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">2. Get field experience on production of Mukau (this can be done together with the supervisor in the field)</span></li><li>3. Back-office management of the nursery. (This shall be key to monitoring the daily changes in seedling stock figures, activities done and the results)</li><li>4. Streamline nursery staff on site. (Provide information that shall ensure we have the right staff to do the job on sites)</li></ol>', NULL, NULL, '<p>HOD same as the supervisor</p>', '2022-11-11 13:51:05', '2022-11-11 13:52:21'),
(153, 113, 178, '<p>The evaluation has been well conducted, i highly appreciate the experience and other technical skills that i am gaining due to my engagement with BGF. All highlighted areas of weaknessess such communication and knowledge management will be corrected.</p>', '<p>John is a hands on staff and have a commendable technical skills in artisan related activities. He graps information very first and apply it appropriately, on forestry part, he is well trained and always aware of what he suppose to do when assigned various tasks.</p><p>He is instrumental&nbsp; time management and have great passion of any job he does. However, he needs to improve on communication and knowledge sharing. He should freely expressed his ideas in order to be beneficial to his current work performance.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>A training schedule is available and the employee will be trained on all activities in the plans. He has expressed interest in operations activities such as plumbing and this can be considered during establishment of the watering system in the plantation.&nbsp;</p><p>On salary reviews; this will be based on the employee\'s performance.&nbsp;</p><p>On transport from site office to the plantation; as the plantation expands, this will be deliberated and feedback given. The site manager is expected to have more presence in the field where the employees are working for supervision and guidance, this will be increased.&nbsp;</p><p>Tools management will be enhanced with constant assessments and implementation of required; repairs, replacement and or addition of more tools in accordance to need based on plans. The employee also requires to improve on communication to assist in better management of activities he is assigned to.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p>HOD same as the manager<br></p>', '2022-11-11 15:11:23', '2022-11-12 19:28:10'),
(154, 143, 179, '<p>I thank the company for the opportunity to join this team. There is need for improvement on the line of security and I look forward to ensure security work is done perfectly.</p><p>I would only wish to urge the company to consider salary increment due to the current high cost of living.</p>', '<p>Daniel Karungu is recently absorbed in the team and has proven to be able to perform his duties with minimal supervision. However, there a lot which has occurred on site for the past few months resulting to cases of theft on site. These incidents occurs under his watch but has failed to come forth to name the culprits involved. These losses cause the company a lot of money and it must be stopped.</p><p>The company has done a lot to the whole team by providing PPEs, communication gadgets and its now upon the guards to ensure they perform what is expected from them without excuses.</p><p>There is also need for a proper training to the whole team on basic security work.</p>', '<p>Been among the literate guards in the team a lot is expected from you in guiding and continuous training the illiterate guards, improve on knowledge management.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p>', '2022-11-11 15:22:45', '2022-11-15 18:37:36'),
(155, 1, 181, '<p>The working environment has been very favorable as we have been given room to balance both work at the office and at home</p><p>The communication Dept has been persistent in the need for communication and this has led to information flowing timely and accurately</p><p>Our weekly Friday meetings have led to improved efficiency where currently new applications are coming out with almost 95% covering the need they were requested. This has saved time</p><p>Continuous support from the supervisor and willingness to explain in detail what is required so that there is no back and forth</p><p>Positive feedback from other departments on the role the IT department is playing in the company</p>', '<p>Michael has been impressively good at getting things done, sometimes under difficult circumstances. It is evident that he needs help to clear the backlog that is accumulating due to the fact that there was no IT department before. He is perfectly integrated into the BGF corporate landscape and he\'s indeed picking up very fastly the workings of the company through the Fridays meetings. We are nearing the end of a very positive year 2022.</p>', '<p>See supervisors\' comments</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p>See supervisor\'s comments</p>', '2022-11-11 17:30:32', '2022-11-11 17:40:31'),
(156, 76, 180, '<p>Firstly I would like to thank the management for the opportunity to join Kiambere security team. There has a been a challenge in terms of communication between me and my supervisors, I would like to commit myself from now henceforth I communicate promptly all incidents on site without fear or favor.</p><p>Lastly I would urge the management to consider salary increment to workers following high cost of living experience in the country.</p>', '<p>Mathew is recently confirmed as a security guard and has shown good potential to work as a security guard with the rest of the team. A lot however, is expected from him in terms of communication and also to put an initiative to ensure&nbsp; theft cases on site are minimized. Theft cases is still too much on site and this is unacceptable. The company has provided more than enough from communication gadgets to protective gears and now its upon the workers to ensure work is done perfectly.</p><p>There is need for basic training to all guards for effective performance.</p>', '<p>Improve on your communication as pointed out in the interaction. </p><p>Continue training illiterate guards on usage of communication app and digital OB.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We expect you being new to the team to help in dealing with theft cases on site..</p>', '2022-11-11 17:45:36', '2022-11-15 18:41:04'),
(157, 6, 177, '<p>Farmers outgrowers program has really transformed and changed the area within 7forks gradually changing the mindset and attitude of the local farmers around. Through several trainings and new intervention to our farmers, there is a lot of change in livelihood which has reduced poverty.</p><p>Through several trainings I have gained a vast experience in handling matters dry land agroforestry, group formation and registration, Group dynamics, leadership skills and human resource management. I will remain grateful to my supervisor in forestry department and all management team for the support and confidence that has been given to me and my team.</p><p>Despite the many challenges, they have made me stronger, and I will remain focused to ensure the company achieves the objectives. I will improve in my communication and planning for better management of the program.</p><div><br></div>', '<p>Recently promoted to the managerial position of the 7 Forks program from a training officer, Florence has shown growth and capacity to lead a team in a tough environment. For an even better performance, she needs to: -</p><p>1. Find confidence within herself to know that she can manage a team with a big number of men.&nbsp;</p><p>2. Improve on communication with her team.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>HOD is the same as the supervisor.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-11 18:09:45', '2022-11-11 18:35:33'),
(158, 94, 182, 'The evaluation process was good, areas of improvement highlighted to be addressed to ensure work efficiency.&nbsp;', '<p>Lughanje is a dynamic, result oriented and have drive for results. he is well versed with all forestry activities but does extremely well in plantation marking activity. He is always ready to influence other staff towards positive goals and this rates its leadership skill to be excellent.&nbsp;</p><p>However, he needs to improve on managing relationship and manage his temper effectively in order to achieve his full potential.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>On training; a schedule is in place for trainings and refreshers, during the year the schedule is reviewed periodically to meet set objectives for the training.&nbsp;</p><p>On tools; the company has provided adequate tools to undertake activities on site and an assessment shall be conducted to establish maintenance and addition needs. Employee encouraged to communicate on instances when they have inefficient tools for work.&nbsp;</p><p>He did a commendable job in stock verification and his tree counting forms had no errors after review.</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Acquisition of personal assets: - This\r\nis not the companyâ€™s responsibility. The company does not give salary advance.\r\nIf an employee wants to acquire assets, they can take loans from banks. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment, and PPE<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Inadequate field supervision by supervisor:\r\n- One of the responsibilities of a supervisor is to continuously follow-up on\r\nhis/her team and check if tasks are performed correctly, provide guidance and refresher\r\ntrainings if need be. However, if this is not being done by the supervisor, the\r\nstaff have a right to raise it with the supervisor and if the supervisor isnâ€™t responsive\r\nthen it can be communicated to his/her supervisor. We also have a communication\r\napp where this could have been raised.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-11 18:23:22', '2022-11-12 15:54:41'),
(159, 2, 183, '<p>I must say for the 3years I have working with BGF under my HOD and other departments I have really grown my experience more than I joined the Company.</p>', '<p>Alex, has grown in understanding the workings of the company and has been a tremendous support in the implementation of several new apps.&nbsp; Staff seems to appreciate his positive attitude but has also understood that he follows the company\'s procedures. When he started the job was new and Alex gave it consistency.</p>', '<p>see supervisor\'s comments</p>', '2022-11-11', '<p>see supervisor\'s comments</p>', '2022-11-11 18:50:01', '2022-11-11 18:51:58'),
(160, 41, 128, '<p>Appreciating the experience that i have gathered within the year, understanding that the knowledge roadmap is continuous and trying my best to be better next time.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Keep up the good work and&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Improve on the improvable areas so that we will have a positive smooth running department next year.</span></p>', '<p>You have performed well in your duties over the year. Keep it up and improve on the few arears that need improvement.</p>', '2022-11-14', 'Your have done a good job in running the accounting system both Kenya and Uganda.', '2022-11-11 19:37:52', '2022-11-14 13:42:21'),
(161, 59, 184, '<p>I would urge the company to keep up with the extension of land for further production.&nbsp;</p><p>I would also urge Forestry team to ensure before transplanting seedlings in newly established land, spraying is done to protect seedlings against termites as observed in newly planted seedling in A016.</p>', '<p>Robert Kilonzo has been taking active role in plantation maintenance on site and he is very skilled especially in handling brush cutters. In establishment activities however, a lot needs to be done with both PMS to get 100% survival. The team seems to have relaxed after the last major establishment in 2018.</p><p>There is need for a lot of refresher training in preparation for next year production and planting to ensure planted seedlings survives. He also need to improve on his communication skills to ensure any occurrences on site is reported on time for decision making.</p>', '<p>On workers disunity; the employee is encouraged to communicate more on all matters related to the job and to approach his supervisor in cases of grievances with colleagues. A better tool management system has been planned for, the employee encouraged to communicate whenever they have an issue on tools for efficiency.&nbsp;</p><p>With the planned establishment in 2023, training will be conducted as per the schedule to prepare the staff and ensure good survival.&nbsp;</p><p>On salary; review is based on the employee\'s performance. Overall the employee\'s performance should improve with focus on communication and self-motivation&nbsp;</p><p><br></p>', '2022-11-12', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure the timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment, and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers: - the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have the capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as requested\r\nby employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training\r\nschedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-11 19:41:33', '2022-11-14 10:52:18'),
(162, 63, 186, '<p>I thank the company for creating platform where grievances of workers are listened to unlike previous years where when any misconduct reported by a worker was handled by dismissal without any hearings.</p><p>I also have to appreciate the company for recent provision of grass and even firewood to the local community from the plantation. This action has made the local community have better view to the company unlike previous years where the community thought there is no gain they get from the project.</p><p>Lastly I would urge thorough investigation to be made and action taken on persons involved in malpractice like theft issues on site like have been observed recently. The security team also to be trained to be more observant especially those assigned nursery area to be able to monitor and observe unusual activities on site to prevent these theft cases like gumboots reported recently.</p>', '<p>Shadrack Masavi has been involved in all plantation maintenance activities on site and performs his work with ease. However in establishment activities there is a lot which needs to be done for all the&nbsp; employees, the work done during establishment of improved seedlings was poor especially during transportation and planting of seedlings.&nbsp;</p><p>There is need for refresher trainings to ensure next years target of producing and planting 250,000 seedlings is achieved. </p><p>He also need to be honest with himself and with the other colleagues for effective teamwork, he had issues with some workers who were doing shoddy work and kept dragging their work when assigned the same activity but failed to report for correction actions. Covering up of a wrong doing is not helping and can only cause loses to the company which is against the policies.</p>', '<p>Staff grievances to be communicated to the site managers, a grievances mechanism to be drafted to compliment the available policies. Theft on site is unacceptable and employees should be vigilant and report all incidences related to theft for disciplinary measures to be taken. Training to the employee will be conducted in preparation of establishment and maintenance. The employee needs to improve on communication, be self-motivated and have enthusiasm to achieve results for work given.</p>', '2022-11-12', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment, and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers: - the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Communication gaps: - we already\r\nhave a communication app that is for use by all the staff. However, the staff has\r\nnot fully utilized it in spite of being encouraged to frequently. <o:p></o:p></span></p><ul><li><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;e. Trainings shall be mandatory as requested by\r\nemployees. They shall also be done according to the relevant training schedule\r\nthat shall be put in consideration after reviews within the department</span><br></li></ul>', '2022-11-12 12:22:39', '2022-11-14 10:57:49'),
(163, 92, 185, '<p>Iam thankful for all trainings and experienced relating to forestry that has been offered to me by the company, also improvement on digitalization of company activities especially the development of communication application which has open free platform for staff suggestions.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Walter is a multiskilled staff who is well versed with several skills such as welding, mechanic ( panel beating), Administartive tasks, theology and all forestry related activities (Melia establishment and mnagement). However, to improve on his reliability, walter need to learn how to operate GPS ( used in compartment demarcation), Tree measurement equipments ( very important in thinning) and power saw operations.</p><p>Walter needs to have high integrity level as some task he is requested to assist requires such value, he needs to be open and expressed his feelings when compelled to do what does not make him happy. Lastly, his focus on undertaking forestry activities has generally improved this year and he must continue avoiding distraction from other assigned task due to his value that is needed by every supervisor.</p>', '<p>The employee will receive all the planned training to build his capacity for better delivery. On distance from site to the plantation a deliberation will be done and feedback give, meanwhile the employee is advised to report to work early. The employee is well experienced and is expected to contribute to planned establishment and maintenance. The supervisor is expected to be more present on field to guide him and his colleagues during implementation of planned activities.&nbsp;</p><p>Salary review will be based on performance and timely delivery of items to site shall be implemented as per the planned activities.</p>', '2022-11-12', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">AAR insurance: - All staff are\r\ncovered by WIBA. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Provision of transport: - Plans To\r\nmake a camp in the plantation in the future and providing a means of transport\r\nto far distances. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings: - <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:108.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-108.0pt;mso-text-indent-alt:-9.0pt;mso-list:l0 level3 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span>i.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">These\r\nshall be done according to the relevant training schedule that shall put in\r\nconsideration after reviews within the department.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">f.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Capacity\r\nbuilding for staff out of Lamu: - it is not the companyâ€™s responsibility to\r\ntake workers out of Lamu. Staff can take leave during which they can travel to destination\r\nof their wish.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">g.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff. Currently there are not\r\nmany activities in the field<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12 12:32:22', '2022-11-14 11:09:31'),
(164, 65, 187, '<p>I thank the company for this far, the resources got from this company has helped a lot in ensuring I educate my children. I would only urge the company to consider salary increment due to high living standard experienced currently.</p>', '<p>The employee is very committed to his work. He has been part of the team that worked in plantation fencing and manual cleaning and its a work well done.</p><p>He however need refresher trainings on seedling establishment in preparation for next years production and planting of 250,000 seedlings.</p><p>There is also need for further training to ensure implementation of activities on site from next year is in line with FSC principles and standards.&nbsp;<br></p>', '<p>Salary review will be based on performance. Addition of extra labour force will be based on plans. </p><p>The employee has good attitude towards the job and works well in a team, however he needs to improve on communication and initiative. More training required to prepare the employee for the year\'s plans which shall be implemented in line with FSC.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-12', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12 13:14:00', '2022-11-14 10:59:32'),
(165, 91, 188, '<p>Evaluation was good, i am happy to note that my supervisor is aware of my significance to the company and encourages me to continue being a role model to fellow PMS. I have taken note on my communication needs and i will try to improve however much being&nbsp; a quiet person.</p>', '<p>Herbert is a discipline and industrious employee, his level of expertise on hands on work is amazing. He is very organized and neat in every task assigned, this explains why operation department has got hold of him. His passion for trees or forestry practice is wonderful that why he does every task assigned without raising any complaint.</p><p>On operational task assigned, his truck record on result output speaks for itself and this make him to be an assest to the company. However, he needs to improve on communication or interpersonal skills i.e be social and stop being too quiet.</p><p>It is important to note that, this year he was fully invloved in operation activities and result achieved in electric fence maintenance and repair has been great.</p>', '<p>On danger from wild animals; planning of activities shall be done in a way that work is done in the same area by the team and survey is done with help of security personnel. On raincoats; there is a schedule on PPEs replacement and the site manager shall advise on quality before procurement.&nbsp;</p><p>Timely delivery of items including fuel will be enhanced and follow up done through the IPR system.</p><p>The employee has skills on power saw operation and this will come in handy during harvesting activities such as thinning. His performance for the year was good and can be relied upon to execute duties with minimal supervision.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-13', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment:- we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment and PPE<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">AAR insurance: - All staff are\r\ncovered by WIBA. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Wild animals: - We have plans to\r\nextend the fence in an appropriate way to keep away the animals<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12 14:37:47', '2022-11-14 11:15:51'),
(166, 66, 190, '<p>Through this discussion I commit myself to improve on the identified gaps such as reporting to work, following instructions and adhering with company policies especially putting on PPEs at all time, to remain honest at all time, effective communication and loyalty to the company and specifically to apologies for a bad behavior which occurred during enquiries of the lost gumboots.</p><p>I would also urge the forestry department to adopt the idea of collecting fruits from the plantation every season to ensure there is enough seeds on site and production done annually.</p><p>There is need for continuous training for seedling production in the nursery even if there no production ongoing on site to ensure activities are done correctly at all tome.</p><p>There is also need for management to increase the number of staff on site for effective performance in all activities.</p><p>Lastly I would request the management to consider salary increment considering the current high cost of living.</p>', '<p>John Muema has been involved in various plantation maintenance activities and operation activities such as fencing which is a job well done for the year. He however got involved in a malpractice which is against the company\'s policies. The security guard on site made a report of theft and his name was&nbsp; forwarded as a suspect.</p><p>He however acted poorly during enquiry of the allegations on the case whereby he refused to follow a direct order which proved dishonesty from him. He however admits his mistakes and claims that he was just trying to avoid being set up and commits himself to improve on the identified gaps.</p><p>He also need training on effective communication to ensure work is done perfectly and in case of any issue the report is made on time and actions taken to avoid loses.</p>', '<p>The employee was implicated on a theft case and this reflected badly on his character of honesty. He needs to improve on various aspects including ability to follow instructions, honesty, communication and self-motivation.&nbsp;</p><p>On salary; review is based on performance. The employee should work on the gaps identified to improve his performance. The employee also needs to read and understand all the company policies to avoid non-conformances.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Addition to work force is based on plans.</span></p>', '2022-11-13', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Replacement of workers:- replacement\r\nof workers shall be done on need after thorough assessment of critical\r\nactivities that need to be done by permanent staff. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Tools &amp; Equipment: - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards mechanization and digital management/maintenance of\r\ntools and equipment to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack\r\nof them or poor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely\r\nreplacement of tools, equipment, and PPE. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Discord among workers: - the company\r\nis working towards restructuring on site and putting staff in the right\r\npositions in which they have capacity to handle issues that arise swiftly and\r\nor prevent them from arising.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-12 17:50:55', '2022-11-14 11:01:52');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(167, 119, 170, '<p>2022 was not such a successful year since no new planting was done and plantation maintenance activities were equally scaled down making the status of the plantation not appealing. However, much was achieved in correcting a lot of mistakes especially on having correct tree stock figures which is the core objective that drives all activities.</p><p>In the whole evaluation process, i was made aware of what is expected on me coming next year and suggestion on areas highlighted as my weak points. This shall be corrected to ensure i do the right thing all the time.</p>', '<p>The siteâ€™s maintenance activities were scaled down and there was no establishment done.&nbsp;</p><p>The employee was expected to complete the plantation stock verification and have correct stock figures always. This was done and a system to ensure reporting of correct figures put in place.&nbsp;</p><p>There was notable improvement on communication of activities on site.</p><p>From analysis, the employee needs to improve further on communication, punctuality, following instructions and work on agreed tasks within timelines without giving excuses.&nbsp;</p><p>Additionally, the employee is expected to complete the siteâ€™s management plan by end of Nov for sustainable forest management in line with FSC. He is also expected to sensitize his team on FSC and ensure its incorporation in the siteâ€™s activities.</p><p>The plantation is expected to expand according to 2023 plans, therefore more initiative is expected from him and fast reaction to avoid non-conformances which lead to costs to the company.</p><div><br></div>', '<p>Refer to the supervisor\'s comment above.</p>', '2022-11-13', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Employing of supervisors: - placement\r\nand replacement of staff done on need basis after thorough assessment of the\r\nproject plan/activities. Activities at Nyongoro site were limited to pruning,\r\ncleaning, tree counting. For these activities only, there was no need for recruitment\r\nof a forest technician. However, we shall get more staff as it shall be agreed\r\nfor when we resume with expansion. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Disputes with the community: - Apart\r\nfrom the existing approaches, we shall also incorporate FSC requirements for\r\ncommunity engagement. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Staff absenteeism: - This should be\r\naddressed in the staffâ€™s evaluations. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-theme-font:\r\nminor-latin;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA\">Backlog in maintenance activities: - This was because\r\nof transitioning from an old company structure and way of working at the BGF\r\ngroup level. This not only affected the work in the plantations but all the\r\ndepartments. However, work shall resume in 2023 when this process is complete</span><br></p>', '2022-11-12 18:30:33', '2022-11-14 15:14:55'),
(168, 142, 191, '<p>I thank the company for opportunity to work as security guard in Kiambere.&nbsp;</p><p>I would urge operations department to check on provision of quality torches and employment of more security guards to ensure patrolling around the plantation is done perfectly.</p><p>Forestry department also to check on removal of dead and windthrows from the plantation.</p><p>The management also need to fast track creation of shelter in A016 and building of latrines in A016 .</p><p>there is also need for signpost to indicate where Kiambere plantation located.</p><p>I would also urge the management to consider salary increment due to the current high cost of living.</p>', '<p>Jane Mbatha is recently absorbed in the security team and has shown good potential to work with ease despite being the only lady among the security team.</p><p>She actively participate during site meetings and any training done on site and she has been giving reports when on duty after every 30 mins which indicates that she is committed in doing her work. She however has issues with reporting things which affects her directly. She has been having an issue in taking and handing over of duty in A016 with Kithome Muthengi and Nichorus Nthiga whereby since she cant report to work very early to be able to take duty at exactly 6am during day shift the two guards have been revenging in taking over of duty late especially when she is assigned compartment A016 which requires guards to be present at all time. She had this challenge but kept quite.</p><p>There is need for further training and to embrace unity among all guards for effective performance. There are a lot of theft cases on site which cost the company a lot of money, the only solution for this is to have a united and committed team to ensure company\'s properties are protected at all time.</p><p><br></p>', '<p>Be more open in sharing challenges you are facing for improved performance.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You also have a problem with communication and reporting to work on time.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Improve on the weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-14 10:47:42', '2022-11-15 18:48:38'),
(169, 107, 194, '<p>The discussion has been okay.<br></p>', '<p>Worker is an average performer. With previous experience in security related issues, You are thereby encouraged to improve on Knowledge Management and Initiative. Having used a walkie talkie before it is my expectation that you\'ll work together with other guards when rolling out of walkie talkies shall be done on site. <br></p>', '<p>With 5yrs experience in BGF and having previous experience on security job your performance is below expectations.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-14 14:09:48', '2022-11-23 16:38:25'),
(170, 85, 196, '<p>I commit myself to continue working hard in ensuring that I have delivered and met the company\'s targets so that the company can also prosper.<br></p>', '<p>Mualid is a hardworking employee who is committed to his work. He has the willingness to learn and listen to instructions. <br></p>', '<p>Employee to be trained on communication which is among his weak areas and missing in the training needs requests.</p><p>Increase interactions with your supervisor for continuous mentoring and training.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-14 16:00:04', '2022-11-23 16:39:09'),
(171, 79, 199, '<p>The company has done a good job in uplifting the community of this region. I wish for the company to continue growing and expanding its operations. I will personally work hard to perform my duty to assist the company in achieving this.<br></p>', '<p>Gobu is an outstanding employee that has stepped up over time to take up responsibility in ensuring the team is working hand in hand with company objectives.<br></p>', '<p>A lot is expected from you in guiding the team with your vast experience of 6yrs and literacy level, maximize your potential.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-14 17:22:56', '2022-11-23 16:39:34'),
(172, 4, 197, '<p>The discussions were fruitful because some areas of improvement have been highlighted and shall be worked on to ensure that departmental and personal objectives are met. The field activities were low during the year but a lot of work has been done relating to planning, correcting and assessment of staff needs for when we resume working in all the sections within the department. There shall also emphasis on building the capacity of the managers within the department for easy delegation of work to them so that I can concentrate on my tasks.</p>', '<p>See Employee comments.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Samuel done all that was expected from him in this transition period where we didn\'t plant but put massively highly needed order and systems in place. He is very fast in acquiring the necessary knowledge to work efficiently with new electronic tools. His problem is that his staff doesn\'t always share his enthusiasm and positive attitude. This again means that at times he risks overworking which shouldn\'t be the case. In any case he is a director, a main member of the Management team and an observer in the board. All this was achieved on merit and there is no reason why his upwards mars would stop. Well done!!<br>And we are reaching the end of the tunnel in matters of planting. That is where the results of the hard work will show!<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2022-11-14 17:23:38', '2022-11-14 17:31:34'),
(173, 100, 200, '<p>I request the company just as in previous times, In cases of good performance, they continue to write congratulatory letters as they used to, so as to boost our morale as workers. Through the same letters, fellow employees who are not lucky enough to get one also work hard to earn one the following year.<br></p>', 'Hardworking employee that is co-operative and follows the company procedures very well. He stepped up without ceasing when called upon to assist his team in interpreting the security schedule and recording of reports in the absence of the supervisors this year. <br>', '<p>A dedicated staff who is very disciplined, reliable and follows instruction.</p>', '2022-11-14', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-14 18:32:18', '2022-11-23 16:40:10'),
(174, 122, 152, '<p>Supervisor has always been supportive towards ensuring that efficiency is achieved.&nbsp;</p><p>I am grateful for the Company for the opportunity it has given to prove my potential and also learn and improve on the areas that need improvement.&nbsp; I will keep it up.</p>', '<p>Ladislaus has a positive attitude towards the job, he needs to improve on the areas highlighted in the evaluation for maximum output.</p>', '<p>Ladislaus has a positive attitude towards the job, he needs to improve on the areas highlighted in the evaluation for maximum output.<br></p>', '2022-11-24', '<p>We know you have the capacity to do better. You have so far done a good job but with areas that need to be improved. Work on these areas and do your best in the coming year.</p>', '2022-11-14 19:00:13', '2022-11-28 10:38:07'),
(175, 84, 201, 'I thank the company for giving me a job this year. I will work on my communication and improve on it.<br>', '<p>You have done well to step up and assist your colleagues specifically in interpreting the approved security schedule in the absence of the supervisors this year. You however need to improve on your communication and always communicate any wrong doing in your team with out fear to your supervisors.<br></p>', '<p>Improve on communication which was pointed out as your week area. Take an initiative of learning more on communication because it\'s not among the trainings requested.</p><p>Stay focused and continue assisting your team on security schedule interpretation.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p>Keep up the good work and improve on the weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 10:52:28', '2022-11-23 16:28:38'),
(176, 101, 203, '<p>I thanks the company for retaining me this year and giving me a salary that has enabled me uplift my family.<br></p>', '<p>You have to work on communication and give timely reports including reporting any wrong doing in the team.<br></p>', '<p>Take an initiative of learning more on communication which is your weak area from the interaction and as pointed out by your supervisor.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 11:13:23', '2022-11-23 16:40:40'),
(177, 51, 202, '<p>I would only like to urge the management to check on salary increment for the guards depending on the current high cost of living.</p>', '<p>Patrick Katoi is one of the old guards and has been committed in performing his duties with minimal supervision.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">He also has been of great assistance in designing and construction of structures on site such as gates two gates in the nursery and the old one at A016 from Katithini, and PPE structure. He has good talent in building different tools such as rungus which can be used by security team on site. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">He always assist in fencing maintenance around the plantation especially in A016 without being assigned and committed to perform more than required.</span></p><p>There is however need for training for all guards to ensure the whole team is more vigilant and protection of the company\'s properties is maintained to minimize cases of theft recorded currently on site.</p>', '<p>A self motivated staff who can work without supervision and always follow instruction. Keep it up!</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">On the extra work such as making gates, that good and we encourage you to continue with that spirit.</p>', '2022-11-15 11:34:39', '2022-11-15 18:55:56'),
(178, 151, 172, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I thank the\r\ncompany for the employment offered, I have manage to educate my children from\r\nthe resources gained from the company and I look forward to continue working\r\ndiligently on my line of duty.</span></p>', '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">The employee is one of the oldest guards on site and started as\r\na casual in security work. He knows all the corners of the plantation however </span>a lot<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;needs to be done to ensure theft cases reported on site and </span>cattle\'s<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;encroachments comes to a stop.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">He also feels that there is discrimination among his colleague\r\nmembers especially to him since he is the only person from Mbeere\r\ncommunity. There is need for </span>interactions<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;with the guard to eliminate this negative feeling which might results to lack of teamwork.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">A lot of training and interactions is required to the whole\r\nsecurity team for effective work performance<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Work on the weak areas pointed out which are very key for a guard to be effective especially self motivation and reliability.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere is a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p>', '2022-11-15 11:43:31', '2022-11-15 18:35:57'),
(179, 109, 204, '<p>I am happy for having worked well throughout the year, I wish the company to continue expanding so that I can continue protecting the trees and all other company property.<br></p>', 'Work on improving on timely communication as agreed. Don\'t hesitate to point out any wrong doing in your area of work. Utilize the Communication App as it is confidential.<br>', '<p>Take initiative of learning more on communication, planning and organization which are your weak areas and very vital in your job.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 11:44:26', '2022-11-23 16:41:22'),
(180, 153, 189, '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">I thank the company for the support in our line of work,\r\nprovision of walkie-talkie gadgets has helped reduced airtime overuse to many\r\nguards.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Secondly I would urge the forestry department to ensure expansion of\r\nplantation is done especially on the extended land towards new Katithini since\r\nthis would create a lot of job opportunities to the local people.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Operations department also need to fast track building of a structure for shelter in A016 for protection\r\nduring rainy season and latrines in blocks which lack toilets such as block 6,\r\n3 and 1.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Lastly I would urge the company to at least improve on salary\r\nincrement considering current living standard in the country.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">Kilonzo Kimau started at slower pace during the first few months\r\nafter his employment but has managed to catch up after continuous interaction\r\nfrom last year.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">He however, had a problem with reporting issues due to fear\r\nwhich is actually still his problem up to now. He had notice conflict between\r\nsecurity guards whereby some few guards reports to work late and delays in\r\nhanding over of duty in A016. Due to this, the affected guards always try\'s to\r\npay back to the ones who delayed them and the problem has been occurring for\r\nweeks but has failed to communicate to the FT however he claims, the issue was\r\nreported to the head of security. Such behaviors result to poor\r\nteamwork and results to loss of company\'s properties as observed recently which\r\nis unacceptable.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">The whole team need closer supervision and training on security\r\njob for effective performance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Improve on self confidence, teamwork and managing relationships which is very key in security work.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Work also on the weak areas highlighted in your evaluation.</p>', '2022-11-15 11:48:21', '2022-11-15 18:44:45'),
(181, 49, 192, '<p>I would only request my supervisors to work on ensuring proper supervision and coordination between security guards is done accordingly. There is need to ensure we have meeting points in the plantation for guards patrolling in the plantation to meet at a certain time during the day or night to exchange issues a part from just using walkie-talkies..</p>', '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">The employee is one of the oldest guards on site and started as\r\na casual in forestry work and has been observing activities done by PMSs and incase of a wrong work done always </span>communicates<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;for </span>immediate<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;corrections. In A016, during watering when the PMS does some </span>contrary<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;to what is expected he has always </span>communicated<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt;\">&nbsp;immediately.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Source Sans Pro, sans-serif\">There is however need for improvement to ensure theft cases on a site comes to an end. All guards are expected to be more vigilant at all times on their&nbsp;line of duty.</font></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">More training and interactions is required to the whole\r\nsecurity team for effective work performance<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>Well done for closely monitoring all the activities taking place in the plantation and updating your supervisor.</p><p> Meetings for guards patrolling the plantation are supposed to be their and if they are not happening we should rectify that.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Your perfomance is below average. Work on the weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 12:06:11', '2022-11-15 18:52:58'),
(182, 154, 193, '<p>I would only urge the management to check on increasing the number of security guards on site to ensure all blocks on site has at least a guard during day and night.</p><p>Operations also to fast track on construction of a shelter in A016 for protection during this rainy season.</p>', '<p>Peter Mutua has proven to be able to perform his duties as security guard with ease. He has taken an active role in operating digital devices on site after being trained only once and when assigned Block 4, reporting after every 30 mins has always been maintained.</p><p>There is however need for improvement in terms of communicating issues affecting other guards instead of covering up. There is also need for team work among all guards to ensure company\'s properties are protected at all time.</p>', '<p>Peter well done, you are doing a good job. Stay focused and influence the other team to be committed like you.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p>Welcome to your new Job, work well and deliver.</p><p>Make a difference in the Security of Kiambere.</p>', '2022-11-15 12:15:42', '2022-11-16 19:23:07'),
(183, 155, 195, '<p>First I would urge the management to take seriously and put into actions suggestion given from site since through this, the other workers would feel motivated to give any suggestion for instances, following up on signpost required for site locations and collection of fruits from the plantation has not been implemented.</p><p>Secondly I would also suggest if the company can consider having a sawmill for processing final products from the plantation rather than selling logs after harvesting since this would create more opportunity for the local community in terms of employment opportunities and&nbsp;acquisition<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;of goods at affordable prices.</span></p><p>Finally<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;the management need to consider allowing provision of a shop or a kitchen where workers can get some refreshment before and after the work.</span></p>', '<p>The employee is well committed in his work and being one of the educated guards on site, he needs to ensure he trains the other guards on various activities such handling digital occurrences and reporting on time.</p>', '<p>Dominic you are on the right track, stay focused and continue training the illiterate team on how to use the digital OB and Walkie Talkies.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p>Keep focused on your security Job and get it well done.</p>', '2022-11-15 12:25:29', '2022-11-16 18:56:04'),
(184, 80, 205, '<p>I have taken note of my mistakes. I will work to improve on all of them and be a better employee.&nbsp; I request the company to resume operations and recruit the community more so women that used to work on temporary basis as this job used to be their main source of income.<br></p>', '<p>We have extensively discussed on areas that you need to improve to make your work better. Kindly have all of those areas addressed for a better performance in the next evaluations.</p>', '<p>Your performance is way below the company expectations. </p><p>You really need to get serious with your work and do what is expected of you. A guard should always follow instructions, be honest, reliable and a team player, none of the above your supervisor is getting from you.&nbsp; </p><p>You also need to improve on reporting to work, your absenteeism from work affects the whole team.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 12:30:34', '2022-11-23 16:41:50'),
(185, 134, 171, '<p>I will work on the areas highlighted that needs my attention. <br></p>', '<p>You are generally a hardworking employee, as advised, take note that security is a team set-up, you should therefore always communicate timely any wrong doing in you team to facilitate immediate corrective action.<br></p>', '<p>Weak in communications which is very vital in security job to be added in training need list.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 13:33:40', '2022-11-23 16:38:00'),
(186, 144, 207, '<p>The discussions were enlightening and informative. I was made aware that my tasks were not only the magazine, but include newsletter and calendar designs, meaning that my choice for training in deeper knowledge of designing is justified. One of the ideas that I have on improving the magazine is photos of better quality. I also think having a full-time employment would be a good thing as I\'m aware that my work is a lot, especially time-consuming stuff like getting articles and sales.</p>', '<p>Joel has made a good start this year and was pushed hard in the first months of his employment to design Miti magazine according to specifications of which there are a lot. It is true that being employed full-time would make things easier like putting more time in getting and writing articles and doing sales of both subscriptions and advertisements. I have a feeling that Joel in this respect has not yet tapped his whole network. I support him in his suggestions of acquisition of skills, experience and training, and personal development objectives.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Same as Manager</p>', '2022-11-15 15:17:46', '2022-11-22 21:28:32'),
(187, 146, 206, '<p>The management need to fast track the request from guards on site. Requests made for purchasing torches, construction of shelter in A016 needs to be implemented as fast as possible for effective performance.</p><p>The human resource department also need to fast track employment of the head of security to assist in supervision of activities on site. During such evaluations, I would also urge immediate supervisors to the security team to be take part in evaluation the rest of the team to check on areas of weakness from each individual.</p><p>I would also urge the management to consider salary increment considering current high cost of living.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Japheth Mutemi started as a slower rate during the first three months after employment but from the second evaluation there has been great improvement in ensuring work is done right first time. He however needs to take further responsibility considering currently their is no head of security and the team has to perform as expected and cases of theft recorded on site must come to a stop. He also has to learn the weaknesses and strength of all security guards as had been noted during probation evaluation, there is still a lot which needs to be done on ensuring there is teamwork. Communication of issues affecting guards on site must also improve for effective decision making to prevent any conflict which might results from unsolved cases between guards.</p>', '<p>Take full responsibility as the assistant HOS and stop referring to the weaknesses of the former HOS. A lot is expected from you in installing discipline to the team and ensuring their major strength punctuality in reporting time is maintained.</p><p>Improve on knowledge management as a trained guard you have a lot of relevant knowledge which should be shared with the team.</p><p>Your presence as the assistant HOS must be felt.</p>', '2022-11-15', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security in Kiambere remains a problem although it has improved.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Theft cases have been reported and we never find the people who steal despite having security guards on duty.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">You need to improve on security and honesty to apprehend and report those breaking the law.</p>', '2022-11-15 15:21:45', '2022-11-15 18:56:53');
