(188, 114, 208, '<p>The discussion has been good. In making the security work more efficient, The company should consider getting a vehicle that will assist in movement and dropping guards in respective blocks.<br></p>', '<p>You have the potential of delivering better in your role. Kindly work on your communication to help your team stay out of trouble due to non-conformance.<br></p>', '<p>Take initiative of learning more on communication which was pointed out as your weak area in the evaluation. We need to work as a team for better results.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 16:07:06', '2022-11-23 16:42:51'),
(189, 88, 209, '<p>I would like to have a salary raise.<br></p>', '<p>Salaries are HR and you\'ll be advised. You are however encouraged to work hard in delivering on your roles and as advised, come up with more innovative ways of how work can be done efficiently to save the company extended expenses.<br></p>', '<p>You need to have drive for results which is very key in your work and improve on your communication.&nbsp;</p><p>If every member of the team does what is expected of him the company will be productive and the pay raise will come automatically.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 17:09:00', '2022-11-23 16:44:23'),
(190, 97, 210, '<p>I thank the company that through my employment throughout from the time I was a temporary employee I have managed to take my children to school. I have taken note of the areas I did not do well and shall improve.<br></p>', '<p>Kindly work on improving on the areas you have not performed nicely to better your output. Having been warned early in the year due to non-compliance to the leave policy, you have improved. Keep it up.<br></p>', '<p>Boru always adhere to the leave policy, absenteeism from work affects planning and organization of the whole team. Teamwork is vey important in security work.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-15 17:53:03', '2022-11-23 16:44:47'),
(191, 82, 211, '<p>I thank the company for paying my salary throughout the year and enabling me to support my family and educate my children. I will work on my communication. I also wish the company prosperity and more expansion of it\'s operations. I commit myself to continue protecting its property.<br></p>', '<p>Kindly take note of communication and let your work revolve around it. This way your work will yield better results.<br></p>', '<p>Well done for been a reliable guard who follows instructions but with your 6 years experience a lot is expected from you in guiding the whole team to the right direction.&nbsp;</p><p>Take initiative of improving your communication skills it\'s very key in your work.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-16 10:16:56', '2022-11-23 16:45:13'),
(192, 104, 212, '<p>I thank the company for my employment, I further request for a salary raise as the cost of living is not high.<br></p>', '<p>You\'ve worked well without major issues this year keep it up. You are however encouraged to always communicate to higher authority without fear or intimidation whenever you spot any non-compliance to the policies in your team.<br></p>', '<p>Take initiative of learning more on communication, it was pointed out as your weakest area and it\'s very important in your line of duty.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-16 10:59:12', '2022-11-23 16:45:33'),
(193, 133, 213, '<p>I\'ll continue to work diligently in delivering on my job.<br></p>', '<p>You have worked well throughout the year, More so you\'ve done well in stepping up to assist your team in reading the schedule on the notice board in the absence of the supervisors. You are however encouraged as discussed to utilize the communication channels in place always.<br></p>', '<p>You are doing a good job in running the nursery area in the absence of security supervisors but a lot is expected from you in guiding and training the team in interpretation of the security schedule, use of communication app and digital OB.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-16 11:50:49', '2022-11-23 16:45:51'),
(194, 30, 155, '<p>Will plan more on my work, and strive to improve on the areas that I have a weakness.</p>', '<p>Your daily job is very crucial and affects the performance of the whole department. For our department to be effective and deliver results, you must focus on achieving your objectives and improve on the highlighted areas.<br></p>', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Your performance has not improved from the last evaluation. We still talk of the same issues; poor filing, delays in document processing etc.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Be aware this affects each one in the finance department. This is not good.</p>', '2022-11-23', '<p>We need to work as a team, doing all the things we say we do to achieve the departments objectives.</p><p>Work on the weak areas highlighted during the evaluation.</p>', '2022-11-16 15:06:57', '2022-11-23 16:08:24'),
(195, 156, 198, '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I would only request the operations department\r\nto fast-track construction of a shelter in A016 for protection during rainy\r\nseason and the management to consider salary increment considering current high\r\ncost of living.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Maithya Makua is among the old guards who are\r\nvery committed on their line of work. He always have passion in learning new\r\nthings however how technical it might look. He had a problem handling\r\ndigital occurrence device but has been persistence in trying to learn and\r\ncurrently he is one of the digital occurrence controllers.</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>With 7 yrs in BGF you are among the seasoned security guards hence you have a bigger role of bringing the security team together. With team work and honesty the theft cases in Kiambere will be easily addressed.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p>There are many&nbsp; theft cases reported in Kiambere and no one has ever been arrested or reported by security. There are attempts by security to cover up which you are part of the security team.</p><p>That shows lack of willingness and honesty to do the job.</p><p>This should change and improve on all the other areas that require improvement from the above sections.</p>', '2022-11-16 18:06:44', '2022-11-16 19:00:46'),
(196, 81, 214, '<p>I will continue to work hard to deliver. I also request for salary review.<br></p>', '<p>You have worked well this year without major disciplinary issues. You are encouraged to continue being highly disciplined and follow all the company procedures to the latter to improve performance and deliver more. Kindly work on your communication and utilize all the available communication channels the company has put in place.<br></p>', '<p>With 6 years experience your performance should be better, work on the weak areas pointed out in the evaluation especially communication.</p><p>Take a personal initiative of learning more on communication skills.</p>', '2022-11-16', '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Security is very important to the operations of this company.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">We also appreciate the good suggestions and comments.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">Keep up the good work, work as a team, be honest and work on your weak areas.</p>', '2022-11-16 18:11:54', '2022-11-23 16:46:13'),
(197, 20, 217, '<p>The objectives set were not fully achieved because of change of plan but on my side, i was prepared and ready to work to my best to ensure that the vision and the mission of the company is achieved. Nevertheless, since most of the objectives have been carried forward, i am going to even do better if granted the opportunity. Thank you so much.</p>', '<p>Silas is a devoted employee who has really strived to achieve&nbsp; his targets. With additional self drive and determination&nbsp; since he whethers well with the community, he can out do his targets and impact positivity in the groups for the betterment of the farmers program.&nbsp;</p><p>As an asset in Dokolo site,he is knowledgeable and his foresight in agroforestry leads him ahead of the rest. Much effort&nbsp; needed in team building and attitude change among his colleagues.</p>', '<p>See HOD comments</p>', '2022-11-18', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Sticking to planned activities: - we\r\nwere in a transition period as a company this also meant change in plans to\r\nfacilitate this transition. Work shall get back to normal in 2023.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proper communication: - The staff\r\nhas always been encouraged to seek information through other avenues if they\r\nfeel they are not satisfied by the communication of their supervisors.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proper facilitation: - - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards digital management/maintenance of tools, equipment and\r\nPPE to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack of them or poor\r\nquality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely replacement of\r\ntools, equipment, and PPE.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as\r\nrequested by employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant\r\ntraining schedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-17 16:17:13', '2022-11-22 09:55:31'),
(198, 18, 218, '<p>It was an interactive session and successful but still need to improve on some weak areas as learning is a continuous&nbsp; process.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Akullu resonates well with farmers and commands admiration from them. Her ability to resolve conflict&nbsp; is commendable.&nbsp; Her knowledge in finance management will be vital in village savings and loans associations in groups.&nbsp;</p><p>Teamwork,positive attitude and self drive will be a major positive initiative that she will need to bring on&nbsp; &nbsp;especially to her colleagues in the Dokolo team</p>', '<p>See HOD comments</p>', '2022-11-18', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change in plans: - we were in a\r\ntransition period as a company this also meant a change in plans to facilitate this\r\ntransition. Work shall get back to normal in 2023.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Buil</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">d</span><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> integrity with the farmers by providing them\r\nwith feedback in</span><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> </span><span lang=\"en-KE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">time</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">:- due to the breaks and changes in\r\nplans, this has not been consistent. However, as we resume with full-scale field\r\noperations, emphasis shall be on group formation and building trust among the\r\nfarmer groups as this is the only way we can succeed. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Replacing staff:- Staff\r\nshall be replaced according to needs and it Is not always automatic.</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">d.&nbsp; &nbsp; General comment:- Some sections have not been clearly articulated by the staff making it difficult to understand what she meant. The supervisor needs to make sure while doing this exercise, that his staff explain themselves clearly on the principle that it is for the betterment of the work environment.<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '2022-11-17 17:40:23', '2022-11-22 09:50:15'),
(199, 25, 216, '<p>Through improvement in decision making, punctaulity and timely communication i will deliver the company\'s set objectives successfully.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Charles is an astute, polite and hardworking individual. He commands good knowledge in melia tree production and management. His ability to absorb differences and work for improvement,</p><p>Timely communication and firmness in decision making is however required in executing his mandate.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proper and timely facilitation: - -\r\nwe shall increasingly work towards digital management/maintenance of tools, equipment,\r\nand PPE to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack of them or\r\npoor quality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely replacement\r\nof tools, equipment, and PPE.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proper communication: - The staff\r\nhas always been encouraged to seek information through other avenues if they\r\nfeel they are not satisfied by the communication of their supervisors.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as\r\nrequested by employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant\r\ntraining schedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-17 18:00:15', '2022-11-22 10:00:51'),
(200, 21, 215, '<p>There is good relaying of information from my supervisor, the company needs to fulfil the obligation stipulated in farmers contracts and thanks for retaining all the staff during the hard time of COVID19</p>', '<p>Bonny is a pioneer in the farmers program and has alot of experience in the farmers program.&nbsp; His expertise on group dynamics and sensitization is commendable.&nbsp;</p><p>Team work, honesty and self drive however, are positive traits he needs to work to boost the team productivity and efficiency.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>See HOD comments</p>', '2022-11-18', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">a.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Change of plans: - we were in a\r\ntransition period as a company this also meant change in plans to facilitate this\r\ntransition. Work shall get back to normal in 2023.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proper communication: - The staff\r\nhas always been encouraged to seek information through other avenues if they\r\nfeel they are not satisfied by the communication of their supervisors.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">c.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Proper facilitation: - - we shall\r\nincreasingly work towards digital management/maintenance of tools, equipment and\r\nPPE to prevent challenges at work that could be caused by lack of them or poor\r\nquality. Policies have also been put in place to ensure timely replacement of\r\ntools, equipment, and PPE.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">d.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Trainings shall be mandatory as\r\nrequested by employees. They shall also be done according to the relevant\r\ntraining schedule that shall be put in consideration after reviews within the\r\ndepartment.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:72.0pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">e.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Salary: - salary issues are\r\naddressed as per the HR policy on salaries. This has been explained clearly by\r\nDDHR&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2022-11-17 18:07:14', '2022-11-22 09:58:10'),
(201, 33, 115, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span lang=\"X-NONE\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(4, 120, 87); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Employee: Comments</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">More experience was gained over the year on\r\nleadership, communication and managing teams.&nbsp;\r\nThese further compliments the objective of working towards realizing the\r\ncompanyâ€™s mission and vision.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A system of plantation stock verification to ensure\r\ncorrect stock figures always was put in place. All the non-conformances observed\r\nwere corrected and corrective measures put in place, they should not be\r\nrepeated for continuous improvement. The importance of doing things right the\r\nfirst time is now well understood, and it will be among the personal objectives\r\nfor next year. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Training, delegation, communication and continuous follow\r\nup will be imperative in ensuring things are done correctly and targets achieved.\r\nThe plantations management plans will be complete by end of the year and their\r\nimplementation to commence immediately. The plantations will be sustainably\r\nmanaged according to the management plans and in line with FSC principles. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;,sans-serif;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-US\">The sitesâ€™ teams had various concerns from the\r\nevaluation including tools management which will be addressed for efficient\r\ndelivery of results. &nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>See HOD\'s comments.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>The exercise explored all the aspects of his responsibilities within the section of plantations in the forestry department. It came out clearly that with 4 years on the job, he has a good understanding of Melia plantations and what BGF wants to achieve. Beyond this, there are some non-technical glaring gaps that have led to bad performances by his team. He needs to therefore improve on the following non-technical aspects in his role for him to achieve the expected results at all times.</p><p>1. Assertiveness:- He needs to be more assertive when executing tasks e.g reporting, communication</p><p>2. Effectively back office:- this has been mismanaged or underused and has led to lots of obvious nonconformances going unseen only to be discovered by the M&amp;E or when the supervisor checks the back office.</p><p>3. Own his managerial responsibility:- he must own his responsibility as a manager. His job is to get things done by his team. He has often sat back and accepted excuses from his team ultimately tasks are not accomplished as needed. This has also been observed in the CARs where his responses have been explanations sometimes the same as the response of the auditees instead of giving the precise causes of non-conformance.</p><p>The above-mentioned areas are key for him to better perform especially next year when we aim to do more in the plantations.&nbsp; This means that we shall have more staff to be supervised, communicate to, guided, and explain aspects of the job in a way that they deliver the desired results.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-19 14:09:13', '2022-11-22 10:19:42'),
(202, 3, 219, '<p>As a continuous interaction with the HOD throughout the evaluation, I have learnt the need to look wholistically at the program and improve on the future.&nbsp; The need to follow up for timely implementation, ensuring effective communication and feedback will guarantee good results.</p><p>Having gone through many trainings conducted by HOD this year, there is a lot of uncharted paths ahead full of possibilities in my site that are yet to be explored. This is the nextfocus.</p>', '<p>See HOD comments below.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">1. Different attitude from the staff compared to Kenya:- this is a work in progress as internally within the company, we acknowledge that Uganda is a completely different environment from Kenya. Therefore, different approaches shall be used to address the issues in Uganda.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">2. Farmers not embracing the program wholistically leading to the cutting down of trees:- group formation is the key and consistently engaging the farmers so that they can embrace the program.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">3.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">Frequent site visit:- These shall resume next year.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">General comment:- John has shown unique qualities for having adjusted well and fast from Kenya to Uganda. There is a feeling of more transparency from Dokolo which we have never had since we started the Dokolo program. A lot has come to light on what was not ok and what we can do to improve the program thanks to him. We have however not done much in the field and in the nursery since he started managing the Dokolo team. We have also lost quite a number of staff during this period. Some work, therefore, needs to be done by him in the following areas:</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">a. Understanding of the melia production:- we have relied mostly on incomplete/inconcisstent information from Dokolo nursery team in the previous years. We still have a huge room for improvement in the nursery. With his oversight i think this is now very possible.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">b. Create better relationships with partners &amp; community:- We have had issues in the community with our partners and farmers because former staff have intentionally sabotaged the program for their own benefit.&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty, ); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\"><span style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\">c. Create functional groups that will effect change like he has done previously in kenyan program.</span></p>', '2022-11-19 17:38:45', '2022-11-22 10:32:17'),
(203, 8, 113, '<p>There is no limit to doing good to your best and exploiting your potential in BGF.</p><p>Over the years, I have grown and done my best in my position. There is still a lot of room to do more.</p>', '<p>As always Lawrence has a very positive evaluation. The few areas to improve in the report have been highlighted by himself but they are minor and depend on his team performance. He is the right person at the right place. As we grow and our activities start again he will however not be in a position to continue working as he does, less he can really delegate upon reliable staff. This seems on its way. Lawrence did an extraordinary job in managing the finances these past two years or would I say the lack of finances! We managed to keep paying our staff throughout and all funding has been used to its full possibilities. Great job and great positive mindset!</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See manager\'s comments</p>', '2022-11-22 15:06:16', '2022-11-22 15:19:23'),
(204, 118, 221, '<p>I thank the company for keeping me on the job and giving me an opportunity to work. I will work to correct the areas I have been advised to look into.<br></p>', '<p>Kindly work on the highlighted areas that need an extra effort for better results.<br></p>', '<p>As we resume normal operations bear in mind it\'s your responsibility to take care of your tractor to achieve one of your personal objectives of cutting operational costs by 50%.</p><p>Well done for fitting in the forestry team and adapting very fast after been moved their temporary due to slowed operations.</p>', '2022-11-24', '<p>Security is a team work. There are too many cover ups when security are lateness to work and with cattle grazing. We need to do more to ensure these issues are addressed.</p>', '2022-11-23 11:04:11', '2022-11-28 10:44:14'),
(205, 42, 220, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I thank the\r\ncompany for the employment offered, I have manage to educate my children from\r\nthe resources gained from the company and I look forward to continue working\r\ndiligently on my line of duty.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Secondly I would like to request the company to consider creating a service money for the employees who reaches retirement age while still working with the company as a from of appreciations.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Lastly I would urge the company to create a program of interacting with the local community to educate them on the importance of forestry and educating of children\'s to enhance eradication of poverty in the region.</span></p>', '<p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">The employee is one of the oldest guards on site and started as\r\na casual in security work. He knows all the corners of the plantation and despite being of age, he has been committed in his duties and willing to learn new ideas and technologies used on site.</span></p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">However, there is need to ensure the whole team work as a unit to bridge the gaps creating conflicts between employees to promote teamwork thus ensuring company\'s properties are protected at all time.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;\">A lot of training and interactions is required to the whole\r\nsecurity team for effective work performance.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '<p>With vast experience of 7yrs a lot is expected from you in guiding the team to the right direction and uniting them to work as a team. Security work can\'t be effective if we don\'t work as a team.</p>', '2022-11-24', '<p>Kiambere site has had theft cases and cases of indiscipline from security. None of these theft cases have been known who is stealing despite having security on site. A reminder is that security is team work.&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-23 11:05:29', '2022-11-28 10:40:44'),
(206, 32, 173, '<p>Communication is a crucial department in BGF and I am continuously growing and learning on the Job. I aim to continuously create a positive impact both internally and externally by spearheading the communication department,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt;\">emphasizing the importance of timely\r\nand accurate communication as that is the basis of the right decision taking.</span></p>', '<p>Whenever something is done rightly or wrongly, communication is always involved. The communication responsibilities vested in the DDC by delegation from management are crucial, especially in an operation spread over different sites and even countries. Continuous emphasis and follow-up have already improved the levels of efficient communication tremendously. However the job is not finished, and never will be. It requires adaptation to new ways of thinking, new techniques, new tools, etc... it requires that the communication responsible is on top of the game at all times and identifies new tendencies timely. It is a demanding job but Claudiah has so far done great. There is of course room for improvement but that is not a denial of all the good progress that has been done&gt; Keep it up!</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See supervisor and Managers comment</p>', '2022-11-26 15:48:32', '2022-11-26 15:52:22');
INSERT INTO `section_sixes` (`id`, `user_id`, `extra_info`, `employee_comments`, `supervisor_comments`, `manager_comments`, `manager_date`, `hod_comments`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(207, 103, 224, '<p>The company to resume operations and assist in cleaning the&nbsp; plantation to make patrols easier. The company to also fast track in handling illegal grazers issue. Besides this, I sincerely thank the company for retaining me throughout the COVID pandemic to date.<br></p>', '<p>Kindly work on&nbsp; the areas that you need to improve for better performance next year. Utilize the available communication channels the company has put in place to improve your work deliverables.<br></p>', '<p>Last year objective was not achieved as indicated because we still have cases of illegal grazers and wildlife animals in the plantation who destroy our trees, work towards achieving that in 2023.</p><p>Communication is very key in your job and it was noted as a weak area in the evaluation take intiative of learning more on communication.</p>', '2022-12-02', '<p>We accept your comments on the cleaning and we will work on that.&nbsp;</p><p>Improve on the weak points.</p>', '2022-12-02 11:26:47', '2022-12-07 11:03:43'),
(208, 34, 225, '<p>I am happy to be in HR department. My supervisor has offered all the necessary guidance and support to take charge of the department and I feel we have done great improvements. We are not yet there, and I will work on ensuring I have all the necessary skills and knowledge to do better.</p>', '<p>The HR department is in the best hands possible and will grow as the company grows.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>See Managers comments</p>', '2022-12-08 12:51:24', '2022-12-08 12:52:33'),
(209, 152, 176, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I thank the company for the\r\nemployment offered, I have manage to educate my children from the resources\r\ngained from the company and I look forward to continue working diligently on my\r\nline of duty.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">I look forward to improve on my areas of weaknesses as discussed with my supervisors especially in reporting to work and occurrence updates on site.</span></p>', '<p>The employee is one of the oldest guard on site, He started as a casual in security work. He knows in and out of the plantation however there were still cases of theft and cattle encroachments reported throughout 2022 which must come to a stop.&nbsp;</p><p>There is also need for improvement on timely communication in terms of reporting all occurrences on site.</p>', '<p>Improve on managing relations which is very key for effective teamwork.</p>', '2023-08-24', NULL, '2023-02-01 13:24:35', '2023-08-24 18:02:08'),
(210, 157, 226, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Better Globe\r\nForestry has enabled me to grow my skill within the short period that I have\r\nworked as GIC training and Implementation Officer. The nature of the work has\r\nexposed me to different working environment, this has boosted my interpersonal\r\nskills and made me know how to handle different people at different times.\r\nFollowing our Today\'s discussion areas that need improvement will be worked on,\r\nall the corrections noted out have been taken positively.</span><o:p></o:p></p>', '<p>For the three months, Dan victor Mwangu has been performing his field activities very well, he is self-motivated, he works and performs his duties under low supervision. Dan Victor can now work with BGF company as GIC Training and Implementation Officer. He needs to improve on communication, Planning and organizing.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">From the probation evaluation analysis, Danâ€™s comments, and\nthe supervisor\'s feedback, Dan Victor Mwangu possesses the right attitude to do\nthe job. He managed to immediately fit into the GIC program when he joined at a\ntime of seedling distribution. He shows a willingness to learn, recognizes correction\nfrom the supervisor, and appreciates the fact that she does not withhold\ninformation. He is adaptable and can do the Job.<o:p></o:p></p>', '2023-07-04 11:36:29', '2023-07-04 12:13:11'),
(211, 158, 227, '<p>I need to own the role given as an FSC intern to be able to deliver what is required of me, do better at follow up and interactions with the rest of the staff so that we can all understand what FSC is to our company and why we need the certification.</p>', '<p>To be filled at the HOD level</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>Though not coming from a Forestry background, Damaris managed to quickly learn and grasp all aspects of FSC. She has also managed in 6 months to understand how the company works and with these, she successfully did an FSC internal audit and identified both major and minor gaps as per the FCS requirements. From the evaluation exercise, I am confident that she can do the job. Her strengths have been identified so as the areas that she needs to work on to boost her capacity for growth.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '2023-08-18 16:53:39', '2023-08-22 10:34:11'),
(212, 160, 228, '<p>-We\'ve been doing very well and the support we\'ve gotten from the supervisors and the management has been helpful.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>-Mutuku need to share the knowledge He got from the NYS training to the security team.</p><p>-He needs to keep on with the good work.</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty,/*!*/ /*!*/); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">- Your performance is average and can be improved. Work on the weak points. We look forward to tap on the trainings you gained from NYS.</p><p style=\"border-color: rgba(229, 231, 235, var(--tw-border-opacity)); --tw-border-opacity: 1; --tw-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-inset: var(--tw-empty,/*!*/ /*!*/); --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 #0000; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 #0000;\">- Integrity is very important for security and should at all times be at the highest.</p>', '2023-08-22 14:15:09', '2023-08-25 17:40:10'),
(213, 161, 229, '<p>-The interaction has been good, the mistakes identified such as changing to correct PPE before clocking in.</p>', '<p>-Need to continue working hard and any problem should be reported to either the FT or assistant head of security.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '<p>- Your performance is below expectation.</p><p>- Integrity is very important for security and should at all times be at the highest.</p>', '2023-08-23 13:14:39', '2023-08-25 17:38:28');
